hadiths[630]{hadithnumber,text}:
803,"Hazrat Abu-Humaid Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab namaz key liye khadey hotey to qibley ki taraf munh kartey, apney dono haath uthatey aur kehtey : (اللّٰهُ أَكْبَرُ), ''Allah sab sey bada hai.''"
804,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab namaz shuru kartey to ye dua padhtey : (سُبْحَانَكَ اللّٰهُمَّ وَبِحَمْدِكَ وَتَبَارَكَ اسْمُكَ وَتَعَالٰى جَدُّكَ وَلاَ إِلٰهَ غَيْرُكَ), ''aey Allah ! to pak hai, hum teri tareef key sath teri pakizgi bayan kartey hain aur tera naam barkaton wala hai aur teri shaan buland hai aur terey siwa koi mabood nahin."
805,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab takbire tahreema kehtey to takbir aur qirat key darmiyan thodi der khamosh rehtey. mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! merey maa baap aap par qurban , takbir aur qirat key darmiyan aap khamosh rehtey hain. irshad farmaiye ke aap us waqt kya padhtey hain. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main kehta hun : (اللَّهُمَّ بَاعِدْ بَيْنِى وَبَيْنَ خَطَايَاىَ كَمَا بَاعَدْتَ بَيْنَ الْمَشْرِقِ وَالْمَغْرِبِ , اللَّهُمَّ نَقِّنِى مِنَ الْخَطَايَا كَمَا يُنَقَّى الثَّوْبُ الأَبْيَضُ مِنَ الدَّنَسِ , اللَّهُمَّ اغْسِلْ خَطَايَاىَ بِالْمَاءِ وَالثَّلْجِ وَالْبَرَدِ), ''aey Allah ! merey darmiyan aur merey gunahon key darmiyan is tarah doori dal dey jis tarah tu ney mashriq aur maghrib key darmiyan fasla kar diya hai. aey Allah ! mujhey merey gunahon sey pak kar dey , jis tarah safed kapda mail kuchail sey pak kiya jata hai. aey Allah ! mujhey pani , barf aur olon key zariey sey merey gunahon sey saaf kar dey.''"
806,"Ummul-momenin Aaysha (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab namaz shuru kartey to ye dua padhtey : (سُبْحَانَكَ اللَّهُمَّ وَبِحَمْدِكَ , تَبَارَكَ اسْمُكَ , وَتَعَالَى جَدُّكَ , وَلَا إِلَهَ غَيْرُك) ''aey Allah ! to pak hai aur sari tareefen terey liye hain, tera naam ba-barkat hai, teri shaan buland hai, aur terey ilawa koi mustahiq ibadat nahin."
807,"Hazrat Juber bin Mut-im (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke jab aap namaz shuru kartey to teen baar farmatey : (اللّٰهُ أَكْبَرُ كَبِيرًا , اللّٰهُ أَكْبَرُ كَبِيرًا), ''Allah bada hai, sab sey bada, Allah bada hai, sab sey bada. phir teen baar farmatey : (الْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ كَثِيرًا , الْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ كَثِيرًا), ''sab tareef Allah hi ki hai, bahut ziyada tareef. sab tareef Allah hi ki hai. bahut ziyada tareef. phir teen baar kehtey : (سُبْحَانَ اللَّهِ بُكْرَةً وَأَصِيلًا), ''main subah Sham Allah ki tasbih aur taqdees karta hun.'' aur baad mein ye kalmaat bhi padhtey :  (اللَّهُمَّ إِنِّي أَعُوذُ بِكَ مِنَ الشَّيْطَانِ الرَّجِيمِ , مِنْ هَمْزِهِ , وَنَفْخِهِ , وَنَفْثِهِ), ''aey Allah ! main teri panah mein aata hun, mardud shetan sey, uskey (shararat key sath) chhuney sey, uski phunk sey aur uskey thutkaarne sey.'' Hazrat Amr (bin Murra) (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : uskey chhuney sey murad mautaa ki bimari hai. aur uska thutkaarna (khilafe shariyat) shaeyri hai, aur uski phunk takabbur hai."
808,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (اللَّهُمَّ إِنِّي أَعُوذُ بِكَ مِنَ الشَّيْطَانِ الرَّجِيمِ , وَهَمْزِهِ , وَنَفْخِهِ , وَنَفْثِهِ), ''aey Allah ! main teri panah mein aata hun mardud shetan sey, uskey chhuney sey , uski phunk sey aur uskey thutkaarne sey. Raavi bayan kartey hain ke : uskey chhuney sey murad mautaa ki bimari hai, aur uska thutkaarna shaeyri hai, aur uski phunk takabbur hai."
809,"Hazrat Halab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamein namaz padhatey they daain haath sey baaein hath ko pakad letey they."
810,"Hazrat Wayl bin Hajar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko namaz padhtey dekha. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney daain haath sey baaein hath ko pakad liya."
811,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey paas sey guzrey , mainey ( namaz mein) apney daain haath par baayan haath rakha huwa tha. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mera daayan haath pakda aur usey baaein hath par rakh diya."
812,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (اَلْحَمْدُ لِلّٰهِ رَبِّ الْعٰلَمِيْنَ) sey qirat ki ibtida (shuruat) farmatey they."
813,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) , Hazrat abu-Bakar aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhuma) (اَلْحَمْدُ لِلّٰهِ رَبِّ الْعٰلَمِيْنَ) sey qirat shuru kartey they."
814,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) qirat ki ibtidaa : (اَلْحَمْدُ لِلّٰهِ رَبِّ الْعٰلَمِيْنَ) sey kartey they.
815,"Hazrat Yazeed bin Abdullah bin Mughaffal sey riwayat hai, unhoney apney walid (Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu)) key barey mein farmaya : mainey Islam mein bidat sey nafrat karney mein un sey sakht afrad Shaaz aur Naadir hi dekhey hain. unhoney mujhey (namaz mein)  (بسم اللہ الرحمن الرحیم) padhtey suna. to farmaya : beta ! bidat sey ijtinab (bacha) karo. mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki iqtida (pairvi) mein bhi namazein padhi hain aur abu-Bakar , umr aur Usman Raziallahu anhum key sath bhi. mainey un mein sey kisi ko aisey padhtey nahin suna. isliye jab tum qirat karo to kaho : (اَلْحَمْدُ لِلّٰهِ رَبِّ الْعٰلَمِيْنَ)."
816,"Hazrat Qutba bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko subah ki namaz mein ye aayat padhtey suna : (وَالنَّخْلَ بٰسِقٰتٍ لَّهَا طَلْعٌ نَّضِيْدٌ ) (Qaaf : 10), ''aur hamney khajoor key buland aur baala darkht paida kiye, jinkey khoshey teh bah teh hotey hain."""
817,"Hazrat Amr bin Hures (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath namaz padhi aur aap Fajr ki namaz mein qirat farma rahey they. (mujhey wo tilawat is tarah yad hai) goya main ab bhi aap sey ye aayaat sun raha hun : (فَلَآ اُقْسِمُ بِالْخُنَّسِ الْجَـــوَارِ الْكُنَّسِ )' ""main qism khata hun peechhey hatney waley, chalney waley, chhupney waley sitaron ki.''"
818,Hazrat Abu-Barza (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Fajr ki namaz mein saath sey sau aayaat tak tilawat kartey they.
819,"Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamen namaz padhatey they to Zohar ki pehli rakat mein taweel qirat kartey they aur dusri rakat mein (us sey) kam qirat kartey they. subah ki namaz bhi isi tarah padhatey they."
820,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Saaib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney subah ki namaz mein Sura- Mominun tilawat farmaai, jab Hazrat Eisaa (Alaihissalam) ka zikr aaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko khaansi aa gaee to aap rukoo mein chaley gaey."
821,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Jume key din Fajr ki namaz mein (الٓمّ تَنْزِيْلُ) aur (هَلْ اَتٰى عَلَي الْاِنْسَانِ) padha kartey they.
822,"Hazrat Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Jume key din namaze Fajr mein (الٓمّ تَنْزِيْلُ) aur (هَلْ اَتٰى عَلَي الْاِنْسَانِ) padha kartey they."
823,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Jume key din subah ki namaz mein (الٓمّ تَنْزِيْلُ) aur (هَلْ اَتٰى عَلَي الْاِنْسَانِ) padha kartey they.
824,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Jume key din subah ki namaz mein (الٓمّ تَنْزِيْلُ) aur (هَلْ اَتٰى عَلَي الْاِنْسَانِ) padha kartey they. Is-haq Raavi bayan kartey hain hamein Amr ney Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey isi tarah bayan kiya hai. main is mein kisi qism ka shak nahin karta.
825,"Hazrat Qaz'a (bin Yahya Basri) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki namaz key mutalliq sawal kiya, unhoney farmaya : terey liye is mein bhalai nahin. mainey kaha : Allah aap par reham farmaae, bayan farma dijiye. unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key hukm sey Zohar ki iqaamat kahi jati thi, to hum mein sey eik shakhs Baqee ki taraf jata, (wahan pahunch kar) hajat sey farigh hota, phir wapis aa kar wuzu karta aur (jab masjid mein pahunchta to) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Zohar ki pehli rakat mein paa leta."
826,"Hazrat abu-Ma'mar Rahimahullah sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Hazrat Khubab (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : aap logon ko Zohar aur Asr mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki qirat ka kis tarah ilm hota tha? unhoney farmaya : aap ki Daadhi-Mubarak ki harkat sey."
827,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey falan sey ziyada kisi ki namaz Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki namaz sey mushabeh nahin dekhi. Hazrat Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Yasar (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : wo sahaba Zohar ki pehli do rakaaton mein taweel qirat kartey they, aur aakhiri do rakaaton mein kami farmatey they, aur Asr ki namaz (zohar key muqabley mein) halki padhaatey they."
828,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : (eik baar) tees badri Sahaba Raziallahu anhum (eik jagah) jama ho gaey. unhoney (aapas mein) kaha : aaiye, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sari namazon mein qirat (ki miqdaar) ka andaza karen. un mein sey kisi do mein ikhtilaf nahin huwa, (aur unhoney ba-ittifaaq faisla diya) unka andaza ye tha ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki qr'at Zohar ki pehli rakat mein tees aayaton key barabar hoti thi aur dusri rakat mein us sey nisf (aadhi) aur Asr ki namaz key barey mein unka andaza ye tha ke wo Zohar ki aakhiri rakaaton sey nisf (aadhi) hoti thi."
829,"Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamein namaz padhatey huye Zohar ki pehli do rakaaton mein qirat kartey they aur kabhi kabhi hamein aayat suna detey they."
830,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamen Zohar ki namaz padhatey they, aur hamein chand aayaton key baad eik aayat Sura- Luqman aur Zaariyaat ki sunai deti thi."
831,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) ney apni walida (Hazrat Lubaaba (Raziallahu anhuma)) sey riwayat kiya ke unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Maghrib ki namaz mein (وَالْمُرْسَلٰتِ عُرْفًا) (Sura- Murselaat) padhtey suna.
832,"Hazrat Juber bin Moa'tam (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Maghrib ki namaz mein Sura- taur padhtey suna. Hazrat Juber (Raziallahu anhu) ney eik aur hadees key doran mein farmaya : jab mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye aayaat padhtey suna (اَمْ خُلِقُوْا مِنْ غَيْرِ شَيْءٍ اَمْ هُمُ الْخٰلِقُوْن . ۔ . ۔ . ۔ . فَلْيَاْتِ مُسْتَمِعُهُمْ بِسُلْطٰنٍ مُّبِيْنٍ)''kya wo baghair kisi (paida karney waley) key (khud ba-khud) paida kiye gaey hain? ya wo khud paida karney waley hain? kya unhoney aasmano aur zamin ko paida kiya hai? balke wo log yaqin nahin rakhtey, ya kya unkey paas terey Rab key khazaney hain? ya wo (un khazanon key) darogha hain? ya kya unkey paas koi seedhi hai ke wo is par (chadh kar aasman ki baaten) sun letey hain? (agar aisa hai) to phir chahiye ke unka sunney wala koi roshan daleel pesh karey.""to qarib tha ke mera dil ud jaeyga."
833,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Maghrib ki namaz mein (قُلْ يٰٓاَيُّهَا الْكٰفِرُوْنَ) aur (قُلْ هُوَ اللّٰهُ اَحَدٌ) tilawat kiya kartey they."
834,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki iqtida (pairvi) mein namaze Isha ada ki, unhoney farmaya : mainey aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko (وَالتِّيْنِ وَالزَّيْتُوْنِ) padhtey suna."
835,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney mazkura baala irshad farma kar kaha : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ziyada khush aawaz ya achchhi qirat karney wala koi insan nahin suna."
836,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) ney apney muqtadiyon ko Isha ki namaz padhaai aur is mein taweel qirat ki to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum (aisi suraten) padha karo : (وَالشَّمْسِ وَضُحٰىهَا سَبِّحِ اسْمَ رَبِّكَ الْاَعْلَى وَالَّيْلِ اِذَا يَغْشٰى aur اِقْراْ بِاسْمِ رَبِّكَ).
837,"Hazrat Ubada bin Samit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney namaz mein Sura- Fatiha nahin padhi uski koi namaz nahin."
838,"Hazrat abu-Saaib (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey suna ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney koi namaz padhi aur is mein Umme Quran (Sura- Fatiha) na padhi to wo (namaz) naqis hai, na-mukammal hai. (Abu-Saaib (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain) mainey arz kiya : Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ! kabhi main Imam key peechhey bhi hota hun (to phir bhi padhun)? unhoney merey bazu ko dabaayaa aur farmaya : aey Faarsi ! isey apney ji mein (aahista) padh ley."
839,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya is shakhs ki koi namaz nahin jo farz aur nafl namaz ki har rakat mein (اَلْحَمْدُ لِلّٰهِ) aur iskey sath koi aur sura nahin padhta."
840,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye irshade Mubarak suna : har wo namaz jis mein Ummu-Kitab (Sura- Fatiha) na padhi jaey wo naqis hai."
841,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har wo namaz jis mein Sura- Fatiha na padhi jaey, wo naqis hai, wo naqis hai."
842,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, un sey eik shakhs ney sawal kiya : kya main us waqt bhi qirat kiya karun jab Imam qirat kar raha ho? Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : eik aadmi ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey sawal kiya tha : kya har namaz mein qirat hai? to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : haan. haazirin mein sey eik sahab ney kaha : ye to wajib ho gaee."
843,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log Imam key peechhey Zohar aur Asr ki namazon mein pehli do rakaaton mein Sura Fatiha aur koi aur sura padhtey they, aur baad ki do rakaaton mein (sirf) Sura Fatiha padhtey they."
844,"Hazrat Samura bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mujhey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key do saktey yad hain. Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ney us sey ittifaq na kiya to hamney Madina mein Hazrat Ubai-bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) ko (khat) likha (ke is masley mein faisla den) unhoney (jawabi tor par) likh bheja ke Hazrat Samra (Raziallahu anhu) ney (sahih) yad rakha hai. Saeed (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : hamney Qatada (Rahimahullah) sey daryaft kiya : ye do saktey kon kon sey hain? unhoney farmaya : (eik to) jab namaz mein dakhil hotey hain aur (eik) jab (Imam) qirat sey farigh hota hai. doosrey moqe par Qatada (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : jab Imam (غَيْرِ الْمَغْضُوبِ عَلَيْهِمْ وَلَا الضَّالِّينَ) kehta hai. Hazrat Qatada (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : Sahaba kiram ko ye baat pasand thi ke jab Imam qirat sey farigh ho to thoda sa khamosh ho jaey yahan tak key uska saans durust ho jaey."
845,Hazrat Hasan (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Samura (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mujhey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key do saktey yad hain. eik sakta qirat sey pehley aur eik sakta rukoo sey pehley. Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ney un sey ittifaq na kiya. chunanche unhoney Hazrat Ubai-bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf Madina Munawra khat likha. to Hazrat Abi (Raziallahu anhu) ney Hazrat Samura (Raziallahu anhu) ki taeed farmaai.
846,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Imam isliye muqarrar kiya jata hai ke uski perwi ki jaey, chunanche jab wo Allahu-Akbar kahey to tum Allahu-Akbar kaho, jab wo qirat karey to khamosh raho, aur jab wo (غَيْرِ الْمَغْضُوْبِ عَلَيْهِمْ وَ لَا الضَّآلِّيْنَ) padhey to tum Aameen kaho, jab wo rukoo karey to rukoo karo, jab wo (سَمِعَ اللَّهُ لِمَنْ حَمِدَهُ) kahey to kaho (اللَّهُمَّ رَبَّنَا لَكَ الْحَمْدُ). ''aey Allah ! aey hamarey Rab ! terey hi liye tareefen hain, jab wo sajda kerey. to tum sajda karo aur jab wo beth kar namaz padhaaey to tum sab beth kar namaz padho.''"
847,"Hazrat abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab Imam qirat karey to khamosh raho , aur jab wo qaada tak pahunch jaey to sab sey pehley Allah ka jo zikr karo wo tashahud hona chahiye."
848,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apney Sahaba ko namaz padhaai jo ghaaliban subah ki namaz thi. (namaz key baad) farmaya : kya tum mein sey kisi ney qirat ki hai? eik aadmi ney kaha : ji haan. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main keh raha tha, kya wajeh hai ke mujh sey tilawate Quran mein kash-ma-kash ho rahi hai?"
849,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein namaz padhaai. iskey baad Raavi ney puri hadees zikr ki, iskey aakhir mein ye izafa hai. iskey baad Sahaba ney un namazon mein khamoshi ikhtiyar farmaai jin mein Imam buland aawaz sey qirat karta hai."
850,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis ka koi Imam ho to Imam ki qirat usi ki qirat hai."
851,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab qirat karney wala (Imam) Aameen kahey to tum bhi Aameen kaho kyonkey farishtey bhi Aameen kehtey hain to jiski Aameen farishton ki Aameen sey mil gaee uskey guzishta gunah maaf ho jaeyngey."
852,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab qirat karney wala (Imam) Aameen kahey to tum bhi Aameen kaho jiski Aameen farishton ki Aameen key muwaafiq ho gaee, uskey guzishta gunah maaf ho jaeyngey."
853,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : logon ney Aameen kehna chhod diya hai. halanke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab (غَيْرِ الْمَغْضُوْبِ عَلَيْهِمْ وَ لَا الضَّآلِّيْنَ) kehtey they to (buland aawaz sey) Aameen kehtey they yahan tak key pehli saf waley sun letey, phir us (aameen) ki aawaz sey masjid goonj uthti."
854,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna ke jab aap ney (وَلَاالضَّآلِّيْنَ) kaha to farmaya : aameen."
855,"Hazrat Wayl bin Hajar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki iqtida (pairvi) mein namaz padhi jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (وَلَاالضَّآلِّيْنَ) kaha to farmaya : aameen, hum sab ney aap ki Aameen suni."
856,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Yahudi tum sey kisi chiz par itna hasad nahin kartey, jitna salam aur Aameen par tum sey hasad kartey hain."
857,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Yahudi tum sey kisi baat par itna hasad nahin kartey , jitna tum sey Aameen par hasad kartey hain, isliye Aameen kasrat sey kaha karo."
858,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke jab aap namaz shuru kartey to apney haath uthatey yahan tak key unhen kandhey key barabar buland kar letey aur jab rukoo kartey aur jab rukoo sey sar uthatey (to bhi rafaa-yadein kartey) aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sajdon key darmiyan haath nahin uthatey they."
859,Hazrat Malik bin Huweris (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab Allahu-Akbar kehtey to apney haath uthatey yahan tak key unhein kanon key qarib ley jatey. aur jab rukoo kartey to isi tarah kartey aur jab rukoo sey sar uthatey to isi tarah kartey.
860,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko namaz mein kandhon tak haath uthatey dekha, jab namaz shuru kartey, jab rukoo kartey aur jab sajda kartey."
861,"Hazrat Umer bin Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farz namaz mein har takbir key sath rafa'ul-yaden kartey they."
862,"Hazrat abu-Humed Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney das sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum ki mojudgi mein farmaya jin mein Hazrat Qatada bin Rabaee (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they : main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki namaz (ka tareeqa) tum sab sey ziyada janta hun. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab namaz mein khadey hotey to bilkul sidhey khadey hotey aur apney haath itney buland kartey ke kandhon key barabar utha letey, phir kehtey (Allahu-Akbar), phir jab rukoo karna chahtey to dono haath uthatey yahan tak key unhen kandhon key barabar buland kar letey, jab (Samia' Allahu-liman-hamida) kehtey to rafaa-yadein kartey aur sidhey khadey ho jatey, jab wo do rakatein padh kar (teesri rakat key liye) uthtey to (Allahu-Akbar) kehtey aur dono haath uthatey, yahan tak key kandhon key barabar buland kar letey jaisey namaz shuru kartey waqt kiya tha."
863,"Hazrat Abbas bin Sehal Saaidi (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Abu-Humed (saaidi), Hazrat Abu-Usaid Saaidi, Hazrat Sehal bin Saad aur Hazrat Muhammad bin Muslima Raziallahu anhum (eik majlis mein) jama ho gaey. unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki namaz ka tazkira kiya. to Abu-Humed (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : tum sab sey ziyada main Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki namaz sey waqif hun. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khadey huye to (Allahu-Akbar) kaha aur rafa'ul-yaden kiya. phir jab rukoo key liye (Allahu-Akbar) kaha to rafa'ul-yaden kiya, phir khadey huye to rafa'ul-yaden kiya, aur sidhey khadey ho gaey yahan tak key har haddi apni jagah par wapis aa gaee."
864,"Hazrat Ali bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab farz namaz padhney key liye khadey hotey, to (Allahu-Akbar) kehtey aur dono haath uthatey yahan tak key wo kandhon key barabar (buland) ho jatey. jab rukoo karna chahtey to isi tarah kartey, jab rukoo sey sar uthatey to isi tarah kartey aur jab do rakatein padh kar khadey hotey to (phir) isi tarah kartey."
865,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) har takbir key waqt rafaa-yadein kartey they.
866,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab namaz shuru kartey aur jab rukoo kartey to dono haath uthaya kartey they.
867,"Hazrat Wayl bin Hajar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey dil mein kaha ke main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko (tawajjoh sey) dekhunga ke aap kis tarah namaz padhtey hain. (mainey dekha ke) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khadey huye, qibley ki taraf munh kiya, apney dono haath uthaey yahan tak key wo aap key kanon key barabar ho gaey. jab aap ney rukoo kiya to phir unhen isi tarah uthaya jab rukoo sey sar uthaya to isi tarah unhen buland kiya."
868,"Hazrat abu-Zubair (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) jab namaz shuru kartey to dono haath uthatey aur jab rukoo kartey aur rukoo sey sar uthatey to isi tarah kartey aur farmatey : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko isi tarah kartey dekha hai. (abu-Zubair (Rahimahullah) key shagrid) Hazrat Ibrahim bin Tahmaan (Rahimahullah) ney (hadees bayan kartey waqt) kanon tak haath uthaey."
869,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab rukoo kartey to apna sar na ooncha rakhtay, na usey (bahut ziyada) jhuka detey balke (un dono haalaton key) darmiyan mein rakhtey."
870,"Hazrat Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs rukoo aur sajdey mein kamar sidhi nahin karta, uski namaz durust nahin."
871,"Hazrat Ali bin Sheban (Raziallahu anhu) jo apney qabiley key wafad mein shamil they, unhoney farmaya : hum log (apney ilaqey sey) rawana ho kar Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye. hamney aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki baiat ki aur aap key peechey namaz ada ki. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney aankh key kinarey sey eik aadmi ko dekha ke rukoo aur sajda sahw ada nahin kar raha tha, yani kamar sidhi nahin kar raha tha. jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) namaz sey farigh huye to farmaya : aey musalmanon ki jamaat ! us shakhs ki koi namaz nahin jo rukoo aur sajda mein kamar sidhi nahin karta ."
872,"Hazrat Wabsa bin Maabad (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko namaz padhtey dekha . aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab rukoo kartey they to kamar is qadr barabar kartey they ke agar kamar par pani dala jaey to thehar jaey ."
873,"Hazrat Musab bin Saad (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey apney walid (Hazrat Saad bin abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) ) key qarib ( namaz padhtey huye ( rukoo kya to tatbeeq (yaksaniyat) ki. unhoney merey haath par maara aur farmaya : hum pehley is tarah kya kartey they, phir hamen hukm diya gaya ke (haath) ghutnon key ooper rakhen ."
874,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) rukoo kartey they to apney haath ghutnon par rakhtey they aur baazuon ko) pahluon sey) door rakhtey they."
875,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab ( سَمِعَ اللّٰهُ لِمَنْ حَمِدَهُ ) kehtey to ( uskey baad ( رَبَّنَا وَلَكَ الْحَمْدُ ) kehtey they.
876,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab Imam kahey : ( سَمِعَ اللَّهُ لِمَنْ حَمِدَهُ ), Allah uski baat sunta hai jo uski tareef karta hai, , to kaho : ( رَبَّنَا وَلَكَ الْحَمْدُ ), aey hamarey rab ! aur terey liye hi sab taarifein hain."
877,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab Imam ( سَمِعَ اللَّهُ لِمَنْ حَمِدَهُ ) kahey to tum ( رَبَّنَا وَلَكَ الْحَمْدُ ) kaho."
878,"Hazrat Abdullah bin abi Ufa( سَمِعَ اللَّهُ لِمَنْ حَمِدَهُ اللهم رَبَّنَا لَكَ الْحَمْدُ مِلْءَ السَّمَوَاتِ وَمِلْءَ الأَرْضِ وَمِلْءَ ما شِئْتَ مِنْ شَىْءٍ بَعْدُ ) ' Allah ney sun li jisney bhi uski tareef ki, aey Allah ! aey hamarey rab ! terey hi liye (sab) tareefein hain, aasmano aur zamin key bharaw key barabar aur har us chiz key bharaaw key barabar jo to uskey baad chahey."
879,"Hazrat abu-Juhaifa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) namaz padh rahey they. (is beech mein) aap key paas (dunyawi) khush qismati (aur maal o dolat) ka zikr kya gaya . eik ney kaha : falan ghodon key lihaz sey bada khush nasib hai. ( bahut sey ghodey uski dolat hain ( doosrey ney kaha : falan ki khush qismati oonton sey hai. eik aur bola : falan ki achi qismat bakriyon sey hai. eik aur bola : falan londi aur ghulamon key lihaz sey bada khush bakhsh hai. jab Rasoolullah ney namaz mukammal ki, aur aakhiri rakat mein rukoo sey sar uthaya to farmaya : (اللَّهُمَّ رَبَّنَا لَكَ الْحَمْدُ مِلْءَ السَّمَوَاتِ وَمِلْءَ الأَرْضِ وَمِلْءَ مَا شِئْتَ مِنْ شَىْءٍ بَعْدُ ، اللَّهُمَّ لاَ مَانِعَ لِمَا أَعْطَيْتَ وَلاَ مُعْطِىَ لِمَا مَنَعْتَ وَلاَ يَنْفَعُ ذَا الْجَدِّ مِنْكَ الْجَدُّ)'aey Allah ! aey hamarey rab ! terey hi liye (sab) tareef hai. aasmano bhar , zamin bhar aur uskey baad jo chiz to chahey , uskey bhadney key barabar . aey Allah ! jo kuch to inayat farmaai usey koi rok nahin sakta aur jo kuch to rok ley (aur na dena chahey) wo chiz koi dey nahin sakta aur kisi (dunyawi) qismat (aur maal o dolat) waley ki (zahiri) khush qismati (aur dolat) usey tujh sey (bachaney mein) kaam nahin aa sakti . Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (aakhiri jumla) (ذَالْجَدِّ) farmatey waqt aawaz ko tool diya ke un (Sahaba) ko malum ho jaey ke haqiqat wo nahin jo wo log keh rahey hain."
880,Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab sajda kartey to haathon (aur baazuon) ko (pahluon sey) alag kartey . agar koi memn samney sey (baazuon key nichey sey) guzarna chahta to guzar jata .
881,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Aqram Khuzai (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main namra key maidan mein apney walid key sath tha. hamarey paas sey eik qafley ka guzar huwa . un logon ney raastey key qarib padaaw dala . mujhey abba jaan ney kaha : tum bakriyon mein raho ( unka khayal rakho .) main un logon (qafla walon) key paas ja kar un sey baat cheet karunga . abba jaan chaley gaey, main bhi qarib chala gaya, dekha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif farma they. namaz ka waqt huwa to mainey unkey sath namaz (ba-jamaat) ada ki. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab sajda kartey they to mujhey aap ki baghlon ki safedi nazar aati thi . Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : log Raavi ka naam Ubedullah bin Abdullah letey hain, jabke abu-Bakar bin abi sheeba ney kaha ke log Raavi ko Abdullah bin Ubedullah kehtey hain. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney eik dusri sanad sey apney ustaad Muhammad bin Bishr sey bhi Ubedullah bin Abdullah bin Aqram Khuzai an Abih key wastey sey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey isi tarah riwayat bayan ki."
882,"Hazrat Wayl bin Hajar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke jab aap sajda kartey they to haathon sey pehley ghutney ( zamin par) rakhtey they aur jab sajdey sey sar uthatey they to ghutnon sey pehley haath uthatey they."
883,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey sath haddiyon par sajda karney ka hukm diya gaya hai."
884,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey hukm diya gaya hai ke saat (aaza) par sajda karun aur baalon ya kapdon ko na sametun. ibne-Taaus (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : merey walid (ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) key shagrid Hazrat Taaus (Rahimahullah)) farmaya kartey they : yani do haath , do ghutney , do qadam (aur peshani aur naak) wo peshani aur naak ko eik hi uzu shumar kartey they."
885,"Hazrat Abbas bin abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye irshad Mubarak suna : jab banda sajda karta hai to uskey sath saat aaza sajda kartey hain. uska chehra , uskey dono haath , uskey dono ghutney aur dono paon ."
886,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key Sahabi Hazrat Ahmar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab sajda kartey to haathon (aur baazuon) ko pahluon sey itna door kartey ke hamen (us mashaqqat ki keyfiyat ko dekh kar) taras aata ."
887,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir Johni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab ye aayat nazil hui : ( فَسَبِّحْ بِاسْمِ رَبِّكَ الْعَظِيمِ) apney azmat waley rab key naam ki tasbih kijiye. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen farmaya : ye kaam apney rukoo mein karo. aur jab ye aayat nazil hui : ( سَبِّحِ اسْمَ رَبِّكَ الأَعْلَى )' apney rab key naam ki tasbih kijiye jo sab sey buland hai. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hum sey farmaya : ye kaam apney sajdon mein karo ."
888,"Hazrat Huzefa bin Yaman (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna ke jab aap rukoo kartey to teen baar (سُبْحَانَ رَبِّىَ الْعَظِيمِ) kehtey aur jab sajda kartey to teen baar ( سُبْحَانَ رَبِّىَ الأَعْلَى ) kehtey ."
889,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) rukoo aur sajdey mein ye dua kasrat sey padhtey they : ( سُبْحَانَكَ اللَّهُمَّ وَبِحَمْدِكَ , اللَّهُمَّ اغْفِرْلِى ) 'aey Allah! main teri tareef key sath teri pakizgi bayan karta hun, aey Allah! mujhey bakhsh dey. aap (us dua key zariey sey) Quran par amal kartey they."
890,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey koi shakhs rukoo karey to usey chahiye ke rukoo mein teen baar kahey : ( سُبْحَانَ رَبِّىَ الْعَظِيمِ ) 'pak hai mera rab azmaton wala . jab usney aisa kya to uska rukoo pura ho gaya aur jab koi shakhs sajda karey to sajdey mein teen baar kahey : ( سُبْحَانَ رَبِّىَ الأَعْلَى ) , pak hai mera rab sab sey buland o bartar , jab usney aisa kya to uska sajda mukammal ho gaya aur ye kam az kam miqdaar hai."
891,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi shakhs sajda karey to aetidaal ko ikhtiyar karey aur apney bazu is tarah na phelaey jis tarah kutta phelaata hai."
892,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sajdey mein aetidaal ikhtiyar karo aur sajda kartey waqt kuttey ki tarah bazu (zameen par) na phailaao."
893,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab rukoo sey sar uthatey to us waqt tak sajda nahin kartey they. jab tak puri tarah khadey na ho jatey, aur jab sajda kar key sar uthatey, us waqt tak (doosra) sajda nahin kartey they jab tak achchhi tarah beth na jatey aur aap apna baayan paon bichha letey they."
894,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey farmaya : do sajdon key darmiyan is tarah na beth ke peeth aur eidiyaan zamin par hon aur dono pindliyan khadi hon."
895,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey Ali ! kuttey ki tarah ediyon par mat beth."
896,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey farmaya : jab to sajdey sey sar uthaey to is tarah na beth jis tarah kutta bethta hai. apney peeth apney qadmon key darmiyan rakh aur paon ki ooper ki samt zamin sey mila dey."
897,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) do sajdon key darmiyan yun kaha kartey they : ( رَبِّ اغْفِرْلِي , رَبِّ اغْفِرْلِي ), ''aey merey Rab ! mujhey bakhsh dey, aey merey Rab ! meri maghfirat farma."
898,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat ki namaz (tahajjud) mein do sajdon key darmiyan (jalse mein) yun kehtey they : ( رَبِّ اغْفِرْلِى وَارْحَمْنِى وَاجْبُرْنِى وَارْزُقْنِى وَارْفَعْنِى ), ''aey merey Rab ! meri maghfirat farma, mujh par reham kar, merey naqs door farma, mujhey rizq dey aur mujhey bulandi ata farma."
899,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath namaz ada kartey to kehtey : bandon ki taraf sey Allah ko salam, Jibreel ko salam, Mekael ko salam, falan falan farishton ko salam. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein (ye kehtey) sun liya to farmaya : yun na kaho : (السَّلاَمُ عَلَى اللّٰهِ ),  Allah ko salam, Allah Taala to khud السلام (salamti bakhshney wala) hai jab tum (tashahud mein) betho to kaho : ( التَّحِيَّاتُ لِلَّهِ وَالصَّلَوَاتُ وَالطَّيِّبَاتُ السَّلاَمُ عَلَيْكَ أَيُّهَا النَّبِىُّ وَرَحْمَةُ اللَّهِ وَبَرَكَاتُهُ السَّلاَمُ عَلَيْنَا وَعَلَى عِبَادِ اللَّهِ الصَّالِحِينَ ), ''tamam aadaab aur taslimaat Allah hi key liye hain aur tamam namazein aur pakizah aamaal bhi usi key liye hain. aey Nabi ! aap par salamti ho aur Allah ki rehmat aur barkaten nazil hon. hum par bhi salamti ho aur Allah key nek bandon par bhi.'' jab banda ye kehta hai to dua aasman aur zamin mein mojud har nek bandey (insan, jin aur farishtey) ko pahunch jati hai. phir kaho : (أَشْهَدُ أَنْ لاَ إِلَهَ إِلاَّ اللَّهُ وَأَشْهَدُ أَنَّ مُحَمَّدًا عَبْدُهُ وَرَسُولُهُ), ''main gawahi deta hun ke Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin aur main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur uskey Rasool hain.'' Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney eik aur sanad sey Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) hi sey mazkura baala riwayat ki maanind hadees bayan ki. eik riwayat mein ye alfaz hain : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum ko ye tashahud sikhatey they. uskey baad Raavi ney mazkura hadees ki tarah bayan kiya."
900,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamein tashahud is tarah sikhatey they jis tarah Quran ki koi sura sikhatey they. aap farmaya kartey they (التَّحِيَّاتُ الْمُبَارَكَاتُ الصَّلَوَاتُ الطَّيِّبَاتُ لِلَّهِ السَّلاَمُ عَلَيْكَ أَيُّهَا النَّبِىُّ وَرَحْمَةُ اللَّهِ وَبَرَكَاتُهُ السَّلاَمُ عَلَيْنَا وَعَلَى عِبَادِ اللَّهِ الصَّالِحِينَ أَشْهَدُ أَنْ laa إِلَهَ إِلاَّ اللَّهُ وَأَشْهَدُ أَنَّ مُحَمَّدًا عَبْدُهُ وَرَسُولُهُ), ''barkaton waley aadaab, pakizah ibadaten, Allah key liye hain. aey Nabi ! aap par salam ho aur Allah ki rahmatein aur barkate (nazil) hon, hum par aur Allah key nek bandon par salam ho, main gawahi deta hun ke Allah key siwa koi ibadat key laaiq nahin aur main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur uskey Rasool hain."
901,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein khutba diya aur hamarey liye hamari sunnatein bayan farmaeen aur hamein namaz ki taalim di, (usi doran mein) farmaya : jab tum namaz padho , aur qaada tak pahunch jao to tum mein sey (har) kisi ko sab sey pehley yun kehna chahiye : (التَّحِيَّاتُ الْمُبَارَكَاتُ الصَّلَوَاتُ الطَّيِّبَاتُ لِلَّهِ السَّلاَمُ عَلَيْكَ أَيُّهَا النَّبِىُّ وَرَحْمَةُ اللَّهِ وَبَرَكَاتُهُ السَّلاَمُ عَلَيْنَا وَعَلَى عِبَادِ اللَّهِ الصَّالِحِينَ أَشْهَدُ أَنْ لاَ إِلَهَ إِلاَّ اللَّهُ وَأَشْهَدُ أَنَّ مُحَمَّدًا عَبْدُهُ وَرَسُولُهُ) ''pakizah aadaab aur ibaadaten Allah hi key liye hain. aey Nabi ! aap par salamti ho aur Allah ki rehmat aur uski barkaten (nazil) hon, hum par bhi salamti ho, aur Allah key nek bandon par bhi. main gawahi deta hun ke Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin . aur main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur uskey Rasool hain. ye saat jumley namaz ka tahiya (التحیات) hain."
902,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamein tashahud is tarah sikhatey they jis tarah Quran ki koi sura sikhatey they. aur wo is tarah hai : (بِاسْمِ اللَّهِ وَبِاللَّهِ التَّحِيَّاتُ لِلَّهِ وَالصَّلَوَاتُ وَالطَّيِّبَاتُ لِلَّهِ السَّلاَمُ عَلَيْكَ أَيُّهَا النَّبِىُّ وَرَحْمَةُ اللَّهِ وَبَرَكَاتُهُ السَّلاَمُ عَلَيْنَا وَعَلَى عِبَادِ اللَّهِ الصَّالِحِينَ أَشْهَدُ أَنْ لاَ إِلَهَ إِلاَّ اللَّهُ وَأَشْهَدُ أَنَّ مُحَمَّدًا عَبْدُهُ وَرَسُولُهُ أَسْأَلُ اللَّهَ الْجَنَّةَ وَأَعُوذُ بِاللَّهِ مِنَ النَّارِ), 'Allah key naam sey , Allah ki tofiq sey, zabani ibaadaten Allah key liye hain badani ibaadaten aur maali ibaadaten Allah key liye hain. aey Nabi ! aap par salam ho aur Allah ki rehmat aur uski barkaten nazil hon. hum par aur Allah key nek bandon par salamti ho. main gawahi deta hun ke Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin aur main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur uskey Rasool hain. main Allah Taala sey jannat ka sawal karta hun aur jahannam sey Allah ki panah maangta hun.''"
903,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! hamein aap ko salam kehney ka tariqa to malum ho chuka hai lekin durood kaisey padhein? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kaho (اللهم صَلِّ عَلَى مُحَمَّدٍ عَبْدِكَ وَرَسُولِكَ كَمَا صَلَّيْتَ عَلَى إِبْرَاهِيمَ وَبَارِكْ عَلَى مُحَمَّدٍ وَعَلَى آلِ مُحَمَّدٍ كَمَا بَارَكْتَ عَلَى إِبْرَاهِيمَ), ''aey Allah ! apney bandey aur Rasool Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par rehmat nazil farma jis tarah tu ney Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) par rehmat nazil farmaai. aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki aal par barkat nazil farma jis tarah tu ney Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) par barkat nazil farmaai.,,"
904,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abi Leila (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney bayan kiya ke Hazrat Kaab bin Ajra (Raziallahu anhu) mujhey miley to farmaya : kya main tumhen eik tohfa na dun? (wo ye hai ke eik baar) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (ghar sey) bahar tashrif laye to hamney kaha : hum aap ko salam kehney ka tariqa to jantey hain, durood kaisey padhein? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kaho (اللَّهُمَّ صَلِّ عَلَى مُحَمَّدٍ وَعَلَى آلِ مُحَمَّدٍ كَمَا صَلَّيْتَ عَلَى إِبْرَاهِيمَ إِنَّكَ حَمِيدٌ مَجِيدٌ اللَّهُمَّ بَارِكْ عَلَى مُحَمَّدٍ وَعَلَى آلِ مُحَمَّدٍ كَمَا بَارَكْتَ عَلَى إِبْرَاهِيمَ إِنَّكَ حَمِيدٌ مَجِيدٌ), ''aey Allah ! Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki aal par rehmat nazil farma jis tarah tu ney Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) par rehmat nazil farmaai. to yaqinan qabile tareef aur buzurgiyon wala hai. aey Allah ! Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam)  ki aal par barkat nazil farma jis tarah tu ney Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) par barkat nazil farmaai. to yaqinan qabile tareef aur buzurgiyon wala hai.''"
905,"Hazrat Abu-Humed Saaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum ney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! hamein aap par durood padhney ka hukm diya gaya hai to hum aap par kis tarah durood padhein? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kaho (اللَّهُمَّ صَلِّ عَلَى مُحَمَّدٍ وَأَزْوَاجِهِ وَذُرِّيَّتِهِ كَمَا صَلَّيْتَ عَلَى إِبْرَاهِيمَ وَبَارِكْ عَلَى مُحَمَّدٍ وَأَزْوَاجِهِ وَذُرِّيَّتِهِ كَمَا بَارَكْتَ عَلَى آلِ إِبْرَاهِيمَ فِى الْعَالَمِينَ إِنَّكَ حَمِيدٌ مَجِيدٌ), ''aey Allah ! Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par, aap ki azwaje-mutahrat (paak biwiyon) par aur aap ki aulad par rehmat nazil farma jis tarah tu ney Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) par rehmat nazil farmaai aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par aap ki paak biwiyon par aur aap ki aulad par barkat nazil farma jis tarah tu ney jahano mein Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ki aal par barkat nazil farmaai. beshak to qabile tareef aur buzurgiyon wala hai.''"
906,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab tum Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par durood padho to durood ko muzayyan (behtar) karo, tumhen kya malum ke wo aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key samney pesh kiya jata ho, sathiyon ney kaha : hamen sikha dijiye (ke kis tarah muzayyan (behtar) kar key durood padhein) ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : yun kaho : (اللَّهُمَّ اجْعَلْ صَلاَتَكَ وَرَحْمَتَكَ وَبَرَكَاتِكَ عَلَى سَيِّدِ الْمُرْسَلِينَ وَإِمَامِ الْمُتَّقِينَ وَخَاتَمِ النَّبِيِّينَ مُحَمَّدٍ عَبْدِكَ وَرَسُولِكَ إِمَامِ الْخَيْرِ وَقَائِدِ الْخَيْرِ وَرَسُولِ الرَّحْمَةِ اللَّهُمَّ ابْعَثْهُ مَقَامًا مَحْمُودًا يَغْبِطُهُ بِهِ الأَوَّلُونَ وَالآخِرُونَ اللَّهُمَّ صَلِّ عَلَى مُحَمَّدٍ وَعَلَى آلِ مُحَمَّدٍ كَمَا صَلَّيْتَ عَلَى إِبْرَاهِيمَ وَعَلَى آلِ إِبْرَاهِيمَ إِنَّكَ حَمِيدٌ مَجِيدٌ اللَّهُمَّ بَارِكْ عَلَى مُحَمَّدٍ وَعَلَى آلِ مُحَمَّدٍ كَمَا بَارَكْتَ عَلَى إِبْرَاهِيمَ وَعَلَى آلِ إِبْرَاهِيمَ إِنَّكَ حَمِيدٌ مَجِيدٌ), ''aey Allah ! apney durood, rehmat aur barkaten nazil farma, Rasulon key sardar, muttaqeen key Imam, anbiya key khaatim (Hazrat) Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par jo terey bandey, terey Rasool, neki key Imam, neki key rehbar aur rehmat key Rasool hain. aey Allah ! unhen maqame Mehmood par faaiz farma jahan un par pehley aur pichhley (sab jin aur insan) rashk kerengey. aey Allah ! Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki aal par rehmat nazil farma jis tarah tu ney Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) par aur Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ki aal par rehmat nazil farmaai. be-shak to qabile tareef aur buzurgiyon wala hai. aey Allah ! Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki aal par barkat nazil farma jis tarah tu ney Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) par aur Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ki aal par barkat nazil farmaai. be-shak to qabila tareef aur buzurgiyon wala hai.''"
907,"Hazrat Aamir bin Rabeea (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo musalman mujh par durood padhta hai, farishtey us waqt tak uskey liye rehmat ki dua kartey rehtey hain jab tak wo mujh par durood padhta rehta hai. ab banda chahey ye amal kam karey ya ziyada kar ley (uski marzi hai)."
908,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney mujh par durood padhna bhulaa diya, wo jannat ka raasta bhool gaya."
909,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey koi shakhs jab aakhiri tashahud sey farigh ho jaey to usey chahiye ke chaar chizon sey Allah ki panah talab kerey. jahannam key azab sey, qabr key azab sey, zindagi aur maut key fitne sey aur Masih Dajjaal key fitne sey."
910,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aadmi sey farmaya : tum namaz mein kya padhtey ho?  usney kaha : main tashahud padhta hun, phir Allah sey jannat ka sawal karta hun aur jahannam sey uski panah maangta hun. qism hai Allah ki ! mujhey wo duayen to aati nahin jo aap aahista aahista padhtey rehtey hain ya jo Muaz Raziallahu anhu gungunaatey hain to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : hum bhi yehi kuchh gungunaatey hain."
911,"Hazrat Numer Khuzai (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko namaz mein daain raan par daayan haath rakhey huye aur apni ungli sey ishara kartey dekha."
912,"Hazrat Wayl bin Hajar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap ney angoothey aur darmiyan ki ungli sey halqa banaya aur uskey qarib ki ungli ( shahadat ki ungli) ko uthaya , aap tashahud mein uskey sath (ishara kartey huye) dua kar rahey they."
913,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab namaz mein bethtey to dono haath ghutnon par rakhtey aur daain haath ki angoothey key sath wali ungli uthatey, uskey sath dua kartey aur aap ney baayan haath apney ghutney par phela kar rakha huwa hota tha."
914,"Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood) (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) daain taraf aur baain taraf salam phertey they yahan tak key aap key rukhsaaron key safedi nazar aati .) aur farmatey : ( ( السَّلاَمُ عَلَيْكُمْ وَرَحْمَةُ اللَّهِ ) , tum par salamti ho aur Allah ki rehmat ho."
915,Hazrat Saad bin abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) daain aur baain janib salam pheraa kartey they.
916,"Hazrat Ammar bin Yasir (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) daain taraf aur baain taraf salam phertey they, yahan tak key aap key rukhsaaron ki safedi nazar aati aur farmatey : ( اَلسَّلاَمُ عَلَيْكُمْ وَرَحْمَةُ اللَّهِ . السَّلاَمُ عَلَيْكُمْ وَرَحْمَةُ اللَّهِ) 'tum par salamti ho aur Allah ki rehmat ho, tum par salamti ho aur Allah ki rehmat ho.'"
917,"Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jange-Jamal key moqey par Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney hamen aisi namaz padhaai ke hamen Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki namaz ki yad dila di, jisey hum faramosh kar chukey they ya (kotahi ki wajeh sey) chhod bethey they. (us namaz mein) unhoney daain taraf aur baain taraf salam pheraa ."
918,Hazrat Sehal bin Saad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney samney ki taraf eik hi salam pheraa .
919,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) samney ki taraf eik salam pheraa kartey they.
920,"Hazrat Salma bin Akwaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap ney namaz ada farmaai to eik hi salam pheraa ."
921,"Hazrat Samra bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab Imam salam kahey to usey (salam ka) jawab do ."
922,"Hazrat Samra bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen hukm diya ke hum apney imamon ko salam kahin aur hum eik doosrey ko salam kahin ."
923,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : koi banda namaz padhaaey to unhen (namaaziyon ko) chhod kar sirf apney liye dua na kerey. agar usney aisa kya to unki khayanat ki."
924,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab salam phertey they to (salam key baad) sirf itna arsa bethtey they ke ye dua padh letey ( اللَّهُمَّ أَنْتَ السَّلاَمُ وَمِنْكَ السَّلاَمُ تَبَارَكْتَ يَا ذَا الْجَلاَلِ وَالإِكْرَامِ ) 'aey Allah! to salamti wala hai aur tujhi sey salamti (hasil hoti) hai aey azmat o buzurgi waley! to bahut barkaton wala hai."
925,"Hazrat ummul-mominin Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab subh ki namaz sey salam phertey to farmatey they : ( اللَّهُمَّ إِنِّى أَسْأَلُكَ عِلْمًا نَافِعًا وَرِزْقًا طَيِّبًا وَعَمَلاً مُتَقَبَّلاً) 'aey Allah! main tujh sey faeyda deney waley ilm, pak rizq aur qubul honey waley amal ka sawal karta hun."
926,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : do chizon par jo shakhs bhi pabandi sey amal karta hai jannat mein dakhil ho jata hai aur wo cheezen ( kaam) aasan hain ( lekin) un par amal karney waley kam hain. har namaz key baad das dafa ( subhan Allah) kahey, das dafa (Allahu-akbar) kahey aur das dafa ( Alhamdulillah) kahey . Sahabi kehtey hain : mainey dekha ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney haath sey us adad ka ishara kya aur farmaya : ye zaban sey kehney mein (paanchon namazon key hisab sey) eik so pachas (kalmaat) hain aur (qiyamat key din nekiyon key) tarazu mein (eik neki ka ajr das guna key aetbar sey) eik hazar paanch so hongey . aur jab apney bistar par jaey to (subhan Allah) aur (Alhamdulillah) aur ( Allahu-akbar) (sab mila kar kul) so martaba keh ley , ye zaban sey kehney mein so hain aur tarazu mein (das guna key hisab sey) eik hazar. bhala tum mein sey kon hai jo din mein dhaai hazar gunah karta ho?, '( jabke nekiyan wo dhaai hazar kamata ho) Sahaba ney arz kya : insan pabandi sey ye dono amal kyon nahin kar sakta ? farmaya : eik aadmi namaz padh raha hota hai ke shetan aa jata hai aur usey kehta hai : falan baat yad kar , falan baat yad kar yahan tak key banda ( namaz sey) ghafil ho jata hai aur jab banda bistar par jata hai to shetan aa jata hai aur usey sulaney lagta hai yahan tak key aadmi ko neend aa jati hai.'"
927,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey arz kya gaya, eik riwayat key mutabiq Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ney khud kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! maal o dolat waley to ajr o sawab ley gaey (aur hum gharib peechey reh gaey) zaban sey ada ki janey wali ibadat jis tarah hum kartey hain, wo bhi kartey hain aur wo (apney maal Allah ki raah mein) kharch kartey hain aur hum (istataat na honey ki wajeh sey) kharch nahin kartey . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey farmaya : kya main tumhen aisa amal na bataun ke jab tum usey karogey to aagey nikal janey walon ko ja logey aur peechey reh janey waley tum tak na pahunch sakengey. har namaz key baad tentees-tentees aur chauntees baar (Alhamdulillah, subhan Allah) aur (Allahu-akbar) kaha karo. Imam Sufiyan bin Uena (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : mujhey malum nahin un mein sey kon sa kalma chauntees baar hai."
928,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab namaz sey farigh hotey to teen baar ( اسْتَغْفِرُ اللہَ ) kehtey , phir farmatey : ( اللَّهُمَّ أَنْتَ السَّلاَمُ وَمِنْكَ السَّلاَمُ تَبَارَكْتَ يَا ذَا الْجَلاَلِ وَالإِكْرَامِ ), aey Allah ! to salamti wala hai aur tujhi sey salamti (hasil hoti) hai. aey azmat o buzurgi waley ! to bahut barkaton wala hai.'"
929,"Hazrat Halab Taai (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamen namaz padhatey they to dono taraf sey phirtey they."
930,"Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood ( (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : koi shakhs apney kaam mein shetan ka hissa muqarrar na kar ley . (wo is tarah) ke sirf daain taraf sey ghumna Allah ka haq (aur apna farz) samajh ley . mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko aksar baain taraf sey ghoomtey dekha hai."
931,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko namaz sey (farigh ho kar) daain taraf mudte bhi dekha hai aur baain taraf bhi ."
932,"Hazrat ummul-mominin Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) salam phertey they to aap key salam phertey hi aurten uth khadi hoti thin. uskey baad Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uthney sey pehley kuch der apni jagah tashrif rakhtey they."
933,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab raat ka khana pesh kar diya jaey aur namaz ki iqaamat ho jaey to pehley khana kha lo ."
934,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab raat ka khana pesh kar diya jaey aur namaz khadi ho jaey to pehley khana kha lo . Imam Nafey Rahimahullah ney farmaya : eik raat Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhuma) ney khana khaya , halanke unhen iqaamat ki aawaz sunai dey rahi thi ."
935,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab khana ( samney) aa jaey aur namaz ki iqaamat ho jaey to pehley khana kha lo ."
936,"Hazrat abu-Mulaih Aamir (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : main eik barish wali raat mein (namaz key liye ghar sey) nikla . jab wapis aa kar darwaza khulwaya to walid sahab (Hazrat Usama bin Umer Hazli (Raziallahu anhu)) ney kaha : kon hai? mainey kaha : abu-Mulaih hun . farmaya : mainey to dekha hai ke hum log suleh Hudebiya key moqey par Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath they. (us doran mein halki si) barish ho gaee jis sey hamarey jooton key talwey bhi geeley na huye. (lekin) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key muazzan ney (Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key hukm sey) aelan kar diya ke , apney thikanon par) khemon mein) namaz padh lo ."
937,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka muazzan barish aur tez hawa wali sard raat mein aelan kar diya karta tha : gharon mein namaz padh lo."
938,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney barish waley din Jumey key roz farmaya : gharon mein namaz padh lo .
939,Hazrat Abdullah bin Haris bin naufal (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke) eik baar ( Juma key din Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) ney muazzan ko Azan kehney ka hukm diya . us din barish ho rahi thi . muazzan ney kaha : ( اللَّهُ أَكْبَرُ اللَّهُ أَكْبَرُ أَشْهَدُ أَنْ laa إِلَهَ إِلاَّ اللَّهُ أَشْهَدُ أَنَّ مُحَمَّدًا رَسُولُ اللَّهِ ) phir ( ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) ney muazzan sey) farmaya : logon mein aelan kar do ke gharon mein namaz padh lein .) ( muazzan ney صلو فی رحالکم  keh kar baqi Azan mukammal kar di ) logon ney unhen kaha : aap ney ye kya ( ajeeb kaam) kar diya ? unhoney farmaya : ye kaam to unhoney bhi kya tha jo mujh sey afzal they ( Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney isi tarah Azan kahlwaai thi ( kya aap mujh sey ye chahtey hain ke main logon ko gharon sey nikaalun aur wo ghutnon tak keechad mein dhanstey huye merey paas (namaz baa-jamaat ki adaegi key liye) ayen ?
940,"Hazrat Talha bin Ubedullah Temi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum namaz padh rahey they aur janwer hamarey samney sey guzar rahey they. ye baat Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein arz ki gaee to aap ney farmaya : kisi key samney kajawey ki pichli lakdi jitni chiz (sutrah key tor par) mojud ho to aagey sey guzarney wala usey koi nuqsan na dega ."
941,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : safar mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein barchhi pesh ki jati thi . aap usey ( zamin mein) gaad kar uski taraf munh kar key namaz padhtey they."
942,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki eik chataai thi, jisey din key waqt bicha diya jata tha aur raat key waqt aap usey aad bana kar uski taraf ( munh kar key) namaz padhtey they."
943,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi shakhs namaz padhey to chehrey key aagey koi chiz (sutrey key taur par) rakh ley, agar kuchh na miley to aasa gaad ley, agar wo bhi na miley to lakeer khinch ley, phir uskey aagey sey jo kuchh bhi guzar jaeyga, usey koi nuqsan na dega."
944,"Hazrat Basar bin Saeed (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : (kuchh afrad ney) mujhey Hazrat Zaid bin Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein namazi key aagey sey guzarney ka masla poochhney key liye bheja. unhoney mujhey bataya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : uskey aagey sey guzarney ki nisbat chaalis tak thehrey rehna behtar hai. Hazrat Sufiyan (bin Uena) (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : mujhey nahin malum ke hadees mein chaalis saal ka lafz hai ya (chaalis) mahiney ya din ya ghadiyaan."
945,"Hazrat Basar bin Saeed (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Zaid bin Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) ney Hazrat Abu Jaheem Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein pegham bheja (ke ye bataaiye) aap ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey namazi key aagey sey kisi key guzarney key barey mein kya suna hai? unhoney farmaya : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna hai, aap farmatey they : agar kisi ko malum ho jaey ke jab uska bhai namaz padh raha ho to us (namazi) key aagey sey guzarney ka kya gunah hai to chaalis. malum nahin chaalis saal farmaya, ya chaalis maah ya chaalis din. tak theherney ko behtar samjhey."
946,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar kisi ko malum ho ke apney bhai key samney sey eik taraf sey dusri taraf guzarney par, jabke wo namaz padh raha ho kitna gunah hai to wo apney uthaey huye eik qadam ki nisbat sau saal tak thehrey rehna behtar samjhey."
947,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) maidane Arafat mein namaz padh rahey they. main aur Fazal (Raziallahu anhu) eik gadhi par sawar ho kar aaye, aur hum saf key kuchh hissey key samney sey guzrey, phir hum us sey utrey aur usey chhod diya, phir hum saf mein shamil ho gaey."
948,"Hazrat Ummul-mominin Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney bayan farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) key hujrey mein namaz padh rahey they. aap key samney sey Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ya umr bin Abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhuma) guzarney lagey to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney haath (key isharey) sey roka, wo wapis palat gaey, phir Hazrat Zenab binte Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) guzarney lagin to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney haath sey isi tarah mana kya lekin wo guzar gaeen. jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) namaz sey farigh huye to farmaya : aurten ghalib aa jati hain."
949,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kaalaa kutta aur haiz wali (ya baligh) aurat namaz tod deti hain.
950,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aurat , kutta aur gadhaa namaz tod detey hain."
951,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aurat , kutta aur gadhaa namaz tod detey hain."
952,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab aadmi key samney kajawey ki pichhli lakdi jaisi koi chiz (sutrah key tor par) mojud na ho to aurat, gadhaa aur kaalaa kutta namaz tod detey hain. Hazrat Abdullah bin Samit (Rahimahullah) ney arz kiya : siyah aur surkh mein farq ki kya wajeh hai? Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : jis tarah tu ney mujh sey puchha hai, isi tarah mainey bhi Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey sawal kiya tha chunanche aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya tha : kaalaa kutta shetan hota hai."
953,"Hazrat Hasan Urfi Rahimahullah sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) ki majlis mein namaz todney wali chizon ki baat chali to haazirin ney kuttey, gadhey aur aurat ka zikr kiya. ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) ney farmaya : aap logon ka memney key barey mein kya khayal hai? eik din Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) namaz padh rahey they ke eik memna aap key samney sey guzarney laga to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jaldi sey qibley ki taraf aagey badh gaey."
954,Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi shakhs namaz padhey to usey chahiye ke sutrah (samney rakh kar us) ki taraf namaz padhey aur us sey qarib ho kar khada ho aur kisi ko samney sey guzarney na dey. agar koi guzarney lagey to us sey ladey kyonkey wo shetan hai.
955,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey koi shakhs jab namaz padh raha ho to usey chahiye ke kisi ko apney samney sey na guzarney dey. agar wo (guzarney wala peechhey hatney sey) inkar karey to us sey ladaai karey, kyonkey uskey sath eik sathi (shetan) hai.  Munkadri ney kaha : uskey sath Uzza hai."
956,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat ko namaz (tahajjud) ada kartey they aur main aap key samney qibley ki taraf is tarah leti hui hoti thi jis tarah janaza pada hota hai."
957,Hazrat Zenab binte Abu-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ney apni walida (Ummul-mominin Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat kartey huye farmaya ke un (Ummul-mominin (Raziallahu anha)) ka bistar Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sajde key maqam key barabar hota tha.
958,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja mohtarma (biwi) Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) namaz padhtey they aur main aap key barabar (leti) hoti thi. jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sajda kartey to baaz oqaat mujhey aap ka kapda chju jata."
959,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney baaten karney waley aur soey huye key peechhey namaz padhney sey mana farmaya."
960,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamein taalim detey they ke hum rukoo aur sajdey mein Imam sey jaldi na karen. (aur farmatey they ke) jab wo takbir kahey to tum takbir (Allahu-Akbar) kaho aur jab wo sajda karey tab tum sajda karo."
961,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Imam sey pehley sar uthata hai, kya usey is baat sey khof nahin aata ke Allah Taala uskey sar ko gadhey ka sar bana dey?"
962,"Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mera badan bhari ho gaya hai to jab main rukoo karun tab rukoo kiya karo, jab main sar uthaun tab tum sar uthaoo, aur jab main sajda karun tab tum sajda karo. main kisi aadmi ko hergiz aisa kartey na dekhun ke wo mujh sey pehley rukoo ya sajda mein chala jaey."
963,"Hazrat Muawiya bin Abu-Sufiyaan (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujh sey pehley rukoo ya sajda na karo. main rukoo kartey waqt tum sey jis qadr bhi aagey hunga, jab main rukoo sey sar uthaaoonga to tum mujh sey mil jaogey, aur sajda kartey waqt main tum sey jitna bhi aagey hunga, jab main (sajdey sey) sar uthaaoonga to tum mujh sey mil jaogey. mera badan bhari ho gaya hai."
964,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye jihalat ki baat hai ke aadmi namaz sey farigh honey sey pehley bar-bar peshani par haath phertaa rahey."
965,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : namaz mein ungliyan mat chatkhaao."
966,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney is baat sey mana farmaya hai ke aadmi namaz key doran mein munh dhank ley."
967,"Hazrat Kaab bin Ajra (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aadmi ko namaz key doran mein ungliyon mein ungliyan daley dekha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney us (key dono haathon) ki ungliyon ko alag alag kar diya."
968,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab kisi ko jamaai aaye to usey chahiye ke munh par haath rakh ley aur aawaz na nikaley kyonkey shetan is sey hanstaa hai."
969,"Hazrat Adi bin Sabit Ansari apney walid sey aur wo Adi key nana (Hazrat Abdullah bin Yazeed bin Zaid Khutmi Ansari (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat kartey hain. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : namaz mein thooknaa, naak saaf karna, haiz aa jana aur ungh aana shetan ki taraf sey hai."
970,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : teen aadmiyon ki namaz qubul nahin hoti : eik wo shakhs jo logon ka Imam bin jaey halanke wo usey na pasand kartey hun, aur wo shakhs jo waqt guzar janey key baad hi namaz key liye aata hai aur wo shakhs jo kisi azad ko ghulam bana ley."
971,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : teen aadmiyon ki namaz unkey saron sey eik baalisht bhi buland nahin hoti, wo aadmi jo logon ka Imam bin jaey halanke wo usey na pasand kartey hon. wo aurat jiski raat us haal mein guzrey ke uska khawind us sey naraz ho aur wo do bhai jo eik doosrey qata talluq kiye huye hon."
972,"Hazrat abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : do ya do sey zyada afrad jamaat hain.'"
973,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main eik raat apni khaala (ummul-mominin) Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) key yahan thehra. raat ko Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) namaz (tahajjud) ada karney key liye khadey huye. main aapki baain taraf ja khada huwa . aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mera haath pakad kar mujhey daain taraf khada kar liya."
974,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) maghrib ki namaz padh rahey they. mein aa kar aap ki baain taraf khada ho gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey daain taraf khada kar liya ."
975,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apney ghar walon mein sey eik khatoon ko aur mujhey namaz padhaai to mujhey apni daain taraf khada kya aur khatoon ney hamarey peechey (khadey ho kar) namaz padhi."
976,"Hazrat abu-Masood Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) namaz key waqt hamarey kandhon ko haath laga kar farmatey they : aagey peechey mat hona warna tumharey dilon mein ikhtilaf pad jaeyga. merey qarib tumharey aql mand aur samajhdaar afrad khadey hon, phir jo un sey (Umar key lihaz sey) qarib tar hon, phir jo un sey qarib tar hon."
977,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye baat pasand thi ke Muhajir aur ansar aap key qarib (agli safon mein) khadey hon. taake aap sey (namaz key masaayel amali tor par) seekh saken."
978,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apney (kuch) Sahaba ko peechey rehtey dekha to farmaya : aagey badho aur meri iqtida (pairvi) karo, tumharey baad waley tumhari iqtida karen. kuch log peechey rehney key aadi ho jatey hain yahan tak key Allah Taala unhen peechey rehney deta hai.'"
979,"Hazrat Malik bin Huweris (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main aur mera eik sathi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye. jab hamney wapis (watan) janey ka irada kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hum sey farmaya : jab namaz ka waqt ho jaey to tum log Azan aur iqaamat kehna aur tumhara Imam wo baney jo tum dono mein sey ziyada bada hai."
980,"Hazrat abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : logon ko wo aadmi namaz padhaaey jo Allah ki kitab (Quran majeed) ziyada padha huwa ho. agar wo qirat mein barabar hon to phir wo shakhs Imam baney jisney hijrat (doosron sey) pehley ki ho. agar hijrat bhi ikhattey ki ho to wo shakhs namaz padhaaey jo un mein sey umr mein bada ho, aur koi shakhs kisi key ghar mein ya uskey daeyrae-iqtidar mein imaamat na karwaaey aur uskey ghar mein uski ijazat key baghair uski makhsus nashist gaah par na bethey ."
981,"Hazrat abu-Haazim (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Sehal bin Saad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) apney qabiley key nojawanon ko aagey badhatey they ke logon ko namaz padhaein . un sey arz kya gaya, aap aisa kyon kartey hain halanke aap ko qadimul-Islam Sahabi honey ka sharf hasil hai? unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna hai, aap ney farmaya : Imam zimmey-daar hai. agar achey tareeqey sey namaz padhaaey to usey bhi sawab hoga aur muqtadiyon ko bhi sawab hoga, aur agar usney ghalati ki to wo gunah gaarhoga, muqtadi gunah gaar nahin hongey."
982,"Hazrat khadsha (Raziallahu anhu) ki behan Hazrat Salama binte Hur (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye irshad Mubarak suna hai : logon par aisa zamana bhi aayega ke wo eik ghadi khadey huye (eik doosrey ko imaamat key liye dhakelengey) unhen koi Imam nahin milega jo namaz padha sakey."
983,"Hazrat abu-Ali Hamdani (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke wo eik kashti mein safar par rawana huye. kashti mein Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir Johni (Raziallahu anhu) bhi mojud they. (safar key doran mein) namaz ka waqt ho gaya, hamney un sey darkhaast ki ke namaz padha den aur ham ney un sey arz kya : aap us (imaamat) ka ziyada haq rakhtey hain kyonkey aap Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key Sabab hain, unhoney inkar kar diya aur farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye irshad Mubarak suna hai : jo shakhs logon ka Imam baney aur sahih tareeqey sey namaz padhaaey to usey bhi namaz ka sawab milega aur in ko bhi. aur agar usney namaz mein koi kotahi (aur ghalati) ki to usey gunah hoga, unhen nahin."
984,"Hazrat abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kya : Allah key Rasool! main to falan sahab ki wajah sey Fajr ki namaz sey peechey reh jata hun kyonkey wo bahut lambi namaz padhatey hain. Hazrat abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jis qadr us din ghazab naak huye, mainey kisi waaz key doran mein aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko is qadr jalal ki keyfiyat mein nahin dekha. (aap ney us waaz key doran mein) farmaya : aey logo! tum mein sey kuch log (muqtadiyon ko) mutnaffar kar detey hain. jo shakhs logon ko namaz padhaaey, usey chahiye ke ikhtisaar sey kaam ley kyonkey un mein kamzor bhi hotey hain, boodhey bhi aur zarurat mand bhi."
985,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mukhtasar aur kamil namaz padhatey they.'"
986,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ney apney sathiyon (muqtadiyon) ko Isha ki namaz padhaai to bahut lambi kar di. hamarey qabiley key eik aadmi ney jamaat sey alag ho kar (akeley) namaz padh li. Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye ittila mili to unhoney farmaya : wo munafiq hai. (kyonkey usney jaan-bujh kar namaz ba-jamaat tarak ki hai) us aadmi ko ye khabar mili to wo Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur jo baat Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ney kahi thi, wo aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key gosh-guzar ki. (baad mein jab Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) hazir huye to) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Muaz! tum logon ko aazmaaish mein dalna chahtey ho? jab tum logon ko namaz padhao to (aisi suraten padha karo) : ( وَالشَّمْسِ وَضُحٰىهَا - سَبِّحِ اسْمَ رَبِّكَ الْاَعْلَى - وَالَّيْلِ اِذَا يَغْشٰى - اِقْراْ بِاسْمِ رَبِّكَ )"
987,"Hazrat Usman bin abi al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mujhey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney aakhiri nasihat us waqt ki, jab mujhey Taaif ka ameer (governer) muqarrar kya. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey farmaya : Usman ! namaz mukhtasar padhaya karna aur kamzor afrad ki munaasibat sey logon (ki quwate-bardasht) ka andaza karna kyonkey un mein boodhey, bachey, bimar door sey aaney waley aur zarurat mand (sab tarah key log) hotey hain.'"
988,"Hazrat Usman bin abi al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mujh sey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney aakhiri baat ye farmaai : jab to logon ka Imam baney to un par takhfeef karna (namaz halki padhaana.)"
989,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main namaz shuru karta hun aur mera irada lambi namaz padhaaney ka hota hai, phir mujhey kisi bachey key roney ki aawaz aati hai to namaz mukhtasar kar deta hun kyonkey mujhey malum hai ke uskey roney sey uski maa pareshan hogi ."
990,"Hazrat Usman bin abi al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey bachey key roney ki aawaz aati hai to main namaz mein ikhtisaar kar deta hun ."
991,"Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main namaz mein khada hota hun aur mera irada usey lamba karney ka hota hai, phir mujhey kisi bachey key roney ki aawaz aa jati hai to main namaz mukhtasar kar deta hun kyonkey mujhey ye baat pasand nahin ke bachey ki maa ko pareshani ho.'"
992,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samra Sawai (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ( Sahaba kiram sey) farmaya : tum is tarah safein kyon nahin banatey jis tarah farishtey apney rab key huzur safein banatey hain? Raavi kehtey hain, hamney arz kya : farishtey apney rab key huzur kis tarah saf bandi kartey hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agli safon ko mukammal kartey hain aur saf main eik doosrey key sath mil kar khadey hotey hain.'"
993,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : apni safein durust karo kyonkey safein durust karna namaz ki takmil mein shamil hai.'"
994,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) saf ko (intehai ehtimam sey) sidha kartey they yahan tak key neze ya teer ki tarah (sidhi) kar detey. (eik baar) aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aadmi ka Sina (saf sey) aagey badha huwa dekha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : apni safein sidhi karo warna Allah Taala zarur tumharey darmiyan ikhtilaf paida kar dega ."
995,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala un logon par rehmat nazil karta hai aur farishtey unkey liye duaaey-khair kartey hain jo safon ko milaate hain aur jo shakhs saf ka shigaaf pur kerega, uskey badley Allah Taala uska darja buland kar dega."
996,Hazrat Arbaz bin Saariya (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) agli saf walon key liye teen baar duaaey-maghfirat farmatey they aur dusri saf key liye eik baar.
997,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna hai ke aap ney farmaya : Allah Taala pehli saf par rehmat nazil farmata hai aur farishtey uskey liye duaaey khair kartey hain."
998,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar logon ko malum hota ke pehli saf mein kya kuch ( ajr o sawab aur rehmat o barkat) hai to qura andazi hoti."
999,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : beshak Allah Taala pehli saf par rehmat nazil farmata hai aur farishtey uskey liye duaaey khair kartey hain.'"
1000,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aurton ki behtareen safein aakhiri hain. aur sab sey nikammi ( kam sawab wali) safein pehli hain. aur mardon ki behtareen safein pehli hain aur sab sey nikammi safein aakhiri hain."
1001,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mardon ki behtareen safein aagey wali hain, aur (un ki) sab sey nikammi safein peechey wali hain, aur aurton ki behtareen safein peechey wali hain aur (un ki) sab sey nikammi (aur kam sawab wali) safein aagey wali hain."
1002,"Hazrat Muawiya bin Qurra apney walid (Hazrat Qurra bin Ayas Muzni (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat kartey hain, unhoney farmaya : hamen Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein sutonon key darmiyan saf bananey sey mana kya jata tha aur us sey sakhti key sath roka jata tha."
1003,"Hazrat Ali bin Sheban (Raziallahu anhu) jo eik wafad mein shamil ho kar tashrif laye they, un sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum (apney ilaqey sey) rawana huye (aur Madina Munawra tak safar kya) yahan tak key hum Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmate-aqdas mein hazir ho gaey aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki baiat ki. hamney aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki iqtida mein namaz ada ki, phir aap key peechey eik aur namaz padhi. aap ney namaz mukammal ki to dekha ke eik aadmi saf key peechey akela khada namaz padh raha hai. ( jab wo shakhs namaz sey farigh huwa to) Allah key Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey paas gaey aur farmaya : shuru sey namaz padho. saf key peechey (akeley) khadey honey waley ki koi namaz nahin."
1004,"Hazrat Wabsa bin Maabad (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik aadmi ney saf key peechey akeley khadey ho kar namaz padhi to Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam ney isey namaz dobara padhney ka hukm diya ."
1005,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : beshak Allah Taala safon ki daain Janab par rahmatein nazil karta hai aur farishtey uskey liye duaaey khair kartey hain."
1006,"Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key peechey namaz padhtey they to hamen, ya farmaya : mujhey, ye baat pasand thi ke hum daain taraf khadey hon."
1007,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey arz kya gaya : masjid ki baain janib to bilkul khaali ho gaee . (log sawab ki niyat sey daain taraf khadey hotey hain) to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney masjid ki baain janib ko abad kya usey dugna sawab milega ."
1008,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab tawafe-kaaba sey farigh huye to Maqame-Ibrahim key paas tashrif laye . Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool ! ye hamarey Jadde-Amjad Hazrat Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ka wo maqam hai jis key barey mein Allah Taala ney farmaya hai : ( وَاتَّخِذُوْا مِنْ مَّقَامِ اِبْرٰهیمَ مُصَلًّى padhi. )' tum Maqame-Ibrahim ko namaz ki jagah muqarrar kar lo . Waleed bin Muslim (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Imam Malik (Rahimahullah) sey puchha : kya unhoney ye lafz isi tarah padha tha. (وَاتَّخِذُوْا مِنْ مَّقَامِ اِبْرٰهیمَ مُصَلًّى)? unhoney farmaya : haan."
1009,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mainey arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool ! kaash! ! aap Maqame-Ibrahim key qarib namaz padhein , to ye aayat nazil hui : ( وَاتَّخِذُوْا مِنْ مَّقَامِ اِبْرٰهٖمَ مُصَلًّى padhi. )' tum Maqame-Ibrahim ko namaz ki jagah muqarrar kar lo ."
1010,"Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath atthara mahiney tak baitul-Maqdis ki taraf munh kar key namazein ada kin, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key Madina tashrif laney key do maah baad Kaba ko qibla muqarrar kar diya gaya tha. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab baitul-Maqdis ki taraf munh kar key namaz padhtey they to aksar aasman ki taraf chehra Mubarak uthatey. Allah Taala ko apney Nabi key dil ki keyfiyat malum thi ke wo Kaba shareef (ko qibla bananey) ki khahish rakhtey hain. Jibril (Alaihissalam) (aasman ki taraf) buland huye to jab wo aasman aur zamin key darmiyan buland hotey ja rahey they to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ye malum karney ki khahish rakhtey they ke Jibril (Alaihissalam) kya wahi ley kar nazil hongey. (aakhir kaar) Allah Taala ney ye aayat nazil farma di : ( قَدْ نَرٰى تَـقَلُّبَ وَجْهِكَ فِي السَّمَآءِ . . . الایۃ ) , hum aap key chehrey ko bar-bar aasman ki taraf uthtey huye dekhtey hain. . hamarey paas eik aadmi aaya , usney kaha : qibla (baitul-Maqdis sey) Kaba ki taraf muntaqil ho gaya hai. hamney do rakatein baitul-Maqdis ki taraf munh kar key ada ki thin (aur abhi namaz mukammal nahin hui thi) hum rukoo mein they (jab ye khabar mili) hamney (fauran) rukh pher liya aur jo namaz padhi ja chuki thi, is par baqi namaz ki bina kar li to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey Jibril! hamari baitul-Maqdis ki taraf munh kar key padhi hui namazon ka kya haal hoga? to Allah Taala ney ye aayat nazil farma di : ( وَمَا كَانَ اللَّهُ لِيُضِيعَ إِيمَانَكُمْ )' Allah Taala tumharey eman (tumhaari namaazein) zaya nahin kerega."
1011,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mashriq aur maghrib key darmiyan qibla hai."
1012,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi shakhs masjid mein dakhil ho to do rakat namaz padhey baghair na bethey."
1013,"Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi shakhs masjid mein dakhil ho to usey chahiye ke bethney sey pehley do rakat namaz padh ley."
1014,"Hazrat Maadaan bin abu-Talha Yaamari (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) Juma key din khutba deney khadey huye. ya farmaya ke unhoney Juma key din khutba diya. aap ney Allah Taala ki hamd o Sana key baad farmaya : logo! tum do paudey khatey ho, jinhen mein bura hi samajhta hun, yani ye lehsun aur ye piyaz. main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein dekha karta tha ke agar kisi (key munh) sey us (lahsun ya piyaz) ki bo mehsus ki jati to usey haath sey pakad kar (masjid sey bahir) baqee ki taraf nikal diya jata, isliye jo shakhs unhen khana chahey, usey chahiye ke pakka kar un ki bo khatam kar ley."
1015,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney ye pauda, yani lahsun khaya ho to wo hamari masjid mein uski bo key sath hamen eza (takleef) na pahunchaey. (Imam Zohri key shagrid) Ibrahim bin Saad ney farmaya : merey walid Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki is hadees mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey, Gendna aur piyaz, key alfaz ka izafa farmatey they."
1016,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney us paudey mein sey kuch khaya ho, wo masjid mein hergiz na aaye."
1017,Hazrat Zaid bin Aslam (Rahimahullah) ney Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat ki ke unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) masjide-Quba mein namaz ada karney key liye tashrif laye . mutaaddid Ansari hazraat hazir ho kar Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko salam arz karney lagey . Zaid bin Aslam (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : mainey Hazrat Suheb (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (us moqey par) salam ka jawab kis tarah detey they? unhoney farmaya : haath sey ishara kartey they.
1018,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mujhey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney kisi kaam sey bheja. jab main (wapis) khidmat aqdas mein hazir huwa to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) namaz padh rahey they. mainey salam kya to aap ney ishara kya, (aur isharay sey jawab diya) jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ( namaz sey) farigh huye to mujhey bulaya aur farmaya : abhi abhi tum ney mujhey salam kya tha aur main namaz padh raha tha. ( isliye zaban sey jawab nahin dey saka .)"
1019,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum namaz mein (eik doosrey ko) salam kar liya kartey they. phir hamen farmaya gaya : namaz mein masroofiyat hoti hai."
1020,"Hazrat Rabeea (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum eik safar mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath they ke aasman par badal chha gaey aur qibley ki samt malum na ho saki. hamney (andazey sey) namaz padhi aur (zameen par) nishan laga liye. jab suraj tulu huwa to malum huwa ke hamney qibley key siwa (kisi aur taraf) namaz padhi hai. hamney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye waqia bayan kya to Allah Taala ney ye aayat mubaraka nazil farma di : ( فَأَيْنَمَا تُوَلُّوا فَثَمَّ وَجْهُ اللَّهِ )' tum jidhar bhi rukh karo, udhar hi Allah ka chehra hai.'"
1021,"Hazrat Tariq bin Abdullah Maharibi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab to namaz padh raha ho to apney samney hergiz na thookna, na daain taraf thookna, albatta baain taraf ya qadam key nichey thook saktey ho."
1022,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko masjid ki qibley wali deewar par balgham laga huwa nazar aaya . aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) logon ki taraf mutawajjeh huye aur farmaya : tumhen kya ho gaya hai ke eik aadmi rab ki taraf mutawajjeh ho kar khada hota hai, phir apney samney balgham thook deta hai? kya tum mein sey kisi ko ye baat pasand hai ke uskey samney aa kar uskey chehrey par thook diya jaey ? jab kisi ko thookna ho to apni baain taraf thook ley ya apney kapdey mein is tarah kar ley .) Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) key ustaad Hazrat abu-Bakar bin abi sheeba ney farmaya : (Imam Ismail ibn aleh (Rahimahullah) ney is hadees ki wazahat kartey huye mujhey yun kar key dikhaya ke) kapdey mein thookaa, phir kapdey ko mal diya ."
1023,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Hazrat Shabas bin Rabai (Rahimahullah) ko samney ki taraf thooktey dekh kar farmaya : aey Shabas! apney samney mat thooka karo, kyonkey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aisa karney sey mana farmaya kartey they aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya hai : jab aadmi namaz mein khada hota hai to Allah Taala apna Chehrey Mubarak uski taraf mutawajjeh farma deta hai yahan tak key wo namaz sey farigh ho jaey ya koi bura kaam kerey."
1024,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney namaz key doran mein kapdey mein thooka, phir usey mal diya."
1025,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney kankariyon ko haath lagaya, usney fuzul kaam kya."
1026,Hazrat Mueqeeb (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney namaz key doran mein kankariyon par haath pherney key barey mein farmaya : agar tumney zarur ye kaam karna ho to eik baar kar lo.
1027,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi shakhs namaz padhney khada hota hai to rehmate-Ilaahi uski taraf mutawajjeh hoti hai, isliye usey chahiye ke (dorane-namaz mein) kankariyon par haath na pherey."
1028,"ummul-mominin Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) chhoti chataai par namaz ada farmatey they."
1029,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney chataai par namaz ada farmaai ."
1030,"Hazrat Amr bin Dinar Rahimahullah sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) ney Basra mein apney bichhoney par namaz padhi , phir apney sathiyon ko bataya ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bhi apney bichhoney par namaz padh liya kartey they."
1031,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey yahan tashrif laye aur Banu Abdul-Ashhal ki masjid mein hamen namaz padhaai, mainey aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko sajdey key doran mein dono haath kapdey par rakhey huye dekha."
1032,"Hazrat Sabit bin Samit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney qabila Banu Abdul-Ash'hal key mohalley (ki masjid) mein namaz ada farmaai aur aap ney eik chadar odh rakhi thi, kankariyon ki thandak sey bachney key liye (sajda kartey waqt) is par haath rakh letey they."
1033,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log sakht garmi mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki iqtida (pairvi) mein namaz padhtey they. jab koi zamin par apni peshani na rakh sakta to apna kapda bicha kar is par sajda kar leta ."
1034,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Subhan Allah kehna mardon key liye hai aur taali bajana aurton key liye hai."
1035,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : subhan Allah kehna mardon ka kaam hai aur taali bajana aurton ka kaam hai."
1036,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney aurton ko taali bajaney ki ijazat di hai, aur mardon ko subhan Allah kehney ki."
1037,"Hazrat ibne-Abi Aus (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : merey dada Hazrat Aus (Raziallahu anhu) baaz oqaat namaz padh rahey hotey to namaz key doran hi mein mujhey ishara kartey to main unhen jootay dey deta. wo farmaya kartey they : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko jootay pehan kar namaz ada kartey dekha hai."
1038,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib (Rahimahullah) apney walid sey aur wo apney dada Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat kartey hain, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko jootay utaar kar namaz padhtey dekha hai, aur jootay pehan kar bhi ."
1039,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko jootey aur mozey pehan kar namaz padhtey dekha hai."
1040,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey hukm diya gaya hai ke main baal ya kapdey na sametun."
1041,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamen hukm diya gaya hai ke hum ( namaz mein) baal ya kapdey na sametein, aur) napak jagah par paon pad janey ki wajeh sey wuzu na karen ."
1042,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key azad karda ghulam Hazrat abu-Raafey (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Hazrat Hasan bin Ali (Raziallahu anhuma) ko baalon ka joda baandh kar namaz padhtey dekha to unkey baal khol diye ya is tarah karney sey mana farmaya , aur kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney is baat sey mana farmaya hai ke koi mard baalon ka juda baandh kar namaz padhey ."
1043,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aasman ki taraf nazren na uthao, kahin esa na ho ki uchak li jaeyn. yani namaz mein ooper nazar na uthao ."
1044,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik din Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Sahaba kiram ko namaz padhaai, jab namaz sey farigh huye to chehra Mubarak namaaziyon ki taraf kya aur farmaya : logon ko kya ho gaya hai ke aasman ki taraf nazren uthatey hain? phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney is barey mein sakht alfaz farmaaey : unhen is harkat sey baaz aa jana chahiye warna Allah zarur unki beenai salb farma lega."
1045,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo log (namaz mein) aasman ki taraf nazren uthatey hain, unhen zarur baaz aa jana chahiye warna un ki nazren wapis (zameen ki taraf) nahin lotengi (balke chin li jaeyngi.)"
1046,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik intehai khush shakal khatoon Nabi (Alaihissalam) ki iqtida (pairvi) mein namaz ada kya karti thin . kuch hazraat isliye agli saf mein khadey honey ka ehtimam kartey ke us khatoon par nazar na padey jabke baaz afrad (jaan bojh kar) peechey reh jatey taake pichli saf mein khadey hon. un mein sey jab koi rukoo karta to apni baghlon key nichey sey is tarah dekhta is par Allah Taala ney uskey barey mein ye aayaat nazil farmaain : ( وَلَقَدْ عَلِمْنَا الْمُسْتَقْدِمِينَ مِنْكُمْ وَلَقَدْ عَلِمْنَا الْمُسْتَأْخِرِينَ )' tum mein sey jo log aagey badhney waley hain, hum unhen bhi jantey hain aur jo peechey rehney waley hain wo bhi hamen malum hain."
1047,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool ! agar koi shakhs eik kapdey mein namaz padh ley (to kya hukm hai?) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya har kisi ko do kapdey muyassar hotey hain?"
1048,Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke wo Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik kapda tawashshoh key andaz sey odh kar namaz padh rahey they.
1049,"Hazrat umr bin Abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko eik kapda odh kar namaz padhtey dekha, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney isey tawashshoh key andaz sey odh rakha tha aur uskey dono sirey aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key kandhon par they."
1050,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Kaisan Rahimahullah apney walid (Hazrat Kaisan bin Jareer (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat kartey hain, unhoney farmaya : mainey Uliya kueyn key maqam par Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko eik kapdey mein namaz padhtey dekha ."
1051,"Hazrat Kaisan (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko eik kapda seeney par gireh dey kar Zohar aur Asr ki namazein padhtey dekha ."
1052,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab Adam (Alaihissalam) ka beta sajdey ki aayat padh kar sajda karta hai to shetan eik taraf ho kar roney lagta hai. wo kehta hai : haaye afsos ! Adam (Alaihissalam) key betey ko sajdey ka hukm huwa, usney sajda kar liya to uskey liye jannat hai aur mujhey sajdey ka hukm huwa tha, mainey (sajda karney sey) inkar kar diya to merey liye jahannam hai."
1053,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir tha ke eik sahab aaye aur arz kya : mainey raat ko khuwab dekha goya main eik darkht ki taraf (munh kar key, aey sutarah bana kar) namaz padh raha hun. mainey (namaz mein) sajdey ki aayat padhi to sajda kya. mujhey sajda kartey dekh kar darkht ney bhi sajda kya. mainey us ( darkht) ko (sajdey mein) yun kehtey suna : ( اللَّهُمَّ احْطُطْ عَنِّى بِهَا وِزْرًا وَاكْتُبْ لِى بِهَا أَجْرًا وَاجْعَلْهَا لِى عِنْدَكَ ذُخْرًا ) 'aey Allah ! is sajdey ki wajeh sey merey gunahon ka bojh utaar dey aur merey liye iska sawab likh dey aur isey apney paas merey liye zakhira bana dey. Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) ney farmaya : mainey (uskey baad) dekha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney sajda ki aayat padhi to sajda kya. mainey aap ko sajdey mein wohi dua padhtey suna jo un sahab ney (khuwab mein) darkht ki kahi hui bayan ki thi ."
1054,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab sajda kartey they to kehtey they : ( اللَّهُمَّ لَكَ سَجَدْتُ وَبِكَ آمَنْتُ وَلَكَ أَسْلَمْتُ أَنْتَ رَبِّى سَجَدَ وَجْهِى لِلَّذِى شَقَّ سَمْعَهُ وَبَصَرَهُ تَبَارَكَ اللَّهُ أَحْسَنُ الْخَالِقِينَ ) 'aey Allah! mainey terey liye sajda kya, tujh par eman laya, teri itaat qubul ki, to mera Malik hai, merey chehrey ney uskey liye sajda kya jisney uskey kaan aur uski aankhen banaeyn, Allah bahut barkaton wala hai. behtareen paida karney wala hai.'"
1055,Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath giyara sajdey kiye. un mein sey eik Sura Najm mein hai.
1056,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath giyara sajdey kiye un mein mufassal Suraton mein koi sajda nahin .) ye sajdey un Suraton mein hain ( Sura aeraf , Sura Raad , Sura nahal , Sura Bani-Israel, Sura Maryam , Sura Haj , aur Sura furqan ka sajda aur Sura Naml ka Hazrat Suleman (Alaihissalam) key waqiey wala sajda . Sura Sajda , Sura Suad aur Ha-Mim wali sura ka sajda (Sura Ha-Mim Sajda.)"
1057,Hazrat Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen pandarah sajdey padhaaey jin mein teen mufassal Suraton mein hain aur Sura Haj mein do sajdey hain.
1058,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath Sura ( إِذَا السَّمَاءُ انْشَقَّتْ ) aur sura ( إِقْرَاْ بِاسْمِ رَبِّکَ ) main sajdae-tilawat kya."
1059,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Sura ( إِذَا السَّمَاءُ انْشَقَّتْ ) main sajda kya . Imam abu-Bakar bin abi sheeba ney kaha ke ye hadees Yahya bin Saeed ki hadees hi hai, unkey ilawa mainey kisi ko usey bayan kartey nahin suna ."
1060,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi masjid mein dakhil huwa aur namaz padhi. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) masjid main eik taraf bethey they. usney (namaz key baad) aa kar aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko salam arz kiya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : W'alaikum-Assalaam, dobara ja kar namaz padh, tu ney namaz nahin padhi. usney wapis (apni jagah) ja kar phir namaz padhi, phir aa kar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko salam arz kiya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : W'alaikum-Assalaam, ja kar namaz padh, tu ney abhi namaz nahin padhi. teesri baar us aadmi ney arz kiya, aey Allah key Rasool mujhey namaz padhney ka tariqa sikha dijiye. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab to namaz key liye janey lagey to (pehley) sanwaar kar kamil wuzu kar, phir qibley ki taraf munh kar key Allahu-Akbar keh, phir Quran mein sey jo terey liye aasan ho padh, phir rukoo kar yahan tak key itminan sey rukoo kar ley, phir sar utha yahan tak key itminaan sey khada ho jaey phir sajda kar yahan tak key itminan sey sajda kar ley, phir sar utha yahan tak key itminan sey beth jaaey, phir sari namaz isi tareeqey sey ada kar."
1061,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Amr bin Ata (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Hazrat Abu-Humed Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) ko das Sahaba ki mojudgi mein ye kehtey suna. un das hazraat mein sey eik Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) hain. Abu-Humed (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki namaz ko tum sab sey ziyada janta hun. deegar Sahaba ney kaha : aisey kyon kar ho sakta hai, jabke aap hum sey ziyada Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki perwi karney waley nahin. (hum bhi to har chhotey badey masley mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki puri puri ittiba karney ki koshish kartey hain) na tumhen hum sey pehley Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki hum nasheeni ka sharf hasil huwa. Abu-Humed (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : ji haan. (iskey bawajud baat yehi hai) un hazraat ney kaha : tab bayan kijiye. unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab namaz key liye khadey hotey to takbir kehtey they, phir apney dono haath itney buland kartey ke kandhon key barabar utha letey aur (haath baandh kar khadey hotey to) aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka har uzu apney apney maqam par thehar jata (bila zarurat harkat na kartey), phir qirat kartey, phir Allahu-Akbar kehtey aur apney haath buland kartey yahan tak key kandhon key barabar utha letey, phir rukoo kartey aur apney haath ghutnon par mazbooti sey rakhtey (rukoo key doran mein) na apna sar bahut ziyada jhuka detey aur na buland rakhtey (balke) aetidaal sey rukoo kartey. phir ( سَمِعَ اللہُ لِمَنْ حَمِدَہ ) kehtey aur apney haath uthatey yahan tak key unhen kandhon key barabar buland kar letey, (aur sidhey khadey ho jatey) yahan tak key har haddi apni jagah thehar jati, phir zamin ki taraf jhuktey aur (sajdey key doran mein) apney haathon ko pahluon sey juda rakhtey, phir sar uthatey aur apney baain paon ko mod kar is par beth jatey jab sajda kartey to paon ki ungliyon ko zamin par lagatey, phir sajda kartey, phir Allahu-Akbar keh kar apney baain paon par beth jatey yahan tak key har haddi apni jagah par aa jati, phir khadey hotey aur dusri rakat mein bhi isi tarah (tamam arkaan ada) kartey, phir jab do rakatein padh kar (teesri rakat key liye) khadey hotey to apney dono haath itney buland kartey ke kandhon key barabar kar detey, jis tarah namaz shuru kartey waqt (rafaa-yadein) kiya tha. phir baqi namaz bhi isi tarah ada kartey yahan tak key jab wo rakat hoti jis mein salam pherna hota to (tashahud mein bethtey waqt) eik paon ko (baain paon ko) eik taraf nikal detey aur tawarruk key tareeqey sey jism ka baayan hissa zamin par rakh kar bethtey. haazirin ney kaha : aap ney sach kaha, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) isi tarah namaz padhtey they."
1062,"Hazrat Umra (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey sawal kiya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kis tarah namaz padhtey they? unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab wuzu kartey waqt bartan mein haath daltey to Allah ka naam letey (Bismillah padhtey) aur achchhi tarah kamil wuzu kartey, phir qibley ki taraf munh kar key khadey ho jatey. phir takbire (tahreema) kehtey aur kandhon tak haath uthatey, phir rukoo kartey to ghutnon par haath rakhtey, aur baazuon ko (pahluon sey) alag rakhtey, phir apna sar uthatey aur apni kamar Mubarak sidhi kar letey aur qaume mein khadey rehtey, jo tumharey qaume sey thoda sa taweel hota tha, phir sajda kartey to apney haath qibley ki taraf rakhtey aur mainey dekha hai ke jahan tak ho sakta baazuon ko (pahluon sey) door rakhtey, phir sar uthatey aur baain qadam par beth jatey aur daayan paon khada rakhtey aur baain pehlu par jhukna pasand nahin farmatey they."
1063,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : safar ki namaz do rakat hai, Jumey ki namaz do rakat hai aur Eid ki namaz do rakat hai. Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zaban Mubarak ke mutabiq ye mukammal hain, naqis nahin."
1064,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : safar ki namaz do rakat hai, Jumey ki namaz do rakat hai, Eidul-Fitr aur Eidul-Azhaa  ki namaz do rakat hai. Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key irshad key mutabiq ye mukammal hain, naqis nahin."
1065,"Hazrat Yala bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey sawal kiya, mainey kaha : Allah Taala ka irshad hai :  (فَلَيْسَ عَلَيْكُمْ جُنَاحٌ اَنْ تَقْصُرُوْا مِنَ الصَّلٰوةِ اِنْ خِفْتُمْ اَنْ يَّفْتِنَكُمُ الَّذِيْنَ كَفَرُوْ), ''tum par namazon key qasr karney mein koi gunah nahin, agar tumhen dar ho ke kafir tumhen sataaeingey. ab to logon ko ye khof baqi nahin raha (to kya ab bhi qasr karna jayez hai ?) Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mujhey bhi isi tarah herat hui thi jis tarah aap ko hui hai to mainey iskey mutalliq Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey sawal kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye tum par Allah ney eik sadqa kiya hai to uska sadqa qubul karo."
1066,"Hazrat Umayya bin Abdullah bin Khalid (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey kaha : hamein Quran Majeed mein hazar ki namaz (jab safar ki haalat mein na hon) aur namaze khof ka zikr to milta hai, lekin safar ki namaz ka zikr nahin milta. Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) ney farmaya : Allah Taala ney Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko hamari taraf (Nabi bana kar) bheja jabke hamen (deen key kisi masley ka) koi ilm na tha to hamney jis tarah Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko kartey dekha hai, hum isi tarah amal kerengey."
1067,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab is Madina shareef sey (safar par) rawana hotey they to do rakat sey ziyada namaz nahin padhtey they (purey safar mein dogaana padhtey rehtey) yahan tak key wapis Madina shareef pahunch jatey."
1068,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Allah Taala ney tumharey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zaban aqdas sey hazar mein chaar rakat namaz farz ki hai aur safar mein do rakat."
1069,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) safar mein Maghrib aur Isha ko jama kar letey they halanke aap ko na to kisi wajeh sey jaldi hoti thi na koi dushman aap key taaqqub mein hota tha aur na aap ko koi khof hota tha."
1070,Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ghazwaaey-tabuk key moqey par safar mein Zohar aur Asr ko aur Maghrib aur Isha ko jama kar key padha.
1071,"Hazrat Hafs bin Aasim bin umr (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main eik safar mein Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) key sath tha. unhoney hamein namaz padhaai, hum namaz sey farigh huye aur wo bhi farigh huye. unhoney nazar uthai to kuch log namaz padhtey nazar aaye. farmaya : ye log kya kar rahey hain? mainey kaha : nafl (ya sunnat waghera) padh rahey hain. unhoney kaha : agar mujhey nafli namaz padhni hoti to main apni farz namaz hi puri kar leta. bhatijey ! main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath safaron mein raha hun. wafat tak aap ney safar mein kabhi do rakat sey ziyada namaz nahin padhi, phir main Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ka hum safar raha to (unhen bhi aisey hi dekha ke) unhoney do rakat sey ziyada namaz nahin padhi, phir main Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ka hum safar raha, unhoney bhi do rakat sey ziyada namaz nahin padhi, phir main Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) key sath raha to unhoney bhi do rakat sey ziyada namaz nahin padhi. un sab ka apni apni wafat tak yehi amal raha aur Allah Taala ka irshad hai : ( لَقَدْ كَانَ لَكُمْ فِيْ رَسُوْلِ اللّٰهِ اُسْوَةٌ حَسَنَةٌ ) ''tumharey liye Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mein achchha namoona hai.''"
1072,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hazar ki namaz bhi muqarrar farmaai aur safar ki namaz bhi. (farz namaz ka ta'yun wazeh farmaya) hum log hazar mein farz sey pehley bhi (sunnat) namaz padhtey they aur farz key baad bhi aur (isi tarah) hum log safar mein bhi farz sey pehley aur farz key baad (sunnat) namaz padhtey they."
1073,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Humaid Zohri (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Hazrat Saaib bin Yazeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : aap ney Makka mein theherney key barey mein kon si hadees suni hai? unhoney farmaya : mainey Hazrat Alaa bin Hizrami (Raziallahu anhu) sey suna, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Muhajir ko (Mina sey) wapsi par (Makka mein) teen din rehney ki ijazat hai."
1074,"Hazrat Ata (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mujhey aur merey sath chand afrad ko Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) ney ye hadees bayan ki ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) zul-hijja ki chaar taareekh ko Makka tashrif laye they."
1075,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unnis din qiyam farmaya aur do-do rakatein padhtey rahey, isliye hum bhi unnis din thehertey hain to do do rakatein padhtey hain jab is sey ziyada thehertey hain to chaar rakat padhtey hain."
1076,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Fateh Makka key saal Makka Mukarrama mein pandarah din thehrey aur namaze qasr ada kartey rahey.
1077,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath Madina Munawra sey Makka Mukarrama ki taraf rawana huye to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) do do rakat namaz ada kartey rahey yahan tak key hum wapis aagey. (Yahya bin Is-haq kehtey hain : ) mainey kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Makka mein kitna arsa qiyam pazeer rahey? Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : das din."
1078,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bandey aur kufr key darmiyan (talluq qaaim karney wala amal) tarake-namaz hai."
1079,"Hazrat Barida bin Haseeb (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : hamarey darmiyan aur un (kafiron aur mushrikon) key darmiyan jo ehad hai, wo namaz hai. jisney isey chhod diya, usney kufr kiya."
1080,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bandey aur mushrik key darmiyan mehaz tarak namaz hi (rabta) hai. jab usney namaz chhod di to wo mushrik ho gaya."
1081,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein khutba diya to irshad farmaya : logo ! marney sey pehley pehley Allah key samney tauba kar lo, mashghool ho janey sey pehley jaldi jaldi nek aamaal kar lo, Allah ka ba-kasrat zikr kar key aur khufiya aur zahiri sadqaat kasrat sey ada kar key apney Rab sey apna talluq ustuwaar kar lo, (uskey nateeja mein) tumhen rizq milega, tumhari madad ki jaeygi aur tumhara haal theek ho jaeyga. jaan lo is saal key is mahina mein, aaj key din is maqam par Allah Taala ney tum par qiyamat tak key liye Juma farz kar diya hai. jo shakhs aadil ya zalim hukmran ki mojudgi mein, meri zindagi mein ya meri wafat key baad, Jumey ki namaz ko ghair aham samajhtey huye ya us (ki farziyat) ka inkar kartey huye jumey ko tarak kerega, (main usey bad dua deta hun ke) Allah karey ! uskey bikhrey huye kaam na simte aur uskey kamon mein barkat na ho, suno ! us shakhs ki (jo bila-uzr Juma tarak karey) koi namaz nahin, uski koi zakat nahin, uska koi Haj nahin, uska koi roza nahin, (ye amal qubul nahin hongey), uski koi neki (qubul) nahin yahan tak key tauba kar ley jo koi tauba kar ley Allah uski tauba qubul farma leyga. khabrdar ! koi aurat kisi mard ki imaamat na karey, koi khana-badosh kisi Muhajir ka Imam na baney, koi fasiq kisi (nek) momin ka Imam na baney, siwaye iskey ke wo usey quwat aur ghalbe sey majbur kar dey aur usey uski talwaar aur kodey ka khof ho."
1082,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Kaab bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab merey walid ki aakhon ki beenai chali gaee to main unka rehbar huwa karta tha. main jab bhi aap ko Jumey key liye ley jata to aap (Jum'ey ki) Azan sun kar Hazrat abu-Umama Asad bin Zarara (Raziallahu anhu) key haq mein duaaey maghfirat aur duaaey khair farmatey. main kuchh arsa un ki zaban sey musalsal yehi baat sunta raha. aakhir mainey dil mein (apney aap sey) kaha : ye to kam aqli ki baat hai ke main un sey iski wajeh daryaft na karun halanke main har Jumey ko, jab bhi wo Jumey ki Azan suntey hain, unhen Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) key haq mein duaaey maghfirat aur duaaey khair kartey sunta hun. (aakhir kaar eik baar) main unhen hasabe mamool namaze Juma ki adaegi key liye ley kar chala. jab unhen Azan ki aawaz sunai di to unhoney apney mamool key mutabiq (Hazrat abu-Umama Asad bin Zarara (Raziallahu anhu) key haq mein) dua ki. mainey arz kiya : abba jaan ! aap jab bhi Jumey ki Azan suntey hain Hazrat Asad bin Zarara (Raziallahu anhu) ko duayen detey hain, iski kya wajeh hai? unhoney farmaya : piyarey betey ! sab sey pehley unhoney hamein Jumey ki namaz padhaai thi, jabke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) abhi Makka sey (hijrat kar key Madina) tashrif nahin laye they. unhoney ye namaz Harra bani Biyaaza mein naqeea' khazmaat key maidan mein padhaai thi. mainey kaha is din aap kitney afrad (us namaz mein shareek) they? unhoney farmaya : chaalis aadmi they."
1083,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala ney hum sey pehley logon ko Jume key pehchanney ki tofiq nahin di. (chunanche) yahudiyon key liye haftey ka din (muqarrar) ho gaya aur esaiyon key liye itwaar. wo log (hafta roza ibadat mein) qiyamat tak hum sey peechhey rahengey. hum duniya walon mein aakhiri (ummat) hain aur qiyamat key din hum awwal hongey, yani sab logon sey pehley hisab kitab ho jaeyga."
1084,"Hazrat Abu-Lubaba bin Abdul-Munzir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Jumey ka din tamam dino ka sardar hai, Allah key yahan iski azmat sab sey ziyada hai wo to Allah key yahan Eidul-Azhaa aur Eidul-Fitr key din sey ziyada azmat wala hai. is mein paanch baaten hain (jo iski afzaliyat ka baais hain : ) is din Allah Taala ney Adam (Alaihissalam) ko paida farmaaya. isi din Allah ney Adam (Alaihissalam) ko zamin par utaara, isi din Allah Taala ney Adam (Alaihissalam) ko faut kiya, is din main eik aisi ghadi hoti hai ke is mein banda Allah sey jo kuch maangey, Allah usey wohi kuchh dey deta hai jab tak kisi haram chiz ka sawal na karey , isi din qiyamat qaaim hogi. har muqarrab farishta aasman , zamin , tamam hawaeyn , pahad aur samandar Jumey key din sey dartey rehtey hain."
1085,"Hazrat Shaddad bin Aus (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tumhara sab sey afzal din Jumey ka din hai. is mein Adam (Alaihissalam) ko paida kiya gaya hai, isi din soor mein phunk maari jaeygi, isi mein be-hoshi taari hogi. lihaza is din mujh par kasrat sey durood padha karo, tumhara durood mujh par pesh kiya jata hai. eik aadmi ney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! jab aap ka jism Mubarak khaak ho jaeyga tab kis tarah hamara durood aap key samney pesh kiya jaeyga? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah ney zamin par haram kar diya hai ke wo nabiyon key jismon ko khaye."
1086,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Jumey (ki namaz) sey (guzishta) Jumey tak key gunah maaf ho jatey hain jabke kabeera gunahon ko na kiya jaaey.
1087,"Hazrat Aus bin Aus Saqafi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney farmaya : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye irshad suna : jisney Jumey key din ghusl kiya aur karaya, awwal waqt mein aaya, (khutbey mein) shuru sey hazir raha, pedal chal kar aaya, sawar ho kar na aaya, Imam sey qarib ho kar tawajjoh sey (khutba) suna  (khutbey key doran mein) fuzul harkat na ki, usey har qadam key badley eik saal key amal, yani eik saal key rozey aur qiyam ka sawab milega."
1088,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko member par (khadey ho kar) ye farmatey suna : jo shakhs Juma padhney aaye usey chahiye ke (pehley) ghusl karey."
1089,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har baligh shakhs par Jumey key din ghusl karna wajib hai."
1090,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney achchhi tarah sanwaar kar wuzu kiya, phir Juma padhney aaya to (Imam sey) qarib ho kar (betha) aur khamoshi sey tawajjoh key sath (khutba) suna, iskey dono jumon key darmiyan key gunah maaf ho jatey hain aur mazeed teen din key bhi, aur jo kankariyon ko haath lagaey, usney fuzul harkat ki."
1091,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney Jumey key din (Jumey ki namaz key liye aatey waqt) wuzu kiya to kafi hai aur achchha hai. uska farz ada ho jaeyga. aur jisney ghusl kiya to ghusl afzal amal hai."
1092,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab Jumey ka din hota hai to masjid key har darwazey par farishtey aa jatey hain jo logon key naam unkey darjaat key mutabiq tarteeb sey likhtey rehtey hain. phir jab Imam (khutba deney key liye) nikalta hai to wo apney sahifey lapet letey hain aur khutba sunney lagtey hain to namaz (Juma) key liye jaldi aaney wala oont ki qurbani deney waley ki tarah (sawab paata) hai, phir jo uskey baad aata hai wo aisey hai jaisey gaaey (bator sadqa) qurban karney wala, jo uskey baad aata hai wo aisey hai jaisey mendhaa qurban karney wala.  Allah key Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney murghi aur andey ka bhi zikr farmaya. (hadees key Raavi) Sehal ney apni hadees mein in alfaz ka izafa kiya : phir jo uskey baad aata hai, wo apna farz ada karney key liye namaz padhney aata hai."
1093,"Hazrat Samura bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney namaze Juma ki aur is mein jaldi hazir honey ki misal aisey bayan farmaai (ke ye amal karney wala aisey hai) jaisey oont qurban karney wala, gaaey ki qurbani deney wala, bakri ki qurbani deney wala, yahan tak key aap ney murghi ka zikr bhi kiya."
1094,"Hazrat Alqama (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) key sath Jumey key liye gaya, unhoney dekha ke un sey pehley teen afrad (masjid mein) aa chukey hain to unhoney farmaya : chaar mein chotha hun aur chaar mein chotha (afzaliyat sey) door nahin. mainey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : qiyamat key din log Jumey mein jaldi aaney ki tarteeb sey Allah key qarib betheingey. pehla, phir doosra, phir teesra. phir farmaya : chaar afrad mein chotha aur chaar afrad mein chauthey number par aaney wala door nahin."
1095,Hazrat Abdullah bin Salam (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Jumey key din member par (khutbey key doran mein) ye farmatey suna : kya harj hai agar tum mein sey koi aadmi kaam kaaj key kapdon key ilawa Jumey key din (namaze Juma ki haziri) key liye do kapdey kharid ley. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) key ustaad Abu-Bakar bin Abi Sheeba ney Muhammad bin Yahya bin Hibban key doosrey shagrid Abdul-Hameed bin Jaafar sey Abdullah bin Salam key betey Yusuf key wastey sey bayan kiya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein khutba diya aur mazkura baala hadees ki maanind bayan kiya.
1096,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Jumey key din Awam sey khitab farmaya to aap ney dekha ke unhoney (roz marra istimal ki) chadaren odh rakhi hain. tab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya harj hai ke tum mein sey kisi aadmi key paas gunjaaish ho to (wo roz marra key) kaam kaaj key kapdon key ilawa Jumey key liye (khaas tor par) kapdey tayyar kar ley.
1097,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Jumey key din achchhi tarah ghusl karey, achchhi tarah sanwaar kar wuzu karey, apna behtareen libas pehney aur Allah ney uski qismat mein ghar walon ki jo khushbu likhi ho wo laga ley, phir Juma padhney aaye to fuzul harkaat na karey aur do aadmiyon key darmiyan judai na karey (ikhattey bethey huye do aadmiyon key darmiyan na bethey) to uskey is Jumey aur doosrey Jumey key darmiyan key (purey haftey key) gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain."
1098,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye Eid ka din hai jo Allah ney musalmanon key liye muqarrar kiya hai, lihaza jo shakhs Juma padhney aaye, usey chahiye ke ghusl kar key aaye. agar khushbu mojud ho to laga ley aur miswak zarur kiya karo."
1099,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log dophare ka aaram Jumey key baad hi kiya kartey they aur khana bhi Jumey key baad hi khaya kartey they."
1100,"Hazrat Salma bin Akwaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath Jumey ki namaz padh kar wapis laut'tey they to hamein deewaron ka itna saya nahin milta tha ke us saye mein chal saken."
1101,Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key muazzan Hazrat Saad Al Qarz (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke wo Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein Jumey key din us waqt Azan kehtey they jab saya tasmey key barabar hota tha.
1102,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log Juma padhtey they, phir wapis aa kar qailula kartey they."
1103,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) do khutbey detey they aur unkey darmiyan thoda sa bethtey they. Bishr ney apni riwayat mein ye izafa kiya hai ke Nabi (Alaihissalam) khadey ho kar khutba detey they.
1104,"Hazrat Amr bin Hures (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko member par khutba detey dekha aur aap ney siyah amama pehan rakha tha."
1105,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khadey ho kar khutba detey they, taaham (asnaaey khutbey mein) eik baar bethtey they, phir khadey ho jatey they (aur doosra khutba detey they)."
1106,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khadey ho kar khutba detey they, phir beth jatey, phir khadey ho kar Quran Majeed ki aayaat tilawat farmatey aur Allah ko yad kartey. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka khutba mutwassit (darmiyana) hota tha aur namaz bhi mutwassit (darmiyani) hoti thi."
1107,(Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key muazzan) Hazrat Saad Al Qarz (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab jang key doran mein khutba detey to kamaan haath mein ley kar khutba detey aur jab Jumey ka khutba detey to aasa haath mein ley kar khutba detey.
1108,"Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood) (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, un sey sawal kiya gaya : kya Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khadey ho kar khutba detey they ya beth kar? unhoney farmaya : kya tum ye aayat nahin padhtey : (وَتَرَكُوكَ قَائِمًا) ''wo aap ko khada chhod jatey hain.'' Imam Abu-Adbullah (Ibne-Maja) ney kaha ye hadees gharib hai, isey ibne-Abi Sheeba key ilawa kisi ney bayan nahin kiya."
1109,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab member par tashrif farma hotey to (haazirin ko) salam kehtey.
1110,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Jumey key din jab Imam khutba dey raha ho (us waqt) agar tum ney apney sathi sey kaha : khamosh raho to tum ney fuzul goi ki."
1111,"Hazrat Ubai-bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Jumey key din khadey ho kar (khutbey key doran mein) Sura- Tabarak (Mulk) tilawat farmaai, aur Allah key dinon (din) (aur maazi (guzre zamaane) key sachchey waqiyat) key zariey sey hamein nasihat farmaai. Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ya Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ney mujhey apni taraf mutawajjeh kar key kaha : ye sura kab nazil hui? mainey to ab (pehli baar) suni hai. unhoney isharey sey kaha : khamosh ! namaz sey farigh kar unhoney kaha : mainey aap sey puchha tha ke ye sura kab nazil hui, aap ney bataya hi nahin. Hazrat Abi (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : aap ko aaj namaz mein sey sirf yehi hissa mila hai ke aap ney fuzul goi ki hai. unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar ye waqia arz kiya aur Hazrat Abi (Raziallahu anhu) ki baat bhi batai. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Abi ney durust kaha hai."
1112,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Sulaik Ghatfaani (Raziallahu anhu) masjid mein aaye to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Khutba irshad farma rahey they. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (un sey) puchha : tum ney namaz padhi hai?  unhoney kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : tab do rakatein padh lo. hadees key Raavi Amr bin Dinar ney Sulaik (key dakhil honey) ka zikr nahin kiya.
1113,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khutba dey rahey they ke eik aadmi aaya, aap ney farmaya : tu ney namaz padhi hai? usney kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : tab do rakatein padh ley."
1114,Hazrat Abu-Hurera aur Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Sulaik Ghatfaani (Raziallahu anhu) aaye aur Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khutba irshad farma rahey they. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen kaha : kya tum ney aaney sey pehley do rakatein padhi hain? unhoney kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : tab do rakatein padh lo aur halki padhna.
1115,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Jumey key din Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khutba irshad farma rahey they ke eik aadmi masjid mein dakhil huwa, wo (qarib aa kar bethney key liye) logon key ooper sey guzarney laga. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : beth ja, tu ney logon ko takleef pahunchaai aur der sey aaya."
1116,"Hazrat Muaz bin Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney Jumey key din logon ki gardanen phalaangin, usey jahannam tak pahunchney key liye pul bana diya gaya."
1117,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Jumey key din (khutbey sey farigh ho kar) jab member sey utartey to aap sey zarurat ki baat cheet kar li jati thi.
1118,"Hazrat Ubedullah bin Abu-Raafey (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Marwan ney Madina mein Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko naaib muqarrar kiya aur khud Makka tashrif ley gaey. Jume key din Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney hamein namaz padhaai to pehli rakat mein Sura Juma aur dusri rakat mein Sura Munaafiqon ki tilawat ki. Hazrat Ubedullah (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : jab Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) namaz sey farigh ho chukey to main unhen mila: mainey unhein kaha aap ney (aaj namaz mein) wo do suraten padhi hain jo Koofa mein Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu)(namaz mein) padha kartey they. Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye suraten padhtey suna hai."
1119,Hazrat Ubedullah Rahimahullah sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Zuhaak bin Qais (Raziallahu anhu) ney Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhuma) ko khat likha. hamein ye bataaiye ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jumey key din Sura Juma key sath dusri kon si sura padhtey they? unhoney jawab diya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) us namaz mein (هَلْ أَتَاكَ حَدِيثُ الْغَاشِيَةِ) (Sura-Ghaashiya) padhtey they.
1120,Hazrat Abu Anba Kholani (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Jumey ki namaz mein (سَبِّحِ اسْمَ رَبِّكَ الْأَعْلَى) aur (هَلْ أَتَاكَ حَدِيثُ الْغَاشِيَةِ) padhte they.
1121,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisey Jumey ki eik rakat miley, wo uskey sath dusri mila ley."
1122,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisey namaz ki eik rakat mil gaee, usey (namaz) mil gaee."
1123,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisey Jumey ki namaz ya kisi aur namaz ki eik rakat mil gaee, usey wo namaz mil gaee."
1124,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Qubaa key rehney waley Jumey key din Jumey ki namaz Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki iqtida (pairvi) mein ada kartey they."
1125,"Sahabiey-Rasool Hazrat Abu-Ja'ad Zamri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney ahmiyat na detey huye teen baar Jumey ki namaz tarak kar di, uskey dil par mohar laga di jaaeygi."
1126,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney kisi majburi key baghair teen baar Jumey ki namaz tarak ki, Allah Taala uskey dil par mohar laga deta hai."
1127,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : khabrdar ! (tawajjoh sey suno ! ) mumkin hai eik aadmi (shehar sey) eik do meel key fasley par chand bakriyan liye huye ho, us ghaas milney mein mushkil pesh aa jaey aur wo mazeed door chala jaey, phir Jumey ka din aaye aur wo aa kar Jumey ki namaz mein shareek na ho, phir (doosra) Juma aa jaey aur wo (is baar bhi) hazir na ho, phir (teesra) Juma aaye aur wo hazir na ho yahan tak key uskey dil par mohar laga di jaey."
1128,"Hazrat Samura bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney jaan boojh kar Juma chhod diya, usey chahiye ke eik Dinar sadqa karey, agar uskey paas (eik Dinar) na ho to aadha Dinar sadqa karey."
1129,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Jumey (ki farz namaz) sey pehley chaar rakatein padhtey they aur un mein fasla nahin kartey they. (eik salam sey padhtey they.)
1130,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, ke wo jab Jumey ki namaz padhtey to wapis ja kar ghar mein do rakatein padhtey they, phir farmatey : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bhi isi tarah kiya kartey they."
1131,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Jumey key baad do rakat namaz  (sunnat) ada kartey they.
1132,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum Jumey key baad namaz padho to chaar rakat (sunnat) padho.
1133,Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid sey aur wo apney dada (Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma)) sey riwayat kartey hain ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Jumey key din namaz sey pehley masjid mein halqey bananey sey mana farmaya hai.
1134,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid sey aur wo apney dada (Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma)) sey riwayat kartey hain, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Jumey key din got maar kar bethney sey mana farmaya, yani jab Imam khutba dey raha ho."
1135,"Hazrat Saaib bin Yazeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka to eik hi muazzan tha, jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (khutba deney key liye ghar sey) bahar tashrif latey (aur member par tashrif rakhtey) to wo Aazan kehta aur jab (khutbey sey farigh ho kar) member sey utartey to wo iqaamat keh deta. Hazrat abu-Bakar aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhuma) ka mamool bhi yehi tha. phir jab Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) khalifa huye aur (namaz key liye aaney waley) logon ki kasrat ho gaee to unhoney bazar main eik ghar (ki chhat) par teesri Azan mazeed kahlwaai. is jagah ka naam Zaur tha (jahan muazzan ye Azan kehta tha) jab Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) (khutbey key liye) tashrif latey to wo Azan kehta aur jab (member sey) nichey utartey to wo iqaamat kehta."
1136,"Hazrat Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab member par khadey hotey to Sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum apney chehrey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf kar letey."
1137,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Jumey (key din) main eik ghadi hai jo musalman aadmi usey is haal mein paa ley ke wo khada namaz padh raha ho, wo us ghadi mein Allah sey jo bhalai maangeyga (duniya ki ho ya aakhirat ki), Allah usey wo chiz dey dega. aap ney haath sey ishara kiya ke wo ghadi mukhtasar si hai."
1138,"Hazrat Amr bin Auf Muzni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna hai : Jumey key din main eik ghadi hai, is mein banda Allah sey jo kuchh maangey, Allah usey uski matlooba chiz dey deta hai. arz kiya gaya : wo kon si ghadi hai? aap ney farmaya : jab namaz khadi ho jaaey, (us waqt sey ley kar) namaz sey farigh honey tak."
1139,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Salam (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif farma they. mainey arz kiya : hum Allah ki kitab (Toraat) mein paatey hain ke Jumey key din eik ghadi aisi hai ke us waqt jo koi momin banda namaz padhta ho aur Allah Taala sey kuchh maangey, Allah uski hajat puri farma deta hai. Hazrat Abdullah bin Salam (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ishara farmaya : ya ghadi sey bhi kam. mainey kaha : aap ney sach farmaya ya eik ghadi sey bhi kam. mainey arz ki : wo ghadi kon si hai? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye din ki aakhiri ghadi hai. mainey arz ki : wo to namaz ka waqt nahin. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : haan, haan momin banda jab namaz padh kar beth rehta hai, wo namaz key ilawa kisi aur wajeh sey nahin rukaa hota, wo namaz hi mein hota hai."
1140,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs pabandi sey baara rakat sunnatein padhta hai, uskey liye jannat mein ghar taamir kar diya jata hai. Zohar sey pehley chaar rakatein Zohar key baad do rakatein, Maghrib key baad do rakatein, Isha key baad do rakatein aur Fajr sey pehley do rakatein."
1141,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Umme-Habiba binte Abu-Sufiyaan (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney din raat mein (farzon key ilawa) baara rakatein padhin, uskey liye jannat main eik ghar taamir kiya jaeyga."
1142,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney din mein baara rakatein padhin, uskey liye jannat main eik ghar taamir kiya jaeyga, Fajr sey pehley do rakatein, Zohar sey pehley do rakatein, Zohar key baad do rakatein aur ghaaliban aap ney ye bhi farmaya : Asr sey pehley do rakatein, aur Maghrib key baad do rakatein. aur ghaaliban ye bhi farmaya : Isha key baad do rakatein."
1143,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) subh saadiq tulu honey key baad do rakatein padhtey they.
1144,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) subah (key farzon) sey pehley do rakatein padhtey, (aur itni halki padhtey) goya aap key kanon mein iqaamat ki aawaz aa rahi hai."
1145,Hazrat Hafsa binte umr (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke jab subah ki Azan ho jati to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) namaz (farz) key liye janey sey pehley halki si do rakatein ada farmatey.
1146,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab wuzu kartey they to do rakat namaz ada farmatey, phir namaz key liye (masjid mein) tashrif ley jatey."
1147,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) iqaamat key waqt do rakat namaz padhtey they."
1148,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Fajr sey pehley ki do rakaaton (sunnaton) mein (قُلْ يَا أَيُّهَا الْكَافِرُونَ ) aur ( قُلْ هُوَ اللَّهُ أَحَدٌ ) ki tilawat farmaai.
1149,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey eik maah tak Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (ki namaz) ka mushaahida kiya to aap Fajr ki sunnaton mein (قُلْ يَا أَيُّهَا الْكَافِرُونَ) aur (قُلْ هُوَ اللَّهُ أَحَدٌ) padhtey they."
1150,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Fajr (ki farz namaz) sey pehley do rakatein padha kartey they, aur farmaya kartey they : ye do suraten kitni achchhi hain, jo Fajr ki sunnaton mein padhi jati hain : (قُلْ يَا أَيُّهَا الْكَافِرُونَ) aur (قُلْ هُوَ اللَّهُ أَحَدٌ)."
1151,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab namaz ki iqaamat ho jaey to farz namaz key ilawa koi namaz nahin hoti. Imam Ibne-Maja ney eik teesri sanad sey mazkura riwayat ki tarah bayan kiya."
1152,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Sarjis (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney namaz key doran main eik aadmi ko Fajr sey pehley ki do sunnatein padhtey dekha, namaz sey farigh ho kar Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney us sey farmaya : tu ney apni dono namazon mein sey kis ka aetbar kiya hai?"
1153,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Malik, ibne Buhaina (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik namaz padhtey huye aadmi key paas sey guzrey jabke namaz Fajr ki iqaamat ho chuki thi. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney us sey kuchh farmaya, mujhey malum na huwa ke kya farmaya. jab wo namaz sey farigh huwa to hum uskey gird jama ho kar poochhney lagey : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney tujh sey kya farmaya tha? usney kaha : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey farmaya tha : ho sakta hai ke koi shakhs Fajr ki chaar rakatein padh ley."
1154,"Hazrat Qais bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aadmi ko Fajr ki namaz key baad do rakatein padhtey dekha. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya subah ki namaz do dafa padh rahey ho? us shakhs ney arz kiya : mainey Fajr sey pehley ki do rakatein (sunnatein) nahin padhi thin, wo (ab) padhi hain to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khamosh ho gaey."
1155,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) neend ki wajeh sey Fajr ki sunnatein na padh sakey to aap ney suraj tulu honey key baad un ki qaza di.
1156,"Hazrat Qaaboos (Rahimahullah) apney walid (Hazrat Abu-Zibyaan Husain bin Jundub (Rahimahullah)) sey riwayat kartey huye farmatey hain ke merey walid ney Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) key paas (kisi ko) ye daryaft karney key liye bheja ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kon si namaz hamesha padhe jaane ko ziyada pasand kartey they? unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Zohar (key farzon) sey pehley chaar rakat padhtey they, jin mein taweel qiyam farmatey aur rukoo aur sajdey khub achchhi tarah kartey."
1157,Hazrat Abu-Ayyub (Khalid bin Zaid Ansari) (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) suraj dhalney par Zohar sey pehley chaar rakatein padhtey they. un mein salam key sath fasla nahin kartey they. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab suraj dhal jata hai to aasman key darwazey khol diye jatey hain.
1158,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki jab Zohar ki pehli chaar sunnatein chhoot jatin to aap unhein Zohar ki baad wali do sunnaton key baad ada kar letey they. Imam Abu-Adbullah (Ibne-Maja) ney kaha, us riwayat ko Qais an Shoba key ilawa kisi ney bayan nahin kiya."
1159,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Haris (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ney Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein kisi ko bheja. main bhi uskey sath gaya. usney Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey masla daryaft kiya to unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney zakat wasul karney key liye eik aadmi bheja tha aur aap key paas bahut sey muhajrin jama ho gaey they (jo zakat aur sadqaat key mustahiq they) aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unkey barey mein bahut fikr mand they. (unhi dinon (dinon) main eik din Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey ghar mein Zohar ki namaz key liye wuzu kar rahey they) ke darwazey par dastak hui. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bahar tashrif ley gaey. Zohar ki namaz padhaaney key baad aap (masjid mein) beth kar us (zakat wasul karney waley) ka laya huwa (zakat) ka maal (mustahiq afrad mein) taqseem karney lagey. aap Asr tak isi kaam mein mashghool rahey. uskey baad Nabi (Alaihissalam) merey ghar mein tashrif laye aur do rakatein padhin, phir farmaya : main zakat aur sadqaat laney waley key mamley mein masroof honey ki wajeh sey Zohar key baad un do rakaaton ko nahin padh saka tha, isliye mainey Asr key baad padh lin."
1160,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Zohar sey pehley chaar aur uskey baad chaar rakatein padhey, Allah Taala usey jahannam par haram farma deta hai."
1161,"Hazrat Aasim bin Zamra Salooli (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamney Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki din ki nafli namaz daryaft ki, unhoney farmaya : tum wo nahin padh saktey. hamney kaha : aap bayan to farmaeyn, hum sey jis qadr ho sakeyga amal kar leingey. Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab Fajr ki namaz padh letey to thehar jatey yahan tak key jab suraj idhar, yani mashriq ki taraf itna buland ho jata jitna Asr key waqt udhar, yani maghrib ki taraf buland hota hai to aap uth kar do rakatein ada kartey. iskey baad twaqquf (qiyaam) farmatey yahan tak key jab suraj is taraf, yani mashriq ki taraf itna buland ho jata jitna Zohar key waqt us taraf, yani maghrib ki taraf hota hai to uth kar chaar rakatein padhtey, phir jab suraj dhal jata to Zohar (key farzon) sey pehley chaar rakatein aur Zohar key baad do rakatein padhte aur Asr sey pehley chaar rakatein padhtey aur do do rakaaton key darmiyan muqarrab farishten, nabiyon aur un ki perwi karney waley musalmanon aur mominon key liye salamti ki dua ka fasla kartey. (iskey baad) Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : ye sola rakatein huin jo Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki din key waqt ki nafli namaz thi. is par pabandi sey amal karney waley log bahut kam hain. hadees key Raavi Wakee kehtey ke merey baap ney apni riwayat mein ye izafa kiya hai : Hazrat Habib bin Abi Sabit (Rahimahullah) ney (ye hadees sun kar) farmaya : Abu-Is'haq ! is hadees key iwaz agar mujhey aap ki masjid bhar sona bhi miley to mujhey pasand nahin (ye hadees itni dolat sey bhi ziyada qeemtii hai)."
1162,Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney teen baar farmaya : har do azaanon key darmiyan namaz hai. teesri baar farmaya : jo koi chahey (padhley).
1163,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein muazzan Azan deta to log Maghrib sey pehley do rakat (sunnat) padhney key liye is kasrat sey khadey ho jatey ke mehsus hota iqaamat ho gaee hai."
1164,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Maghrib ki namaz ada farmatey, phir merey ghar tashrif latey aur do rakat ada farmatey."
1165,"Hazrat Raafey bin khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey yahan (yani) banu Abdul-Ash'hal key mohalley mein tashrif laye. aap ney hamari masjid mein hamein maghrib ki namaz padhaai, phir farmaya : ye do rakatein apney gharon mein padha karo."
1166,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Maghrib (key farzon) key baad ki do rakaaton mein (قُلْ يَا أَيُّهَا الْكَافِرُونَ) aur (قُلْ هُوَ اللَّهُ أَحَدٌ) padhte they.
1167,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney Maghrib key baad chhe rakatein padhein aur unkey darmiyan koi na munasib baat munh sey na nikali, uskey liye ye namaz baara baras ki ibadat key barabar ho jaeygi."
1168,"Hazrat Khaarija bin Huzaafa Adwi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laye aur farmaya : Allah Taala ney tumhen mazeed eik namaz ata farmaai hai, wo tumharey liye surkh oonton sey behtar hai, wo namaz witr hai jis ko Allah Taala ney tumharey liye Isha ki namaz sey subah saadiq tulu honey tak key waqt mein muqarrar kiya hai."
1169,"Hazrat Aasim bin Zamra Salooli (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : witr lazimi nahin hai aur na tumhari farz namazon ki tarah hai lekin Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney namaze witr ada ki hai aur farmaya : aey Quran walo ! witr padha karo kyonkey Allah Taala witr (akela) hai, witr ko pasand karta hai."
1170,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala witr (akela) hai aur witr (taaq adad) ko pasand karta hai, Quran walo ! witr (ki namaz) padha karo. eik Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) ney kaha : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kya farma rahey hain?  farmaya : terey liye ya terey sathiyon key liye nahin."
1171,"Hazrat Ubai-bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) witron mein (سَبِّحِ اسْمَ رَبِّكَ الْأَعْلَى) aur (قُلْ يَا أَيُّهَا الْكَافِرُونَ) aur (قُلْ هُوَ اللَّهُ أَحَدٌ) padha kartey they."
1172,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) witron mein (سَبِّحِ اسْمَ رَبِّكَ الْأَعْلَى) aur (قُلْ يَا أَيُّهَا الْكَافِرُونَ) aur (قُلْ هُوَ اللَّهُ أَحَدٌ) padha kartey they. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney mazkura baala hadees key hum maana eik aur hadees, eik dusri sanad sey bayan ki hai."
1173,"Hazrat Abdul-Azeez bin Juraij (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamney Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey daryaft kiya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) namaze witr mein kya padhtey they? to unhoney farmaya : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) pehli rakat mein (سَبِّحِ اسْمَ رَبِّكَ الْأَعْلَى) dusri rakat mein (قُلْ يَا أَيُّهَا الْكَافِرُونَ) aur teesri rakat mein (قُلْ هُوَ اللَّهُ أَحَدٌ) aur muawwizten (Sura-Falaq aur Sura- Naas) padhtey they."
1174,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat ko do-do rakat kar key namaz padhte they aur eik witr padhtey they."
1175,"Hazrat Abu-Mujliz (Rahimahullah) ney Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat kartey huye kaha ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : raat ki namaz do do rakat hai aur witr eik rakat hai. Abu-Mujliz kehtey hain : mainey kaha : ye farmaiye ke agar meri aankh lag jaaey? ye farmaiye ke agar main soyaa reh jaun (phir witr kaisey padhun)? ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhuma) ney farmaya : farmaiye farmaiye ko us sitarey key paas phenk do. mainey sar uthaya to mujhey simaak sitaara nazar aaya , ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhuma) ney do baara yehi hadees bayan kartey huye kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya hai : raat ki namaz do do rakat hai aur witr subah saadiq sey pehley ki eik rakat hai."
1176,"Hazrat matlab bin Abdullah (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik aadmi ney Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey sawal kiya : main witr kaisey padhun? ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhuma) ney farmaya : eik rakat witr padh liya karo. usney kaha : mujhey dar hai ke log kahengey ye dum-kati namaz hai. ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhuma) ney farmaya : ye Allah aur uskey Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sunnat hai, yani ye Allah (ki muqarrar ki hui) aur Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki (farmaai hui) sunnat hai."
1177,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) har do rakat par salam phertey they aur eik witr padhtey they."
1178,"Hazrat Hasan bin Ali (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mujhey merey nana Janab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ye alfaz sikhaey they ke inhen witon key qunoot mein padha karun : (اللهم عَافِنِي فِيمَنْ عَافَيْتَ وَتَوَلَّنِي فِيمَنْ تَوَلَّيْتَ وَاهْدِنِي فِيمَنْ هَدَيْتَ وَقِنِي شَرَّ ما قَضَيْتَ وَبَارِكْ لِي فِيمَا أَعْطَيْتَ إِنَّكَ تَقْضِي وَلَا يُقْضَى عَلَيْكَ إِنَّهُ لا يَذِلُّ من وَالَيْتَ سُبْحَانَكَ رَبَّنَا تَبَارَكْتَ وَتَعَالَيْتَ), ''aey Allah ! to jinhen aafiyat bakhshta hai, mujhey bhi un mein (shamil kar key) aafiyat bakhsh aur jin sey to mohabbat rakhta hai, un mein (shamil kar key) mujh sey mohabbat rakh aur jinhen tu ney hidayat di, un mein (shamil kar key) mujhey bhi hidayat dey aur tu ney jo bhi faisla kiya hai, uskey shar sey mujhey mehfooz farma aur jo kuchh tu ney mujhey diya hai is mein barkat ata farma, yaqinan to hi faisley karta hai, terey muqabley mein koi faisla nahin hota aur jisey to dost rakhey, wo kahin zaleel nahin ho sakta, aey hamarey Rab to pak hai, to barkaton wala aur raf'aton (bulandiyon) wala hai."""
1179,"Hazrat Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) witron key aakhir mein yun (dua) farmatey they : (اللَّهُمَّ إِنِّى أَعُوذُ بِرِضَاكَ مِنْ سُخْطِكَ وَأَعُوذُ بِمُعَافَاتِكَ مِنْ عُقُوبَتِكَ وَأَعُوذُ بِكَ مِنْكَ لاَ أُحْصِى ثَنَاءً عَلَيْكَ أَنْتَ كَمَا أَثْنَيْتَ عَلَى نَفْسِكَ), ''aey Allah ! main teri narazi sey bachtey huye teri khushnoodi ki panah mein aata hun aur teri saza sey bachtey huye teri maafi ki panah mein aata hun aur main tujh sey (terey gaiz aur ghazab sey) teri (rehmat ki) aman chahta hun, main teri tareefen shumar nahin kar sakta, to wesa hi hai jaisey tu ney khud apni sifaat bayan farmaai hain.''"
1180,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni kisi dua mein haath nahin uthatey they magar barish ki dua kartey waqt haath (is qadr) buland kartey they ke aap ki baghlon ki safedi nazar aa jati.
1181,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab to Allah sey dua karey to sidhi hatheliyon key sath dua kar aur haathon ki pusht key sath (haath ultey kar key) dua mat kar. aur jab to (dua sey) farigh ho jaey to haathon ko chehrey par pher ley."
1182,Hazrat Ubai-bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) witr padhte they to rukoo sey pehley duaaey qunoot padhte they.
1183,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke un sey subah ki namaz mein qunoot padhney ka masla daryaft kiya gaya to unhoney farmaya : hum rukoo sey pehley bhi qunoot padh liya kartey they, aur rukoo key baad bhi."
1184,"Janab Muhammad (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey qunoot key barey mein sawal kiya to unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney rukoo key baad duaaey qunoot farmaai."
1185,"Hazrat Masruq (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki namaze witr key mutalliq sawal kiya to unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney raat key har hissey mein witr padhey hain, raat key shuru mein bhi aur darmiyan mein bhi aur jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat hui to (un dino) aap key witr (aam taur par) sahar (subah) key waqt khatam hotey they."
1186,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney raat key har hissey mein witr padhey hain. raat key shuru mein bhi aur darmiyan mein bhi aur aap key witr sahar (subah) tak khatam hotey they."
1187,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis ko ye khof ho ke wo raat key aakhiri hissey mein nahin jaag sakeyga, wo raat ki ibtida (shuruat) mein (Isha key baad) witr padh kar so jaey aur jisey ye ummid ho ke wo raat key aakhiri hissey mein jaag padeyga, usey chahiye ke raat key aakhiri hissey mein witr padhey kyonkey raat key aakhiri hissey mein tilawat (sun'ney) key liye (farishtey) hazir hotey hain aur ye afzal hai."
1188,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs witr chhod kar soyaa rahey (aur uski aankh na khule) ya usey yad na rahey to usey chahiye ke subah ko yad aaney par witr padh ley."
1189,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : subah honey sey pehley witr padh liya karo. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) key ustaad Janab Muhammad bin Yahya bayan kartey hain ke is hadees sey Sabit hota hai ke Abdur-Rehman (bin Zaid bin Aslam) ki riwayat (hadees : 1188) zaeef hai."
1190,"Hazrat Abu-Ayyub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : witr zaruri hain, lihaza jo shakhs paanch rakat witr padhna chahey padh ley aur jo shakhs teen witr padhna chahey padh ley aur jo shakhs eik witr padhna chahey padh ley."
1191,"Hazrat Saad bin Hisham (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey sawal kartey huye kaha : Ummul-mominin ! mujhey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki namaze witr (tahajjud) key mutalliq irshad farmaiye. unhoney farmaya : hum log Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key liye miswak aur (wuzu key liye) pani tayyar rakhtey they. Allah Taala raat key jis hissey mein Nabi (Alaihissalam) ko uthana chahta, utha deta, aap miswak kartey, wuzu kartey, phir no rakat namaz padhtey, is mein sirf aathwein rakat par (tashahud key liye) bethtey to apney Rab sey duayen kartey. (yani) Allah ka zikr kartey, uski tareef farmatey aur duayen padhtey, phir salam pherey baghair khadey ho jatey. khadey ho kar naween rakat padhtey, phir (tashahud mein) beth kar Allah ka zikr kartey, uski tareefen kartey, Rab sey duayen maangtey aur uskey Nabi par durood padhtey, phir (qadrey buland aawaz sey) salam phertey jo hamen sun jaey, phir salam pherney key baad beth kar do rakatein padhtey. ye giyara rakatein huin. jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki umr ziyada ho gaee aur jism Mubarak bhari ho gaya to aap saat witr padhtey they aur salam key baad do rakatein padhtey they."
1192,"Hazrat Ummul-mominin Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) saat ya paanch rakat witr padhtey they, unkey darmiyan salam ya kalam key sath tafriq (farq) nahin kartey they (eik hi salam sey padhte they)."
1193,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) safar mein do rakat (farz) ada kartey they, is sey ziyada nahin padhtey they aur Nabi (Alaihissalam) (safar mein) raat ko tahajjud bhi padhtey they. (Saalim farmatey hain) mainey arz kiya : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (safar mein) witr bhi padhtey they?  ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhuma) ney farmaya : haan."
1194,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) aur Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney safar ki namaz do rakat muqarrar farmaai hai. ye mukammal namaz hai, naqis nahin, aur safar mein witr padhna sunnat hai."
1195,Hazrat Ummul-mominin Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) witr key baad beth kar halki si do rakatein padh liya kartey they.
1196,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik witr padhtey they, phir do rakatein padhtey, un mein qirat beth kar kartey jab rukoo karna hota to khadey ho kar rukoo kartey."
1197,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main raat key aakhiri hissey mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko hamesha apney yahaan soey huye paati thi. Wakee (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain : yani witr key baad."
1198,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab Fajr ki do (sunnat) rakatein padh letey to daain pehlu par let jatey."
1199,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab Fajr ki do rakatein padhtey to let jaatey."
1200,"Hazrat Saeed bin Yasar (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : main Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) key sath (safar mein) tha, main (raastey mein ruk gaya aur) un sey peechhey reh gaya aur (sawari sey utar kar) witr padh liye. (jab dobara un sey ja mila) to unhoney puchha : tum peechhey kyon reh gaey they? mainey arz kiya : mainey witr padhey hain. farmaya : kya tumharey liye Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mein achchha namoona nahin? mainey kaha : ji haan. hai. farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney oont hi par witr padh liya kartey they."
1201,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sawari par witr padh letey they.
1202,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) sey farmaya : kis waqt witr padhtey ho? unhoney kaha : Isha key baad raat key shuru mein padh leta hun. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : umr ! tum (kab witr padhtey ho)? unhoney kaha : raat key aakhiri hissey mein (padhta hun)  Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : abu-Bakar ! tum ney ziyada pukhta aur qabile aitimad kaam ikhtiyar kiya aur umr ! tum ney quwat wala kaam ikhtiyar kiya. Imam Ibne-Maja Rahimahullah ney kaha, hamein Abu-Daawood Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Tauba ney eik dusri sanad sey Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhuma) sey isi tarah riwayat bayan ki."
1203,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney namaz padhaai, is mein (bhool kar) kami beshi ho gaee. Ibrahim Nakhai (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : weham mujhey huwa hai (yaad nahin raha ke ustaade mohtaram Hazrat Alqama (Rahimahullah) ney kami ka lafz farmaya tha ya ziyadti ka) arz kiya gaya : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya namaz mein kuchh izafa ho gaya hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main eik insan hi hun, jis tarah tum bhool jatey ho, (kabhi kabhar) main bhi bhool jata hun to jab kisi sey bhool ho jaey to bethey bethey do sajdey kar liya kerey. phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (qibley ki taraf) munh pheraa aur do sajdey kiye."
1204,Hazrat Ayaaz bin Hilal Ansari (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey sawal kiya aur kaha : eik aadmi namaz padhta hai (lekin namaz key doran mein) usey malum hi nahin rehta ke usney kitni namaz padhi hai (wo kya kerey)?  Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey koi namaz padhey aur usey malum na rahey ke kitni namaz padhi hai to bethey bethey do sajdey kar ley.
1205,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik baar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Zohar ki namaz ki paanch rakatein padhin. aap sey kaha gaya : kya namaz (ki rakaaton) mein izafa kar diya gaya hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : baat kya hai?  aap ko bataya gaya (ke paanch rakatein padhi gaee hain). tab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney paon moda aur do sajdey kar liye."
1206,"Hazrat ibne Baheena (Abdullah bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik namaz padhaai, wo ghaaliban Asr ki namaz thi, dusri rakat padh kar Nabi (Alaihissalam) (tashahud key liye) bethney sey pehley hi (bhool kar) khadey ho gaey, phir jab salam sey pehley ka waqt aaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney do sajdey kar liye."
1207,Hazrat ibne Baheena (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Zohar ki do rakaaton key baad khadey ho gaey. (tashahud key liye) bethna yad na raha. (baaqi namaz padhney key baad) jab aap salam key siwa baqi namaz sey farigh ho gaey to saho key do sajdey kar liye aur salam pher diya.
1208,"Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi shakhs do rakatein padh kar (atahiyaat padhey baghair) uth khada ho aur abhi puri tarah khada na huwa ho (ke yad aa jaey) to wo beth jaey. agar puri tarah khada ho chuka ho (phir yad aaye) tab na bethey (zayed rakat puri kar key) sahoo key sajdey kar ley."
1209,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap farma rahey they : jab kisi ko do aur eik key darmiyan shak ho jaey to wo eik rakat shumar karey aur do aur teen key darmiyan shak ho to do rakatein shumar kar ley. agar teen aur chaar key darmiyan shak pad jaey to teen rakatein samajh ley, phir baqi namaz puri kar ley yahan tak key shak-izaafey key barey mein reh jaey, phir salam pherney sey pehley bethey bethey do sajdey kar ley."
1210,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey kisi ko apni namaz (ki rakaaton) mein shak ho jaey to wo shak ko chhod kar yaqin par bana kerey. phir jab usey (namaz) mukammal ho janey ka yaqin ho jaey to (aakhir mein) do sajdey kar ley. agar uski namaz mukammal ho gaee thi. (aur eik rakat zayed padhi gaee hai.)  to wo rakat nafl bin jaeygi aur agar namaz (waaqaee) kam thi to us rakat sey namaz mukammal ho jaeygi aur do sajdon sey shetan ki naak khaak aalud ho jaeygi."
1211,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik namaz padhaai is mein malum nahin izafa ho gaya ya kami reh gaee? phir aap ney (Sahaba sey) poochha, hamney bata diya (ke ye ghalati hui hai) Nabi (Alaihissalam) ney paon mod kar qibley ki taraf munh kar liya aur do sajdey kiye, phir salam pheraa, phir hamari taraf munh kiya aur farmaya : agar namaz key barey mein koi naya hukm aata to main tum ko bata deta. main to sirf eik insan hun, jis tarah tum log bhool jatey ho isi tarah mujh sey bhi bhool ho jati hai. chunanche jab main bhool jaun to mujhey yad dila diya karo. aur tum mein sey jis ko namaz mein shak ho jaey to wo (soch kar) sehat sey qarib tar baat malum karey, phir uskey mutabiq namaz puri karey. salam pherey aur do sajdey kar ley."
1212,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab kisi ko namaz mein shak pad jaey to usey chahiye ke sahih baat (soch kar) malum kerey. phir do sajdey kar ley. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) key ustaad Ali bin Muhammad Tanaafusi bayan kartey hain ke ye asal hai. iska koi inkar nahin kar sakta."
1213,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney bhool kar do rakaaton par salam pher diya. eik aadmi jisey Zul-Yadain kehtey they, usney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! kya namaz kam ho gaee hai ya aap bhool gaey hain? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : na namaz kam hui hai aur na main bhoolaa hun. unhoney arz kiya : agar ye baat hai to (arz ye hai ke) aap ney do hi rakatein padhi hain. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya jis tarah Zul-Yadain kehta hai (wesay hi huwa hai)? Sahaba ney kaha : ji haan. tab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney aagey badh kar do rakatein padhain, phir salam pheraa, phir sahoo key do sajdey kiye."
1214,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein pichhley waqt ki eik namaz (Zohar ya Asr ki) do rakatein padha kar salam pher diya. masjid main eik lakdi thi (shayad sutoon hoga) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) us sey tek laga kar tashrif rakha kartey they, phir (salam pherney key baad) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uth kar us lakdi ki taraf chaley. jin afrad ko (janey ki) jaldi thi wo ye kehtey huye chal diye. namaz kam ho gaee hai. haazirin mein Hazrat abu-Bakar aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhuma) bhi mojud they. wo aap sey kuchh arz karney sey darey (ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko nagawar na guzrey) logon main eik lambey haathon waley sahab bhi they, jo Zul-Yadain key naam sey maroof they. unhoney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya namaz kam kar di gaee hai ya aap sey bhool ho gaee? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : na namaz kam ki gaee hai aur na main bhoolaa hun. unhoney arz kiya : aap ney do hi rakatein padhi hain. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya (aisey hi huwa hai) jis tarah Zul-Yadain kehta hai?  Sahaba ney kaha : ji haan, tab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney uth kar do rakatein padhein, phir salam pheraa, phir do sajdey kiye phir salam pheraa."
1215,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Asr ki teen rakatein padh kar salam pher diya, phir uth kar hujrey mein tashrif ley gaey. eik lambey haathon waley sahab, Hazrat Kharbaaq (Raziallahu anhu) ney (bahir sey) aawaz di : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya namaz kam ho gaee hai? aap ghussey ki keyfiyat mein chadar ghaseet'tey huye bahar tashrif laye aur (haazirin sey maamla) daryaft kiya, aap ko uski khabar di gaee to Nabi (Alaihissalam) ney jo rakat (ghalati sey) chhod di thi wo padhaai, phir salam pheraa, phir do sajdey kiye, phir salam pheraa."
1216,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : shetan namaz key doran mein kisi key paas aata hai, phir uskey aur uskey dil key darmiyan haael (rukawat) ho jata hai, (waswasey daalta hai) yahan tak key namazi ko malum nahin rehta ke usney ziyada namaz padhi hai ya kam. jab ye surat pesh aaye to (namazi ko chahiye ke) salam sey pehley do sajdey kar ley, phir salam pher dey."
1217,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : shetan insan key aur uskey dil key darmiyan mudaakhlat karta hai, chunanche us (namazi) ko malum nahin rehta ke kitni namaz padhi hai. jab ye soorate-haal pesh aaye to usey chahiye ke salam sey pehley do sajdey kar ley."
1218,"Hazrat Alqama (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney salam key baad sahoo key sajdey kiye, phir bayan farmaya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney bhi isi tarah kiya tha."
1219,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap ney farmaya : har bhool mein do sajdey hain. salam pherney key baad."
1220,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) namaz key liye (ghar sey) tashrif laye aur (الله اكبر) keh diya. (takbire tahreema keh kar namaz shuru kar di), phir Sahaba ko ishara kiya to wo (namaz ki haalat mein) thehrey rahey. aap ney ja kar ghusl farmaya : (wapis aaye to) aap key sar sey pani tapak raha tha. chunanche aap ney namaz padhaai aur farigh ho kar farmaya : main janabat (sambhog ke baad naapaki) ki haalat main tumharey paas aa gaya tha aur mujhey yad hi nahin raha yahan tak key main namaz mein khada ho gaya."
1221,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisey namaz mein qai aa jaey ya Nakseer phootey ya koi chiz pet mein sey munh mein aaye ya mazi nikley to usey chahiye ke (namaz chhod kar) chala jaey, wuzu kerey. phir apni namaz par bana kar ley b-sharte-ke us bich mein kalam na kerey."
1222,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi namaz padh raha ho aur uska wuzu toot jaey to usey chahiye ke apni naak pakad kar (wuzu key liye) chala jaey ."
1223,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mujhey phoda nikla huwa tha. mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey namaz key mutalliq sawal kya (ke kaisey namaz padhun?) to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : khada ho kar namaz padh , agar (khada honey ki) taqat na ho to beth kar, agar uski bhi taqat na ho to pehlu key bal (let kar namaz padh ley.)"
1224,"Hazrat Wayl bin Hajar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko beth kar namaz padhtey dekha , aap bimari ki wajeh sey daain taraf jhuk kar bethey huye they."
1225,"ummul-mominin Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : qism hai us zaat ki jisney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko wafat di! Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) us waqt tak faut nahin huye jab tak aap aksar (nafli) namaz beth kar na padhney lagey, aur Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko wo nek amal pasand tha jis par banda hameshgi ikhtiyar karey agar-che (wo amal) thoda ho."
1226,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) beth kar qirat kartey they. jab rukoo karna chahtey to itney arsey key liye khadey ho jatey jis mein koi insan chaalis aayaton ki tilawat kar ley ."
1227,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko raat ki namaz hamesha khadey ho kar padhtey dekha yahan tak key aap umr-rasida ho gaey, tab aap beth kar namaz padhney lagey yahan tak key jab chaalis ya tees aayaton key barabar qirat reh jati to khadey ho kar ye qirat kartey aur sajda kartey ."
1228,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Shaqeeq Uqeli (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki raat ki namaz ( tahajjud ( key mutalliq sawal kya to unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat ka eik lamba hissa khadey ho kar namaz padhtey aur raat ka eik taweel hissa beth kar namaz padhtey they. jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khadey ho kar qirat kartey to rukoo bhi khadey ho kar kartey aur jab beth kar qirat kartey to rukoo bhi beth kar kartey ."
1229,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke wo beth kar namaz padh rahey they ke unkey paas sey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) guzrey aur farmaya : bethey huye ki namaz khadey huye ki namaz sey (sawab mein) aadhi hoti hai.
1230,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (ghar sey) bahar tashrif laye to kuch log beth kar namaz padhtey nazar aaye to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bethey huye ki namaz khadey huye ki namaz sey aadhi hoti hai.
1231,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey sawal kya ke aadmi beth kar namaz padhey to kya hukm hai? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs khada ho kar namaz padhey , wo afzal hai aur jo shakhs beth kar namaz padhey , uskey liye khadey honey waley sey aadha sawab hai aur jo shakhs let kar namaz padhey , uskey liye bethney waley sey aadha sawab hai."
1232,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) us marz mein mubtala huye jis mein aap ki wafat hui . . padhi. aur abu-Muaawia ki riwayat mein ye alfaz hain : jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki bimari shadeed ho gaee . . padhi. . to (eik din (Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko namaz (ka waqt ho janey) ki ittilaa deney key liye hazir huye to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaho , logon ko namaz padha den . hum (ummahaatul-Momineen) ney arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool ! abu-Bakar narmdil aadmi hain. jab aap ki jagah (namaz padhaney) khadey hongey to (riqqat taari ho janey ki wajeh sey) roney lagengey aur namaz nahin padha sakengey. aap Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm dey den to wo namaz padha dengey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : abu-Bakar sey kaho logon ko namaz padhaein , tum to Yusuf ki sath waliyan ho.' ummul-mominin (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain : chunanche hamney Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko bula bheja , unhoney namaz padhaana shuru ki to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko apni tabiat mein kuch ifaaqa mehsus huwa . chunanche aap do aadmiyon ka sahara ley kar namaz key liye tashrif ley aaye , aap key qadmon (key zamin par jam kar na rakhey ja sakney) ki wajeh sey zamin par lakeer banti ja rahi thi. Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki aamad ka ehsas huwa to wo peechey hatney lagey . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen ishara kya ke apni jagah thehrey rahen. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (aagey) tashrif ley aaye yahan tak key dono as-haab ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key barabar bitha diya . chunanchey (ye namaz is tarah ada ki gaee ke) Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki iqtida (pairvi) kar rahey they aur (tamam) log Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki iqtida (pairvi) kar rahey they."
1233,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apni bimari key dinon mein Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya ke logon ko namaz padhaein , chunanche wo namazein padhatey rahey. (eik din) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ifaaqa mehsus kya to aap (hujra mubarak sey) bahar tashrif laye . us waqt Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) logon ko namaz padha rahey they. jab unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha to peechey hatney lagey . Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ishara farmaya ke apni jagah raho. tab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key pehlu mein unkey barabar beth gaey to Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki namaz ki iqtida (pairvi) kar rahey they aur doosrey log abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki iqtida (pairvi) mein namaz ada kar rahey they."
1234,"Hazrat Salim bin Ubaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par bimari ki haalat mein be-hoshi taari ho gaee , phir ifaaqa huwa to farmaya : kya namaz ka waqt ho gaya hai? Sahaba Raziallahu anhum ney kaha : ji haan . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Bilal sey kaho ke Azan den aur abu-Bakar sey kaho , logon ko namaz padhaein, phir Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par (dobara) be-hoshi taari ho gaee . ifaaqa huwa to farmaya : kya namaz ka waqt ho gaya ?' Sahaba Raziallahu anhum ney kaha : ji haan . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Bilal sey kaho ke Azan den aur abu-Bakar sey kaho , logon ko namaz padhaein . phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par) teesri baar ( be-hoshi taari ho gaee . ifaaqa huwa to farmaya : kya namaz ka waqt ho gaya hai? Sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum ney kaha : ji haan , Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Bilal sey kaho ke Azan den aur abu-Bakar sey kaho , logon ko namaz padhaein . Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ney arz kya : abba jaan naram dil aadmi hain, jab us maqam par khadey hongey to roney lagengey aur namaz nahin padha sakengey . agar aap kisi aur ko) namaz padhaaney ka ( hukm den ( to behtar hoga ( , phir Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par be-hoshi taari ho gaee . ifaaqa huwa to farmaya : Bilal sey kaho ke Azan den aur abu-Bakar sey kaho , logon ko namaz padhaein . tum ( aurten) to Yusuf ki sath waliyan ho. Raavi farmatey hain, chunanche Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha gaya to unhoney Azan di aur Hazrat abu-Bakar sey kaha gaya to unhoney logon ko namaz padhaai. uskey baad (eik din) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko kuch ifaaqa mehsus huwa to farmaya : kisi ko bulao jo mujhey sahara dey. chunanche Hazrat Barira (Raziallahu anha) aa gaeen, aur eik sahab bhi hazir ho gaey . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) un dono key saharey sey (masjid ki taraf) chaley. jab Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki nazar Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par padi to peechey hatney lagey . Nabi (Alaihissalam) ney isharey sey farmaya ke apni jagah thehrey rahen , phir Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aa kar Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key pehlu mein beth gaey yahan tak key abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney namaz mukammal kar li . uskey baad Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat ho gaee . Imam abu-Adbullah ( Ibne-Maja ( (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : ye hadees gharib hai, Nasar bin Ali key ilawa kisi ney isey riwayat nahin kya."
1235,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) us bimari mein they jis mein aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat hui to aap Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) key ghar tashrif farma they. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Ali ko bulao . Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ney arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool ! Hazrat abu-Bakar ko bula lein ? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bula lo. Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ney arz kya : Hazrat umr ko bula lein? farmaya : bula lo . Hazrat Umme al-Fazal (Raziallahu anha) ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko bula lein ? farmaya : haan . jab ye hazraat jama ho gaey to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney sar Mubarak utha kar dekha aur khamosh ho gaey . Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key paas sey uth jao . uskey baad Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko namaz ki ittilaa deney hazir huye . to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : abu-Bakar ko hukm do , logon ko namaz padha den . Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! abu-Bakar narm-dil aur kam bhale hi hain jab wo aap ko (imaamat key liye) mojud na paeyngey to ro padengey, (is par) log bhi (aap ko yad kar key gham zada ho jaeyngey aur) roney lagengey . agar aap Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko namaz padhaaney ka hukm den ( to behtar hoga), aakhir abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) (ghar sey) bahar tashrif laye aur logon ko namaz padhaai. uskey baad (eik din) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ifaaqa mehsus kya to do mardon key saharey (masjid ki taraf) rawana huye, aap key qadam Mubarak (badhti kamzori ki wajeh sey) zamin par lakeer banatey ja rahey they. Sahaba Raziallahu anhum ney jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko (masjid mein tashrif latey) dekha to subhan Allah keh kar abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko mutanabbeh kya. wo peechey hatney lagey to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen isharay sey farmaya ke apni jagah thehrey raho , phir Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye aur unkey daain taraf beth gaey . abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) khadey rahey , chunanche abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki iqtida (pairvi) kar rahey they aur (doosrey tamam) log Hazrat abu-Bakar ki iqtida (pairvi) kar rahey they. Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) ney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney qirat wahan sey shuru ki jahan abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) pahunchey they. Janab Wakee ney farmaya : yehi sunnat hai. Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) ney farmaya : usi bimari key doran mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat ho gaee."
1236,"Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) peechey reh gaey . hum (qafley key) logon tak pahunchey to Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) unhen eik rakat padha chukey they. unhoney jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki mojudgi ko mehsus kya to peechey hatney lagey. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen ishara farmaya ke namaz mukammal karen. (namaz sey farigh honey key baad) farmaya : aap ney achcha kya. isi tarah kya karen."
1237,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bimar ho gaey . aap key Sahaba mein sey chand afrad aap ki iyaadat key liye hazir huye . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney beth kar namaz padhi to unhoney aap ki iqtida (pairvi) mein khadey ho kar namaz shuru kar di . Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen ishara farmaya ke beth jao , namaz sey farigh ho kar farmaya : Imam isliye muqarrar kya gaya hai ke uski perwi ki jaey, isliye jab wo rukoo karey to tum rukoo karo, jab wo sar uthaey to tum sar uthao , jab wo beth kar namaz padhey to tum ( bhi) beth kar namaz padho ."
1238,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghodey sey gir padey aur aap ka jism Mubarak daain taraf sey zakhmi ho gaya . hum log Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki Iyadat (bimari ka haal poochney) key liye hazir huye. (isi beech mein) namaz ka waqt ho gaya, aap ney hamen beth kar namaz padhaai aur hamney aap key peechey beth kar namaz ada ki, namaz sey farigh ho kar Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Imam isliye muqarrar kya gaya hai ke uski perwi ki jaey. jab wo (Allahu-Akbar) kahey to tum (Allahu-Akbar) kaho , jab wo rukoo karey to tum rukoo karo, jab wo ( سَمِعَ اللهُ لِمَنْ حَمِدَه) kahey to tum ( رَبَّنَا وَلَكَ الْحَمْد ) kaho , jab wo sajda karey to tum bhi sajda karo, jab wo beth kar namaz padhaaey to tum sab log beth kar namaz padho ."
1239,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Imam isliye muqarrar kya gaya hai ke uski perwi ki jaey, jab wo ( Allahu-Akbar ) kahey to tum ( Allahu-Akbar ) kaho , jab wo rukoo karey to tum rukoo karo, jab wo ( سَمِعَ اللَّهُ لِمَنْ حَمِدَهُ ) kahey , tum ( رَبَّنَا وَلَكَ الْحَمْدُ ) kaho , agar wo khada ho kar namaz padhey to tum khadey ho kar namaz padho , agar wo beth kar namaz padhey to tum bhi beth kar namaz padho ."
1240,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bimar ho gaey. hamney aap key peechhey namaz padhi jabke aap beth kar namaz padha rahey they aur Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) (buland aawaz sey) takbeeren kehtey they, (yani) logon ko Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki takbir sunatey they. aap ney hamari taraf tawajjoh farmaai to hamen khadey dekha, Nabi (Alaihissalam) ney ishara farmaya to hum beth gaey aur hamney beth kar Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki namaz ki iqtida (pairvi) ki. salam pherney key baad aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum to Faarsiyon aur Romiyon ka sa kaam karney lagey they. wo baadshaahon key samney khadey rehtey hain jabke wo (badshah) bethey hotey hain, (isliye) is tarah na kiya karo. apney imaamon ki iqtida (pairvi) karo. jab Imam khada ho kar namaz padhey to tum bhi khadey ho kar namaz padho, agar wo beth kar namaz padhey to tum bhi beth kar namaz padho."
1241,"Abu-Malik Saad bin Tariq Ashjai (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey apney walid (Hazrat Tariq bin Ashim (Raziallahu anhu)) sey kaha, abba jaan ! aap ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key peechhey bhi namazein padhi hain aur Hazrat abu-Bakar , Hazrat umr , Hazrat Usman Raziallahu anhum key peechhey bhi aur yahan koofa mein Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) key peechhey bhi taqriban paanch saal namazein padhi hain, kya ye hazraat Fajr ki namaz mein qunoot kiya kartey they? unhoney farmaya : beta ! ye bidat hai."
1242,"Hazrat Ummul-mominin Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Fajr ki namaz mein qunoot padhney sey mana farma diya gaya tha."
1243,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Fajr ki namaz mein qunoot farmatey they. (qunoot mein) Arab key eik qabiley key khilaf eik mahiney tak bad dua kartey rahey they. phir usey tarak kar diya.
1244,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney jab Fajr ki namaz mein (rukoo sey) sar uthaya to farmaya : aey Allah ! Waleed bin Waleed, Salma bin Hisham, Ayash bin Rabee'a‬ Raziallahu anhum aur Makka key (doosrey) kamzor afrad ko (mushrikon sey) najat dey. aey Allah ! qabila muzir (key kafiron) par giraft ko shadeed tar kar dey aur un par Yusuf (Alaihissalam) (key zamaney) key salon jaisey (qehat aur sakhti key) saal musallat farma dey."
1245,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney namaz key doran mein do siyah janwaron, yani bichchhu aur sanp ko qatl karney ka hukm diya."
1246,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) namaz padh rahey they ke eik bichchhu ney dank maar diya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah bichchhu par lanat kerey. ye to na kisi namazi ko chhodta hai na ghair namazi ko, isey maar diya karo, حِلّ mein ho ya Haram mein."
1247,Janab ibne Abu-Raafey (Rahimahullah) apney walid sey aur wo unkey dada sey riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik bichchhu maar dala jabke aap namaz padh rahey they.
1248,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney do namazon, yani Fajr key baad suraj key tulu honey tak aur Asr key baad suraj key ghurub honey tak, key padhney sey mana farmaya hai."
1249,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Asr key baad koi namaz nahin yahan tak key suraj ghurub ho jaey aur Fajr key baad koi namaz nahin yahan tak key suraj tulu ho jaey."
1250,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney bayan kiya : merey paas qabile aitimad hazraat ney gawahi di un mein Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they aur merey nazdik un mein sab sey ziyada qabile aitimad Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) they ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Fajr key baad koi namaz nahin yahan tak key suraj tulu ho jaey aur Asr key baad koi namaz nahin yahan tak key suraj ghurub ho jaey."
1251,"Hazrat Amr bin Abasa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa to arz kiya : kya koi waqt Allah ko doosrey oqaat sey ziyada pyara bhi hota hai? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : haan, raat ka darmiyani hissa, tum jab tak chaho namaz (tahajjud) padho, yahan tak key subh saadiq tulu ho jaey, phir ruk jao yahan tak key suraj tulu ho jaey. jab tak wo is tarah (nazar aata) rahey jaisey dhaal hoti hai yahan tak key roshni ho jaey, phir jitni chaho namaz padho yahan tak key sutoon apney saye par qaaim ho jaey, phir (namaz sey) perhez karo yahan tak key suraj dhal jaey kyonkey dophar ko jahannam dehkaai jati hai, phir jitni chaho namaz padho yahan tak key Asr ki namaz padh lo, phir (namaz sey) rukey raho yahan tak key suraj ghurub ho jaey kyonkey wo shetan key do seengon key darmiyan ghurub hota aur shetan key do seengon key darmiyan tulu hota hai."
1252,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Safwan bin Muattal (Raziallahu anhu) ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey masla puchha to kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! main aap sey wo baat poochhta hun jis sey aap waqif hain aur main us sey la ilm hun. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wo kya chiz hai? unhoney kaha : kya raat aur din key oqaat mein sey koi aisa waqt bhi hai jis mein namaz padhna makrooh hai? farmaya : haan, jab to subah ki namaz padh ley to namaz chhod dey yahan tak key suraj nikal aaye kyonkey wo shetan key do seengon key darmiyan tulu hota hai, phir (nafl) namaz padh kyonkey (us waqt mein) namaz mein (farishtey) hazir hotey hain. aur wo qubul hoti hai yahan tak key suraj terey sar par neze ki tarah khada ho jaey. jab wo neze ki tarah terey sar par ho to namaz tarak kar dey kyonkey us waqt jahannam dehkaai jati hai aur uskey darwazey kholey jatey hain yahan tak key suraj teri daain taraf dhal aaye jab wo dhal jaey to us waqt ki namaz mein (farishtey) hazir hotey hain aur wo qubul hoti hai. (uskey baad sunnatein nafl waghera padh saktey ho) yahan tak key to Asr ki namaz padh ley, phir namaz chhodey rakh yahan tak key suraj ghurub ho jaey."
1253,"Hazrat abu-Adbullah (Abdur-Rehman bin Aseela) Sunabihi (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : suraj shetan key do seengon key darmiyan tulu hota hai. ya farmaya : uskey sath shetan key seeng tulu hotey hain, jab suraj buland ho jata hai to shetan us sey alag ho jata hai, jab wo aasman key darmiyan mein pahunchta hai to shetan us sey mil jata hai, jab dhal jata hai to wo alag ho jata hai, phir jab suraj ghurub honey key qarib hota hai to shetan us sey mil jata hai, jab ghurub ho jaey to alag ho jata hai. isliye un teen oqaat mein namaz na padha karo."
1254,"Hazrat Juber bin Mut-im (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey bani Abd Munaaf ! koi shakhs raat ya din mein jis waqt bhi is ghar ka tawaf karna aur namaz padhna chahey, tum usey mana na karna."
1255,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : shayad tumhen aisey log milen jo namaz ko be waqt ada kartey hon. agar tum unhen pao to gharon mein us waqt namaz ada kar liya karo jo tumhen malum hai (ke ye sahih waqt hai), phir unkey sath bhi namaz padh lo aur usey nafl samajh lo."
1256,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : namaz waqt par ada kar, phir agar tujhey Imam logon ko namaz parhata mil jaey to unkey sath bhi namaz padh ley aur (awwal waqt ada kar key) tu ney apni namaz mehfooz kar li warna (dobara padhney sey) wo terey liye nafl bin gaee."
1257,"Hazrat Ubada bin Samit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mustaqbil mein aisey hukmran hongey jinhen dusri cheezen namaz sey mashghool kar dengi aur wo namazon ko unkey oqaat sey muakhar kar dengey . tum unkey sath padhi hui apni namaz ko nafl samajh lena."
1258,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney namaze khof key barey mein farmaya : Imam apney saath wali jamaat ko namaz padhaaey, wo log eik sajda (eik rakat) ada karen. aur unka eik (doosra) giroh in (namaz ada karney walon) key aur dushman key darmiyan ho, phir wo log (dushman key muqabil) chaley jaeyn jinhoney apney Ameer key sath eik sajda ada kiya hai (eik rakat padhi hai), wo un logon ki jagah ley lein, jinhoney namaz nahin padhi aur jinhoney namaz nahin padhi thi wo aagey aa kar apney Ameer key sath eik sajda (eik rakat) ada kar lein, phir unka Ameer salam pher dey kyonkey usney apni namaz (puri) padh li hai aur dono girohon key afrad apney apney tor par eik eik sajda (rakat) ada kar lein agar khof us sey bhi shadeed ho to chaltey chaltey ya sawari par (jis tarah mumkin ho namaz padh lein). Raavi ney kaha : hadees mein sajde sey murad rakat hai."
1259,"Hazrat Sehal bin Abu-Hasma (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney namaze khof key barey mein farmaya : Imam qibley ki taraf munh kar key khada ho jaey aur mujahideen ki eik jamaat uskey sath (uski iqtida (pairvi) mein namaz ada karney key liye) khadi ho jaey. dusri jamaat dushman key muqabil rahey, un logon key chehrey saf ki taraf hongey. wo unhen eik rakat padhaaeyga aur wo apni jagah eik rukoo aur do sajdey ada kar leingey, phir wo un ki jagah chaley jaeyngey aur wo (doosri jamaat key afrad) aa jaeyngey. Imam key sath mil kar eik rukoo aur do sajdey kerengey (Imam eik rakat padhaaeyga). is tarah Imam ki do rakatein ho jaeyngi aur in (muqtadiyon) ki eik eik rakat , phir wo (dono girohon key muqtadi) eik eik rukoo aur do-do sajdey (apney apney) kar leingey. Imam Ibne-Maja key ustaad Muhammad bin Bashaar kehtey hain : mainey Yahya bin Saeed Qataan sey is hadees key barey mein puchha to unhoney mujhey yehi hadees Shoba sey Abdur-Rehman key wastey sey Qasim sey bayan ki (jabke yehi hadees jab unhoney Yahya bin Saeed Ansari sey bayan ki to unhoney Abdur-Rehman ka wasta zikr nahin kiya). aur ye hadees bayan kartey huye Yahya bin Saeed Qataan ney mujhey kaha ke is ko Ansari ki hadees key sath hi likh lo mujhey hadees yad nahin, Yahya ney kaha : lekin wo Yahya bin Saeed Ansari ki hadees ki jaisi hi hai."
1260,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Sahaba ko namaze khof padhaai. aap ney un sab key sath rukoo kiya, phir Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney sajdey kiye aur aap key qarib wali saf ney bhi sajdey kiye aur dusri saf key afrad khadey rahey. jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (sajdon sey farigh ho kar) uthey to un logon ney (jo khadey rahey they) khud hi do do sajdey kar liye , phir agli saf key log peechhey chaley gaey yahan tak key in (pichhli saf walon) ki jagah ja khadey huye. wo log (pichhli saf waley) un logon key darmiyan sey guzar kar pehli saf walon ki jagah aa khadey huye. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney un dono (safon walon) key sath mil kar rukoo kiya, phir Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney sajdey kiye aur is saf walon ney bhi jo  (ab) aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey qarib thi. jab unhoney (sajdon sey farigh ho kar) sar uthaya to unhon (doosri saf walon) ney do sajdey kar liye, un sab ney rukoo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath kiya tha. aur eik jamaat ney sajdey apney apney kiye, us waqt dushman qibley ki janib tha."
1261,"Hazrat Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : suraj aur chaand ko logon mein sey kisi key marney par girahan nahin lagta, jab tum ye chiz dekho to khadey ho kar namaz padho."
1262,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein suraj girahan ho gaya, aap ghabraey huye kapda khinchtey (ghar sey) bahar tashrif laye yahan tak key masjid mein aagaey, aap namaz padhte rahey yahan tak key suraj roshan ho gaya, iskey baad farmaya : baaz logon ka khayal hai ke suraj aur chaand ko girahan badey logon mein sey kisi ki maut ki wajeh sey lagta hai, aisa hergiz nahin hai. suraj aur chaand ko kisi ki maut ya zindagi ki wajeh sey girahan nahin lagta. (lekin) Allah Taala jab makhluq mein sey kisi chiz par tajalli farmata hai to wo aajizi ka izhar karti hai."
1263,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zindagi mein (eik baar) suraj ko girahan laga to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghar sey nikal kar masjid mein tashrif ley gaey. aap ney khadey ho kar takbir (tahreema) kahi. Sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum aap key peechhey safein baandhey huye they. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney taweel (lambi) qirat farmaai, phir Allahu-Akbar keh kar taweel (lamba) rukoo kiya, phir sar utha kar ( سَمِعَ اللَّهُ لِمَنْ حَمِدَهُ رَبَّنَا وَلَكَ الْحَمْدُ ) farmaya : phir qiyam farmaya aur taweel (lambi) qirat ki jo pehli qirat sey kam taweel (lambi) thi , phir Allahu-Akbar keh kar taweel (lamba) rukoo kiya jo pehley rukoo sey mukhtasar (kam) tha, phir farmaya : ( سَمِعَ اللَّهُ لِمَنْ حَمِدَهُ رَبَّنَا وَلَكَ الْحَمْدُ ) (iskey baad sajdey kar key ye rakat mukammal ki), phir dusri rakat mein bhi isi tarah kiya. is tarah purey chaar rukoo aur chaar sajdey kiye. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key namaz sey farigh honey sey pehley suraj roshan ho chuka tha, phir khadey ho kar khutba diya, is mein Allah ki shaayaan shaan hamd aur sanaa bayan farmaai. uskey baad farmaya : suraj aur chaand Allah ki nishaniyon mein sey do nishaniyan hain, inhen kisi ki maut ya zindagi ki wajeh sey girahan nahin lagta . jab tum inhen (girahan laga huwa) dekho to namaz ki taraf bhago."
1264,"Hazrat Samura bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein suraj girahan ki namaz padhaai aur hamein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki (qirat ki) aawaz sunai nahin dey rahi thi. (siree qirat ki.)"
1265,"Hazrat Asma binte Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney suraj girahan ki namaz padhaai. aap khadey huye aur taweel (lamba) qiyam farmaya , phir rukoo kiya to bahut taweel (lamba) rukoo kiya, phir sar uthaya aur qiyam kiya to bahut taweel qiyam (lamba) kya, phir (dobara) rukoo kiya to bahut taweel (lamba) rukoo kiya, phir sar uthaya (aur qauma kya), phir sajda kiya to bahut taweel (lamba) sajda kiya, phir sar uthaya (aur jalsaa kiya), phir sajda kiya to bahut taweel (lamba) sajda kiya, phir sar uthaya aur qiyam kiya to bahut taweel (lamba) qiyam kiya, phir rukoo kya to bahut taweel (lamba) rukoo kiya, phir sar utha kar qiyam kiya to bahut taweel (lamba) qiyam kya, phir rukoo kiya to taweel (lamba) rukoo kiya, phir sar uthaya (aur qauma kiya) phir sajda kiya to taweel (lamba) sajda kiya, phir sar uthaya , phir sajda kya to taweel sajda (lamba) kiya, phir namaz sey farigh huye to farmaya : jannat mujh sey qarib ho gaee thi yahan tak key agar main jur'at karta to uska phal tod kar tumharey paas ley aata aur jahannam mujh sey qarib hui yahan tak key mainey kaha : aey Rab ! (kya logon par azab aa jaeyga) jabkey main in key darmiyan mojud hun?  Hazrat Nafey bin umr (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : mera khayal hai unhoney (ibne-Abi Muleka ney hadees bayan kartey huye) ye alfaz bhi farmaae they ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mainey (jahannam mein) eik aurat dekhi jisey uski eik billi panje maar rahi thi. mainey kaha : iska kya maamla hai? to unhoney kaha : usney is (billi) ko band kar diya tha yahan tak key wo bhook sey mar gaee, na usney isey (khud) khana diya, na isey chhoda ke zamin key keedey makodey kha leti."
1266,"Hazrat Is-haq bin Abdullah bin Kinaana (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai unhoney kaha : mujhey (eik shehar key) Ameer ney Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) ki khidmat mein bheja ke un sey namaz istisqaa ka masla daryaft karun. Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) ney farmaya : unhen mujh sey khud poochh leney mein kya chiz rukaawat thi? phir farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aajizi key sath saada libas mein, khushu aur khuzooa' key sath, aahista raftaar sey, gidh-gidate huye (Eid gaah ki taraf) rawana huye, phir aap ney do rakat namaz ada ki jis tarah Eid key moqey par padhi jati hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney tumharey is khutbey jaisa khutba nahin diya tha."
1267,"Hazrat Ibaad bin Tameem (Rahimahullah) ney (apney Maa sharek chacha) Hazrat Abdullah bin Zaid bin Aasim (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat ki ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) barish ki dua key liye Eid-gaah tashrif ley gaey. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney qibley ki taraf munh kiya, apni chadar palti aur do rakat namaz ada ki. Imam Abu-Bakar bin Muhammad bin Hazam key shagrid Yahya bin Saeed ney bhi in sey mazkura baala riwayat ki tarah bayan ki. Janab Masoodi (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : mainey abu-Bakar bin Muhammad bin Amr (Rahimahullah) sey daryaft kiya : kya Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney chadar ka ooper wala hissa nichey kiya tha, ya daayan hissa baain taraf kiya tha? unhoney farmaya : nahin, balke daayan hissa baain taraf kiya tha."
1268,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera Raziallahu anhu sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik din Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) barish ki dua karney key liye bahar tashrif ley gaey. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Azan aur iqaamat kahlwaae baghair hamein do rakatein padhaaeen, phir khutba diya, Allah sey dua ki aur haath uthaey huye qibla rukh ho gaey, phir aap ney apni chadar ko palta, yani daain hissey ko baain taraf aur baain ko daain taraf kar liya."
1269,"Hazrat Shurehbil bin Samt (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Hazrat Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : Kaab bin Murra ! hamein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki hadees sunaaiye aur ehtiyat kijiye. Hazrat Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! hamarey liye pani ki dua kijiye. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apney haath utha diye aur farmaya : ( اللَّهُمَّ اسْقِنَا غَيْثًا مَرِيئًا مَرِيعًا طَبَقًا عَاجِلاً غَيْرَ رَائِثٍ نَافِعًا غَيْرَ ضَارّ ), ''aey Allah ! hum par barish nazil farma jo khush-gawaar ho, (barkaton aur rizq mein) izafa kar deney wali ho, har jagah barasney wali ho (jal-thal eik kar dey) jaldi nazil honey wali ho, takheer (deri) karney wali na ho, faaedey deney wali ho, nuqsan deh na ho.'' (Allah taala ney dua qubul farmaai) abhi namaze Juma sey farigh nahin huye they ke barish aa gaee. (barish musalsal hoti rahi yahan tak key) log khidmat mein hazir huye aur barish (ki kasrat) ki shikayat ki, unhoney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! (hamarey to) makaan gir gaey hain, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (اللَّهُمَّ حَوَالَيْنَا وَلاَ عَلَيْنَا), ''aey Allah ! hamarey ird-gird (barish barsa) hum par na barsa."" fauran (badal phat kar daain baain bikharne lag gaya."
1270,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) (khana-badosh) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! main aap key paas aisey logon key paas sey aaya hun jinka koi charwaahaa safar kharch nahin leta aur koi saand dam nahin hilaataa. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) member par tashrif farma huye, Allah ki tareef ki, phir farmaya : ( اللَّهُمَّ اسْقِنَا غَيْثًا مُغِيثًا مَرِيئًا طَبَقًا مَرِيعًا غَدَقًا عَاجِلاً غَيْرَ رَائِثٍ ), ''aey Allah ! hum par barish nazil farma jis sey hamari fariyad poori ho jaey, khushgawar ho, har jagah barasney wali ho, (rizq mein) izafa karney wali ho, badey qatron wali ho, jaldi nazil honey wali ho, takheer (deri) karney wali na ho.'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) member sey nichey tashrif ley aaye (iskey baad) jis samt sey bhi koi (musafir) aaya, usney yehi kaha : hamarey yahan barish hui hai."
1271,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney barish ki dua ki (aur haath khub uthaey ( yahan tak key mujhey aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki baghlon ki safedi nazar aa gaee . (hadees key Raavi) Hazrat Moatamir (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain : mera khayal hai ke namaz istisqaa key moqey par aisa huwa ."
1272,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main baaz oqaat Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key Chehrey aqdas ko dekhta jabke aap member par (barish ki dua key liye) tashrif farma hotey aur aap key member par utarney sey pehley Madiney ka har par naala purey zor sey bahney lagta to mujhey shayer ka ye sher yad aa jata : wo safed faam shakhsiyat (Rasool akram (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam)) jis key chehrey key waseeley sey badal sey barish maangi jati hai, yatimon ka nigehban , bewaaon ka muhafiz . ye Abu-Talib ka kalam hai."
1273,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key barey mein gawahi deta hun ke aap ney khutbey sey pehley (eid ki) namaz padhi , phir khutba diya, aap ney mehsus kya ke main aurton ko) apni baat (nahin suna saka) kyonkey wo door thin (chunanche aap khawatin key paas tashrif ley gaey aur unhen waaz o nasihat ki aur unhen sadqa karney ka hukm diya. Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ney apney haath is tarah kiye huye they, chunanche (har) aurat ney baali, angoothi aur (aisi hi) chiz ( jo kisi key paas thi kapdey mein) dalna shuru kar di ."
1274,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eid key din baghair Azan aur baghair iqaamat key ( eid ki) namaz ada farmaai .
1275,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Marwan ney eid key din member nikalwaaya, (aur eid gaah mein member par khutba diya (aur namaz sey pehley khutba diya, eik aadmi ney uth kar kaha : aey Marwan! aap ney khilafe-sunnat kaam kya hai. aap ney eid key din member nikala hai. (masjid sey utha kar eid gaah mein laye hain) halanke (Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein) wo nikala nahin jata tha, aur aap ney namaz sey pehley khutba shuru kar diya, halanke ibtida (shuruat) khutbey sey nahin huwa karti thi ( balke pehley namaz hoti thi .) Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya is shakhs ney apna farz ada kar diya hai. mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna hai : jo shakhs koi burai dekhey aur usey apney haath sey tabdeel karney ki taqat ho to usey chahiye ke apney haath sey tabdeel kar dey. agar taqat na ho to apni zaban sey (mana kar dey) agar zaban sey (mana karney ki)taqat na ho to dil sey (nafrat kerey) aur ye sab sey kamzor eman hai."
1276,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) , unkey baad Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) , phir unkey baad Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) eid ki namaz khutbey sey pehley ada farmatey they."
1277,Hazrat Saad Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key muazzan sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eidain ki namaz mein pehli rakat mein qirat sey pehley saat takbeerein aur dusri rakat mein qirat sey pehley paanch takbeerein kehtey they.
1278,Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid (Hazrat Shuaib bin Muhammad (Rahimahullah) sey aur wo apney dada (Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma)) sey riwayat kartey hain ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney namaaz eid mein saat aur paanch takbeerein kahin .
1279,Hazrat Kasir bin Abdullah (Rahimahullah) apney walid (Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Auf (Rahimahullah) sey aur wo unkey dada (Hazrat Amr bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat kartey hain ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney dono Eidon mein pehli rakat mein saat takbeerein aur dusri rakat mein paanch takbeerein kahin.
1280,ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eidul-Fitr aur eidul-azhaa ( ki namaz ( mein saat aur paanch takbeerein kahin jin mein rukoo ki takbeerein shamil nahin.
1281,Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) dono Eidon mein (سَبِّحِ اسْمَ رَبِّكَ الأَعْلَى ) aur) هَلْ أَتَاكَ حَدِيثُ الْغَاشِيَةِ ) padha kartey they.
1282,"Hazrat Ubedullah bin Abdullah (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) eid key din bahar tashrif laye, unhoney Hazrat abu Waqid Lesi (Raziallahu anhu) sey daryaft karaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) us din (eid key din) kin Suraton ki qirat farmatey they? abu Waqid (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Sura Qaaf aur Sura Qamar"
1283,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eidain mein (سَبِّحِ اسْمَ رَبِّكَ الأَعْلَى ) aur) هَلْ أَتَاكَ حَدِيثُ الْغَاشِيَةِ ) padha kartey they.
1284,"Hazrat Abu Kahil Ehsami (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko oontni par khutba irshad farmatey dekha aur eik Habshi ney oontni ki mahaar pakad rakhi thi ."
1285,"Hazrat Abu Kahil Qais bin aaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko eik khoobsurat oontni par sawar ho kar khutba detey huye suna aur eik Habshi ney uski mahaar thaam rakhi thi ."
1286,Hazrat Salma bin Nabeet apney walid (Hazrat Nabeet bin Shuret (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat kartey hain ke unhoney Haj kya aur farmaya : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko oontni par (sawar ho kar) khutba detey dekha hai.
1287,"Hazrat Saad al-Qurz (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khutbey key doran mein takbeerein kaha kartey they. eidain key khutbey mein kasrat sey takbeerein kehtey they."
1288,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eid key din bahar ( eid gaah mein) tashrif ley jatey they logon ko do rakat namaz padhatey , phir salam pher kar apney paon par khadey ho jatey . logon ki taraf Chehrey Mubarak kar letey jabke log bethey rehtey . aap farmatey : sadqa karo, sadqa karo . to ziyada tar aurten sadqa kartin, baali, angoothi aur (is tarah ki) koi chiz (sadqey mein pesh kartiin) agar aap koi lashkar rawana karney ki zarurat mehsus farmatey to ye baat bhi logon ko bata detey warna (khutba khatam kar key) wapis aa jatey ."
1289,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eidul-Fitr ya Eidul-Azha key din Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bahar ( maidan mein) tashrif ley gaey . aap ney khadey ho kar khutba diya, phir thodi der beth gaey, phir khadey ho gaey (aur khutba diya)."
1290,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Saaib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath namaz eid mein shareek huwa , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen eid ki namaz padhaai, phir farmaya : hamney namaz padh li hai. ( ab) jo shakhs khutba sunney key liye bethna chahey beth jaey aur jo shakhs jana chahey chala jaey ."
1291,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bahar (maidan mein) tashrif ley gaey aur logon ko namaze-Eid padhaai. is sey pehley ya baad mein koi (nafl) namaz ada nahin ki.
1292,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid sey, aur wo apney dada (Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhuma)) sey riwayat bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney namaz eid key moqey par is sey pehley ya baad mein namaz (nafl) ada nahin farmaai."
1293,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eid ki namaz sey pehley koi namaz nahin padhtey they, phir jab (namaze-eid ki adaegi key baad ghar) wapis tashrif latey to do rakat namaz padhtey."
1294,Hazrat Saad al-Qurz (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) namaz eid key liye pedal tashrif ley jatey they aur pedal wapis aatey they.
1295,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) namaze-eid key liye pedal tashrif ley jatey they aur pedal wapis aatey they."
1296,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : namaz eid key liye chal kar jana sunnat hai."
1297,Hazrat abu-Raafey (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eid ki namaz key liye pedal jatey they.
1298,"Hazrat Saad al-Qurz (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab eidain ki namaz key liye tashrif ley jatey to Hazrat Saeed bin abul-Aas key ghar key paas sey guzartey , phir khemon walon key paas sey guzartey , phir ( namaz key baad) doosrey raastey sey , yani banu Zureq key raastey sey wapis hotey, phir Hazrat Ammar bin Yasir (Raziallahu anhuma) key ghar key paas sey aur Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) key ghar key paas sey guzar kar maidan mein pahunchtey.) aur wahan sey masjide-nabawi aur Ummahatul-Momineen key gharon ki taraf chaltey.)"
1299,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke wo eid ki namaz key liye eik raastey sey jatey aur doosrey sey wapis aatey aur bayan kartey ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bhi isi tarah kartey they.
1300,"Hazrat abu-Raafey (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eid ki namaz key liye pedal tashrif ley jatey they aur jis raastey sey jatey they, uskey ilawa doosrey raastey sey wapas tashrif latey they."
1301,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab eid ki namaz key liye bahar tashrif ley jatey, to jis raastey sey jatey, uskey siwa doosrey raastey sey wapis aatey they."
1302,"Hazrat Aamir (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat ayaaz Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ney eik eid Anbaar mein manaai to farmaya : kya baat hai main tumhen gatey-bajatey nahin dekh raha jis tarah Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki mojudgi mein gaana-bajana hota tha?"
1303,"Hazrat Qais bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key ehade-Mubarak mein jo jo kuch hota tha, wo sab mainey (tum logon ko kartey) dekh liya hai, siwaye eik chiz key. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki mojudgi mein eidul-fitr key din gana-bajana hota tha. (jo tum ney tarak kar diya hai.) Imam sahab key shagrid abul-Hasan ney yehi hadees apni teen sanadon, یعنی بواسطہ ابن دیزیل an آدم an شیبان an جابر an عامر اور بواسطہ إسرائیل an جابر اور بواسطہ إبراہیم بن نصر an أبی Naeem an شریک an أبی إسحاق an عامرbayan ki."
1304,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eid key din subh key waqt eid gaah tashrif ley jatey , aap key aagey aagey barchhi ley jaai jati . jab aap eid gaah pahunchtey to aap key samney barchhi gaad di jati , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uski taraf munh kar key namaz ada kartey . uski wajeh ye thi ke eid gaah eik khula maidan thi, is mein koi aisi chiz nahin thi jisey sutra banaya ja sakey ."
1305,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eid key din ya kisi aur din jab namaz ada farmatey to aap key samney barchhi gaad di jati . aap uski taraf munh kar key namaz ada farmatey aur log aap key peechey khadey ho jatey they . Imam Nafey (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : isi wajeh sey khulafaa ney ye tariqa ikhtiyar kya hai."
1306,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eid-gaah mein eid ki namaz barchhi ko sutra bana kar ada farmaai.
1307,"Hazrat Umme Atiya (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen hukm diya ke hum eidul-fitr aur eidul-azha mein aurton ko ley kar jaeyn. Umme Atiya (Raziallahu anha) ney bayan farmaya ke hamney arz kya : ye farmaiye ke agar hum mein sey kisi aurat key paas chadar na ho? (to wo kya kerey?) aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : usey uski behan apni chadar odha dey ."
1308,"Hazrat Umme Atiya (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : no-jawan, parda-nasheen bachchiyon ko bhi (namaz eid key liye) gharon sey bahar (eid gaah mein) ley kar aao , unhen chahiye ke wo eid mein aur musalmanon ki dua mein hazir hun . haiz wali aurten aam logon ( namaz padhney wali aurton) ki namaz ki jagah sey alag rahen ."
1309,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eidain mein apni sahab zadiyon aur khawatin ko ghar sey bahar (eid gaah mein) ley jaya kartey they.
1310,"Hazrat Ayas bin Abu-Ramla Shami (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey eik aadmi ko Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) sey sawal kartey suna : kya aap Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath eik din mein do Eidon ( Juma aur eid) mein hazir huye hain? unhoney kaha : haan . usney kaha : phir Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kya kartey they? farmaya : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eid ki namaz ada farmaai , phir Jumey ki rukhsat dey di, phir farmaya : jo koi (Jumey ki namaz) padhna chahey padh ley ."
1311,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tumharey is din mein do eidein jama ho gaee hain to jo shakhs chahey uskey liye ye (namaz eid) Jumey key badley kifaayat kereygi aur hum inshaAllah Juma padheingey . Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney baqiiya key doosrey shagrid Yazeed bin Abde-Rabba sey Muhammad bin Yahya key wastey sey Hazrat Abu-Hurera ki sanad sey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey mazkura riwayat ki misl bayan kya."
1312,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein do eidein (eik din mein) jama ho gaeen . aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney logon ko (eid ki) namaz padhaai , phir farmaya : jo shakhs Jumey ki namaz mein aana chahey aa jaey jo peechey rehna chahey peechey reh jaey ."
1313,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein (eik dafa) eid key din barish ho gaee to aap ney masjid mein namaz  (eid) padhaai ."
1314,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney musalmanon key ilaqey mein eidein key moqey par hathiyar pehanney sey mana farmaya , illa ye ke wo dushman key muqabil hon."
1315,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eidul-fitr aur eidul-azhaa key din ghusl kya kartey they."
1316,"Hazrat Faaka bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eidul-Fitr key din , qurbani key din aur Arfa key din ghusl kartey they, Hazrat Faaka (Raziallahu anhu) bhi un dinon mein apney ghar walon ko ghusl karney ka hukm diya kartey they."
1317,Hazrat Abdullah bin Basar (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke wo eidul-fitr ya eidul-azha key din logon key sath (eid gaah ki taraf) rawana huye . unhoney Imam key der karney ko na pasand farmaya. aur farmaya : hum to us waqt tak farigh ho jaya kartey they. us waqt nafl namaz ki adaegi ka waqt ho chuka tha.
1318,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat ko do do rakat namaz ada kartey they."
1319,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : raat ki namaz do do rakat hai."
1320,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey raat ki namaz (tahajjud) key barey mein sawal kya gaya to aap ney farmaya : (namazi ko chahiye ke) do-do rakat padhta rahey, jab subh saadiq ho janey ka khof mehsus ho to eik witr padh ley ."
1321,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat ko do-do rakat namaz padhtey they."
1322,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : raat aur din ki (nafl) namaz do do rakat hai."
1323,"Hazrat Umme-Haani bint Abu-Talib (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Fateh Makka key roz zuha ki namaz aath rakat ada ki aur har do rakat par salam phera."
1324,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har do rakat mein salam hai."
1325,"Hazrat Muttalib bin abu-Wadaaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : raat ki namaz do do rakat hai, har do rakat key baad tashahud hai aur aajizi aur pasti ka izhar hai, aur haath utha kar kaho : aey Allah ! mujhey bakhsh dey , jisney aisey na kya, uski namaz naqis hai."
1326,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney (Allah key vaadon par) eman rakhtey huye, sawab ki niyat sey Ramzan key Rozey rakhey aur Ramzan ka qiyam kiya, uskey wo gunah maaf kar diye jaeyngey jo pehley (sarzad) ho chukey hain."
1327,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath Ramzan key rozey rakhey. aap ney un dinon mein qiyam na farmaya yahan tak key saat raaten baqi reh gaeen to saatwen raat aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen namaz (taraaweeh) padhaai yahan tak key taqriban tihai raat guzar gaee, phir us sey muttasil (lagi hui) chati raat aai to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney qiyam na farmaya, phir us sey muttasil paanchwen raat aai to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen namaz (taraaweeh) padhaai yahan tak key taqriban aadhi raat guzar gaee. mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! kaash! aap hamen is raat ka baqi hissa bhi ata farmatey (puri raat qiyam farmatey). to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Imam key sath uskey farigh honey tak qiyam karta hai (uska) wo (qiyam) puri raat key (qiyam key) barabar hota hai. phir us sey muttasil chauthi raat aai to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney qiyam na farmaya. phir us sey muttasil teesri raat aai to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apni khawatin ko aur ehale khana ko ikhatta kiya, aur (bahut ziyada) log bhi jama ho gaey. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen namaz padhaai yahan tak key hamein khatra mehsus huwa ke hamari falah chhoot jaeygi. (abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey) puchha gaya : falah ka kya matlab hai? farmaya : sehri ka khana, phir farmaya : iskey baad mahiney ki baqi raaton mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein namaz (taraaweeh) nahin padhaai."
1328,"Hazrat Nazar bin Sheban (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : meri mulaqat Hazrat abu-Salma bin Abdur-Rehman (Rahimahullah) sey hui. mainey kaha : mujhey koi hadees sunaaiye jo aap ney apney walid sey maahe Ramzan key barey mein suni ho. unhoney kaha : achchha. mujhey walid sahab (Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf Zohri (Raziallahu anhu)) ney hadees sunai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney maah Ramzan ka zikr kiya to farmaya : ye aisa mahina hai jis key rozey Allah ney tum par farz kiye hain aur mainey tumharey liye uski raaton key qiyam ka tariqa jari kiya hai. chunanche jo shakhs eman rakhtey huye aur sawab ki niyat sey uskey rozey rakhega aur qiyam kerega, wo gunahon sey is tarah nikal (kar pak saaf ho) jaeyga jis tarah us din (pak saaf) tha jab wo apni maa key yahan paida huwa tha."
1329,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : shetan raat ko insan key sar key pichhley hissey mein rassi sey teen girhein lagata hai. agar insan jaag kar Allah ka zikr karey to eik gireh khul jati hai, phir jab uth kar wuzu kar leta hai to eik (aur) gireh khul jati hai, phir jab namaz padhney khada ho jata hai to uski tamam girhein khul jati hain. chunanche wo subah ko chaaq aur chauband aur khush baash hota hai, usey bhalai mil gaee hoti hai. agar (insan) ye kaam na karey to subah ko sust aur bojhal tabiat hota hai, usey bhalai nahin mili hoti."
1330,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki mojudgi main eik shakhs ka zikr huwa ke wo raat sey subah tak (sari raat) soyaa raha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya is shakhs key kanon mein shetan ney peshab kar diya tha."
1331,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : falan ki tarah na ho jana. wo raat ko qiyam kiya karta tha, phir usney raat ka qiyam (tahajjud padhna) tarak kar diya."
1332,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Hazrat Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Dawud (Alaihissalam) ki walida ney Hazrat Suleman (Alaihissalam) (Alaihissalam) sey farmaya : piyarey betey ! raat ko ziyada na soyaa karo, raat ko ziyada soney ki wajeh sey insan qiyamat key din muflis ho jaeyga."
1333,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs raat ko ziyada namaz padhey, uska chehra din ko khoobsurat ho jata hai."
1334,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Salam (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Madina shareef tashrif laye to log fauran aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho gaey (jamghataa ho gaya), logon ney (khushi sey eik doosrey ko) kaha : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif ley aaye hain. logon key sath main bhi aap ki ziyaarat key liye gaya, jab mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key Chehrey aqdas ko tawajjoh sey dekha to mujhey yaqin ho gaya ke aap ka chehra, kisi jhootey aadmi ka chehra nahin. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney sab sey pehley jo kalam farmaya, wo ye tha : logo ! salam ko aam karo, khana khilaya karo, raat ko jab log so rahey hon to tum namaz padha karo, salamti key sath jannat mein dakhil ho jaogey."
1335,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed aur Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab aadmi raat ko jaagey aur apni biwi ko bhi jagaaey, phir wo dono do rakat namaz padhein to unkey naam Allah ka bahut ziyada zikr karney waley mardon aur bahut ziyada zikr karney wali aurton mein likh diye jatey hain."
1336,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala us mard par rehmat farmaaey jisney raat ko jaag kar namaz padhi aur apni biwi ko jagaya to usney bhi namaz padhi, agar aurat ney (jaagney sey) inkar kiya to us (mard) ney uskey chehrey par pani key chheentey maarey. Allah Taala us aurat par reham farmaai jisney raat ko jaag kar namaz padhi aur apney khawind ko jagaya to usney bhi namaz padhi. agar mard ney (jaagney sey) inkar kiya to us (aurat) ney mard key chehrey par pani key chheentey maarey."
1337,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Saaib (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Hazrat Saad bin abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey yahan tashrif laye, us waqt un ki beenai khatam ho chuki thi. mainey salam kiya to unhoney farmaya : tum kon ho? mainey bataya (ke Abdur-Rehman bin Saaib hun) to farmaya : bhatijey ko khush aamadeed ! mujhey malum huwa hai ke tum Quran Majeed ki tilawat badi umda aawaz sey kartey ho. mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye irshade Mubarak suna hai : ye Quran gham key sath nazil huwa hai, jab tum isey padho to roya karo, ronaa na aaye to takalluf sey ro'o aur isey achchhi aawaz sey padho. jo isey achchhi aawaz sey (tajweed key usoolon key mutabiq) na padhey, wo hum mein sey nahin."
1338,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zindagi-mubaarka main eik raat Isha key baad mujhey (khidmat mein hazir honey mein) der ho gaee, phir main aai to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum kahan thin? mainey kaha : main aap key eik Sahaba ki qirat sun rahi thi, mainey kisi aur ki aisi (umda) qirat aur aawaz nahin suni. Ummul-mominin ney bayan farmaya : Allah key Nabi uth khadey huye, main bhi uth kar aap key sath gaee yahan tak key aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney bhi uski qirat suni, phir meri taraf mutawajjeh ho kar farmaya : ye Hazrat Abu-Huzaifa (Raziallahu anhu) key Mola Salim hain. Allah ki tareef hai (aur uska shukar hai) jisney meri ummat mein aisey afrad paida farmaey."
1339,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Quran ki tilawat mein achchhi aawaz wala wo hai jisey tum tilawat kartey sun kar ye guman karo ke wo Allah ka khof rakhta hai."
1340,"Hazrat Fazala bin Ubaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala achchhi aawaz waley aadmi ko buland aawaz sey Quran padhtey huye us sey bhi ziyada tawajjoh sey sunta hai jis qadr tawajjoh sey gaaney wali londi ka Malik apni londi ka gaanaa sunta hai."
1341,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) masjid mein dakhil huye to eik aadmi ki tilawat ki aawaz sunai di. farmaya : ye kon hai? arz ki gaee : Abdullah bin Qais (Raziallahu anhu) hain. farmaya : usey to aale Dawud (Alaihissalam) ka eik saaz mil gaya hai."
1342,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Quran ko apni aawaazon key sath muzayyan (sajaaya) karo."
1343,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs apna wazeefa (tilawat ya azkaar ka muqarrara mamool) ya wazeefey ka kuchh hissa neend ki wajeh sey na padh saka, phir usney wo (chhuta huwa hissa) Fajr aur Zohar key darmiyan (kisi waqt) padh liya, uskey liye itna hi sawab likha jaeyga, goya usney wo raat ko padha."
1344,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs apney bistar par (soney key liye) aata hai aur uski niyat hoti hai ke wo raat ko uth kar namaz padheyga, phir is par subah tak neend ghalib aa jati hai, uskey liye uski niyat key mutabiq (pura sawab) likha jaeyga aur uski neend uskey Rab ki taraf sey is par sadqa hogi."
1345,"Hazrat Aus bin Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log qabila Saqqeef key wafad mein shamil ho kar Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye, unhoney Quraish key haleefon (doston) ko to Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) key yahan thehraya aur Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney banu Malik ko apni eik imarat mein thehraya. (Hazrat Aus farmatey hain) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) har raat Isha key baad hamarey paas tashrif latey aur qadmon par khadey ho kar hum sey baat cheet farmatey (wa'z aur nasihat kartey jo baaz oqaat taweel (lambi) ho jati) yahan tak key aap kabhi eik paon par bojh dey kar khadey hotey , kabhi doosrey par. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamein aksar wo baaten sunatey jo aap ko apni qom Quraish ki taraf sey takleefen pahunchi thin aur farmatey : (hum aur wo) barabar nahin they. hum log to kamzor aur dabey hotey they. (wo ghalib aur zor-aawar they) phir jab hum Madiney aagey to hamarey aur unkey darmiyan ladaai ka tawazun kam-o-besh honey laga, kabhi hum un par ghalib aatey, kabhi wo hamein nuqsan pahuncha jatey. eik raat aisa huwa ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jis waqt hamarey paas tashrif laya kartey they, uski nisbat takheer sey tashrif laye. mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! aaj raat aap ko hamarey yahan tashrif laney mein der ho gaee. farmaya : meri (roz marra ki) Quran ki manzil puri nahin ho saki thi, mujhey ye baat achchhi na lagi ke usey pura kiye baghair tumharey paas aaun. Hazrat Aus (Raziallahu anhu) ney bayan farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key Sahaba Raziallahu anhum sey daryaft kiya : aap log (rozaana tilawat key liye) Quran Majeed key hissey kis tarah muqarrar kartey hain? to unhoney farmaya : (pehla hissa) teen Suraton ka (Baqara, Aale-Imran aur Nisaa) (doosra hissa) paanch Suraton ka (Maayda sey Bara'at tak)  (teesra hissa) saat Suraton ka (Yunus sey Nahal tak)  (chotha hissa) no Suraton ka (Bani Israel sey furqan tak) (paanchwan hissa) giyara Suraton ka (Sho'araa sey Yaseen tak) (chhata hissa) tehra Suraton ka (Saaffaat sey Hujuraat tak) aur (saatwaan hissa) Mufassal ka (Qaaf sey aakhir tak)."
1346,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Quran Majeed hifz kar liya, phir mainey eik hi raat mein uski tilawat ki to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey khatra hai ke taweel (lamba) waqt guzarney par tum ko uktaahat pesh aa jaeygi. isliye eik mahiney mein (purey) Quran ki tilawat kiya karo. mainey kaha : mujhey apni taqat aur jawani sey faeyda utha leney den. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : phir das din mein (pura) Quran padh liya karo. mainey kaha : mujhey apni taqat aur jawani sey faeyda uthaney den. farmaya : phir saat din mein (pura) Quran padh liya karo. mainey kaha : mujhey apni taqat aur jawani sey (mazeed) faaeyda uthaney den. to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (meri darkhaast qubul karney sey) inkar farma diya."
1347,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney teen din sey kam muddat mein Quran Majeed pura padha usney Quran ko samjha hi nahin."
1348,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : merey ilm mein nahin ke Allah key Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney subah tak pura Quran Majeed padha ho."
1349,"Hazrat Umme-Haani binte Abu-Talib (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mujhey raat ko Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki tilawat ki aawaz sunai deti thi jabke main apney ghar ki chhat par hoti thi."
1350,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney subah tak eik hi aayat bar-bar padhtey huye qiyam farmaya. aayat ye hai : ( إِنْ تُعَذِّبْهُمْ فَإِنَّهُمْ عِبَادُكَ وَإِنْ تَغْفِرْ لَهُمْ فَإِنَّكَ أَنْتَ الْعَزِيزُ الْحَكِيمُ ),''agar to in ko saza dey to be-shak wo terey hi bandey hain aur agar to in ko maaf farma dey to be-shak to hi ghalib hai, badi hikmat wala hai."
1351,Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney namaz padhi. aap jab kisi rehmat ki aayat par pahunchtey to (Allah ki rehmat ka) sawal farmatey. aur jab kisi azab ki aayat par pahunchtey to (Allah key azab sey) panah maangtey aur jab kisi aisi aayat par pahunchtey jis mein Allah ki taqdees aur pakizgi ka zikr hota to Allah ki tasbih bayan farmatey.
1352,"Hazrat Abu-Leila Bilal Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat ko nafl namaz padh rahey they. mainey aap key pehlu mein namaz padhi. (tilawat key doran mein) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik aayat par pahunchey jis mein azab ka zikr tha to aap ney farmaya : (أَعُوذُ بِاللَّهِ مِنَ النَّارِ وَوَيْلٌ لأَهْلِ النَّارِ), ''mein jahannam sey Allah ki panah maangta hun aur jahannamiyon key liye halakat hai.''"
1353,"Hazrat Qatada (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki tilawat key barey mein sawal kiya to unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aawaz ko tawee (lamba)l kartey they."
1354,"Hazrat Ghuzaif bin Haris (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : main Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur arz kiya : kya Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (namaz mein) buland aawaz sey qirat kartey they ya khamoshi sey? unhoney farmaya : kabhi zor sey tilawat kartey they, kabhi khamoshi sey. mainey kaha : Allahu-Akbar ! shukar hai Allah ka jisney is mamley mein gunjaaish (aur aasani) rakhi."
1355,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab raat ko namaz key liye bedaar hotey to farmatey : (اللَّهُمَّ لَكَ الْحَمْدُ أَنْتَ نُورُ السَّمَوَاتِ وَالأَرْضِ وَمَنْ فِيهِنَّ وَلَكَ الْحَمْدُ أَنْتَ قَيَّامُ السَّمَوَاتِ وَالأَرْضِ وَمَنْ فِيهِنَّ وَلَكَ الْحَمْدُ أَنْتَ مَالِكُ السَّمَوَاتِ وَالأَرْضِ وَمَنْ فِيهِنَّ وَلَكَ الْحَمْدُ أَنْتَ الْحَقُّ وَوَعْدُكَ حَقٌّ وَلِقَاؤُكَ حَقٌّ وَقَوْلُكَ حَقٌّ وَالْجَنَّةُ حَقٌّ وَالنَّارُ حَقٌّ وَالسَّاعَةُ حَقٌّ وَالنَّبِيُّونَ حَقٌّ وَمُحَمَّدٌ حَقٌّ اللَّهُمَّ لَكَ أَسْلَمْتُ وَبِكَ آمَنْتُ وَعَلَيْكَ تَوَكَّلْتُ وَإِلَيْكَ أَنَبْتُ وَبِكَ خَاصَمْتُ وَإِلَيْكَ حَاكَمْتُ فَاغْفِرْ لِى مَا قَدَّمْتُ وَمَا أَخَّرْتُ وَمَا أَسْرَرْتُ وَمَا أَعْلَنْتُ أَنْتَ الْمُقَدِّمُ وَأَنْتَ الْمُؤَخِّرُ لاَ إِلَهَ إِلاَّ أَنْتَ وَلاَ إِلَهَ غَيْرُكَ وَلاَ حَوْلَ وَلاَ قُوَّةَ إِلاَّ بِكَ), ''aey Allah ! terey hi liye tareef hai to aasmano ka, zamin ka aur jo koi unkey darmiyan hain, unka Noor hai, aur terey hi liye tareef hai ke to aasmano ko , zamin ko aur jo koi unkey darmiyan hain, in ko qaaim rakhney wala hai. aur terey hi liye tareef hai ke to aasmano ka, zamin ka aur jo koi unkey darmiyan mein hain, unka Malik hai aur terey hi liye tareef hai to hi haq hai, tera wada haq hai, teri mulaqat haq hai, tera farman haq hai, jannat haq hai, jahannam haq hai, qiyamat haq hai, (tamam) anbiya haq hain, aur Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) haq hain. aey Allah ! main tera muteea' farman hun, tujh par eman laya hun, mera aitimad tujhi par hai main teri hi taraf ruju karney wala hun (makhalfeen haq sey), teri hi madad sey behes aur takraar karta hun, tujhi ko apna faisal banata hun to merey sab gunah maaf farma dey jo mainey pehley kiye , baad mein kiye , chhup kar kiye aur jo elania kiye to hi aagey badhaaney wala hai aur to hi peechhey hataney wala hai, sirf to hi mabood hai, terey siwa koi (bar-haq) mabood nahin, aur teri tofiq key baghair na bachao hai na taqat. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney abu-Bakar Khallaad ki sanad sey bhi ye riwayat zikr ki hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab raat ko tahajjud key liye khadey hotey . . . phir mazkura baala riwayat key hum maana bayan kiya."
1356,"Hazrat Aasim bin Humaid (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey sawal kiya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat key qiyam (tahajjud) ki ibtida (shuruat) kis chiz sey kartey they? unhoney kaha : tum ney mujh sey wo baat poochhi hai jo tum sey pehley kisi ney nahin poochhi, aap das baar (اللہُ أَکْبَرُ) das baar (اَلْحَمْدُلِلَّہِ) das baar (سُبْحَانَ اللہِ) aur das baar (اَسْتَغْفِرُاللہ) kehtey they. phir farmatey : (اللَّهُمَّ اغْفِرْلِى وَاهْدِنِى وَارْزُقْنِى وَعَافِنِى), ''aey Allah ! mujhey bakhsh dey, mujhey hidayat dey, mujhey rizq inayat farma aur mujhey aaram aur rahat sey behraa-war farma.'' aur aap qiyamat key din (maidane-hashr mein) khadey honey ki tangi sey Allah ki panah chahtey they."
1357,"Hazrat Abu-Salma bin Abdur-Rehman (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey sawal kiya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab raat ko uthtey they to apni namaz kis tarah shuru kartey they? unhoney farmaya : aap kehtey they : (اللَّهُمَّ رَبَّ جِبْرَئِيلَ وَمِيكَائِيلَ وَإِسْرَافِيلَ فَاطِرَ السَّمَوَاتِ وَالأَرْضِ عَالِمَ الْغَيْبِ وَالشَّهَادَةِ أَنْتَ تَحْكُمُ بَيْنَ عِبَادِكَ فِيمَا كَانُوا فِيهِ يَخْتَلِفُونَ اهْدِنِى لِمَا اخْتُلِفَ فِيهِ مِنَ الْحَقِّ بِإِذْنِكَ إِنَّكَ لَتَهْدِى إِلَى صِرَاطٍ مُسْتَقِيمٍ), ''aey Allah ! aey Jibreel , Mekael aur Israafeel key Malik ! aey aasmano aur zamin key khaliq ! aey poshida aur zahir (sab chizon) ka ilm rakhney waley ! apney bandon main to hi faisla kerega jis jis chiz mein wo ikhtilaf kartey they. haq key jin masaayel mein ikhtilaf kiya gaya hai, un mein mujhey apney hukm sey hidayat nasib farma, be-shak to hi sidhi raah ki taraf hidayat deta hai.'' (Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ustaad) Abdur-Rehman bin umr (Rahimahullah) ney kaha :  (is dua mein) Jibreel ka lafz Hamza key sath yad karo kyonkey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey isi tarah marvi (riwayat hui) hai."
1358,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) namaze Isha sey farigh honey key baad sey subah saadiq tak giyara rakat namaz ada kartey they. har do rakat par salam phertey aur eik rakat witr padhtey aur in rakaaton mein (itna lamba) sajda kartey they ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sar uthaney sey pehley koi shakhs pachas aayaten padh sakta tha. phir jab muazzan namaz Fajr ki pehli Azan dey kar khamosh hota to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uth kar halki si do rakatein padh letey they."
1359,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat ko tehra rakat namaz ada kartey they."
1360,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat ko nau rakatein padhtey they.
1361,"Hazrat Aamir bin Sharaaheel Shaabi (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas aur Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhum sey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki raat ki namaz key mutalliq sawal kiya to unhoney farmaya : ( Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki namaz) tehra rakat hoti thi. un mein aath rakatein (bator nawaafil) hoti thin aur aap teen witr padhtey they aur do rakatein Fajr tulu honey key baad padhtey they."
1362,"Hazrat Zaid bin Khalid Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey (dil mein) kaha aaj raat main zarur Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki namaz (tahajjud) dekhunga, chunanche main aap ki chaukhat ya khemey (key nichley hissey) par sar rakh kar let gaya. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (raat ko) uthey, aap ney (pehley) halki do rakatein padhin, phir do rakatein padhin jo bahut hi taweel (lambi) thin, phir do rakatein padhin jo un sey kam taweel (lambi) thin , phir do rakatein padhin jo un sey pehley wali rakaaton sey kam taweel (lambi) thin , phir do rakatein padhin jo un sey bhi kam taweel (lambi) thin , phir do rakatein padhen , phir witr padha. ye kul tehra rakatein huin."
1363,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja (biwi) mohtarma Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) key yahan soey aur wo un ki khaala thin. Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ney bayan farmaya : main takiye key arz mein letaa aur Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ki ehliya uskiy lambaai mein let gaey. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) so gaey. jab aadhi raat hui ya aadhi raat sey thoda sa pehley ya thoda sa baad ka waqt tha to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bedaar ho gaey aur neend door karney key liye chehrey par haath pherney lagey, phir aap ney Sura Aale-Imran ki aakhiri das aayaat padhin, phir eik (khoonti par) latki hui mushk ki taraf gaey aur us sey wuzu kiya, aap ney khub achchhi tarah wuzu kiya, phir khadey ho kar namaz padhney lagey. Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) ney farmaya : main bhi uth khada huwa. mainey isi tarah kiya (aayaat padhin aur wuzu kiya) jis tarah Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney kiya tha, phir main ja kar aap key (baain) pehlu mein khada ho gaya. (aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki iqtida (pairvi) mein namaz shuru kar di) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apna daayan haath merey sar par rakha (aur mujhey apney peechhey sey apney daain pehlu mein kar liya) aur mera daayan kaan pakad kar modney lagey. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney do rakatein padhin, phir do rakatein padhin, phir do rakatein padhin, phir do rakatein padhin, phir do rakatein padhin, phir do rakatein padhin, phir witr padha. phir let gaey yahan tak key muazzan aa gaya. aap ney halki si do rakatein padhin phir namaz padhney key liye ghar sey (masjid mein) tashrif ley gaey."
1364,"Hazrat Amr bin Abasa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa . mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap key sath kon kon Islam laya hai? farmaya : azad aur ghulam. mainey kaha : kya koi ghadi dusri ghadi ki nisbat Allah sey ziyada qurb ka baais hai? farmaya : haan, raat ka darmiyani hissa."
1365,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat key shuru hissey mein sotey they aur aakhiri hissey mein ibadat kartey they."
1366,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala har raat jab raat ka aakhiri teesra hissa baqi hota hai to (aasmane-duniya par) nuzool farmata hai aur kehta hai : kon hai jo mujh sey maangey to main usey ata karun? kon hai jo mujh sey dua karey to main uski dua qubul karun? kon hai jo mujh sey bakhshish maangey to main usey bakhsh dun? (Allah taala isi tarah farmata rehta hai) yahan tak key subah saadiq tulu ho jati hai. isi liye salaf raat key pehley hissey key bajaey aakhiri hissey mein namaz padhna ziyada pasand kartey they."
1367,"Hazrat Rifaa (bin Araaba) Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala mohlat deta hai yahan tak key jab aadhi ya do tihai raat guzar jati hai to farmata hai : merey bandon ko merey siwa kisi sey hergiz nahin maangna chahiye. jo mujhey pukareyga, main uski dua qubul karunga. jo mujh sey maangeyga, main usey dunga. jo mujh sey bakhshish talab kerega, main usey bakhsh dunga. (ye keyfiyat musalsal jari rehti hai) yahan tak key subah saadiq tulu ho jati hai."
1368,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Yazeed (Rahimahullah) ney Hazrat Alqama (Rahimahullah) sey aur unhoney Hazrat Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat bayan ki ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Sura Baqra ki aakhiri do aayaten (ye shaan rakhti hain ke) jo shakhs unhen eik raat mein padh ley, wo uskey liye kafi hongi. hadees ke raawi Hafs apni hadees mein bayan kartey hain ke Abdur-Rehman bin Yazeed (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : (baad mein) meri mulaqat Hazrat Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey hui jabke wo (Kaaba Shareef ka) tawaf kar rahey they to unhoney (khud) ye hadees mujhey sunai."
1369,"Hazrat Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Sura Baqra ki aakhiri do aayaten raat ko padheyga, wo uskey liye kafi hongi."
1370,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey kisi ko ungh aaye to usey chahiye ke so jaey yahan tak key neend jati rahey. (kyonkey) agar wo ungh ki haalat mein namaz padheyga to kya malum wo (Allah sey) bakhshish maangney lagey to (neend key ghalbey ki wajeh sey pata na chaley aur) apney aap ko bura bhala keh dey.
1371,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) masjid mein tashrif laye to aap ko do sutonon key darmiyan (eik sutoon sey doosrey sutoon tak) eik rassi bandhi hui nazar aai. farmaya : ye rassi kaisi hai? Sahaba ney arz kiya : Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ki hai, wo is maqam par namaz padha karti hain, jab thak jati hain to (ghaflat door karney key liye) iskey sath latak jati hain. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : isey khol do, isey khol do. insan ko (zehni aur jismani) khushi (aur aamaadagi) ki haalat mein namaz padhni chahiye. jab thak jaey to beth jaey."
1372,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey koi shakhs jab raat ko qiyam kerey. phir uski zaban par Quran mushkil ho jaey aur usey pata na chaley ke wo kya keh raha hai to (usey chahiye ke) wo let jaey."
1373,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs maghrib aur Isha key darmiyan bees rakat namaz padhey, uskey liye Allah Taala jannat main eik ghar taamir kar deta hai."
1374,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney Maghrib key baad chhe rakat namaz padhi aur unkey darmiyan koi buri baat na kahi to us ko baara saal ki ibadat key barabar sawab hoga."
1375,"Hazrat Aasim bin Amr (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke Iraaq sey chand afrad Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey milney key liye (watan sey) aaye, jab wo Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir huye to unhon (Hazrat Umar) ney kaha : aap log kis qom sey talluq rakhtey hain? unhoney kaha : Iraaq key rehney waley hain. farmaya : aap log ijazat ley kar aaye hain? unhoney kaha : ji haan. unhoney (Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey) ghar mein namaz padhney key mutalliq sawal kiya. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey uskey mutalliq sawal kiya tha to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aadmi ka ghar mein namaz padhna Noor (ka baais) hai, isliye apney gharon ko munawwar kiya karo. Imam Ibne-Maja ney apney ustaad Muhammad bin abi Husain ki sanad sey ye riwayat bayan ki to Aasim bin Amr aur umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) key darmiyan Umer ka wasta bayan kiya."
1376,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi shakhs apni namaz puri kar ley to usey chahiye ke uska eik hissa apney ghar key liye bhi rakhey kyonkey Allah Taala uski namaz ki wajeh sey uskey ghar mein bhalai ata farmaeyga."
1377,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : apney gharon ko qabren na bana lo."
1378,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey sawal kiya : kon si chiz afzal hai? ghar mein namaz padhna ya masjid mein namaz padhna? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya tum mera ghar nahin dekh rahey ke wo masjid sey kitna qarib hai? mujhey masjid mein namaz padhney sey apney ghar mein namaz padhna ziyada pasand hai, siwaye iskey ke farz namaz ho."
1379,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Haris (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Hazrat Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) key zamaney mein jab Sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum Kasir tadaad mein mojud they, mainey namaze zuhaa key mutalliq daryaft kiya to mujhey Hazrat Umme-Haani (Raziallahu anha) key siwa koi shakhs aisa na mila jo mujhey bataey ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ye namaz padhi hai, albatta Hazrat Umme Haani (Raziallahu anha) ney mujhey bataya ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney is namaz ki aath rakatein padhi thin."
1380,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jo shakhs zuhaa ki baara rakatein padheyga Allah Taala uskey liye jannat mein soney ka eik mehal taamir kerega."
1381,"Hazrat Muaz Adwiya Rahimahullah sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey sawal kiya : kya Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) zuhaa (chaasht) ki namaz padhtey they? unhoney farmaya : haan , chaar rakat padhtey they aur is sey ziyada bhi padh letey they, jis qadr Allah Taala chahta."
1382,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs namaze zuhaa (chaasht) ka dogaana pabandi sey ada kerega, uskey gunah maaf ho jaeyngey, chahey samandar ki jhaag ki tarah (bahut ziyada) hon."
1383,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamein istikhaare (ki dua) isi tarah (ehtimam sey) sikhatey they jis tarah Quran Majeed ki sura ki taalim detey they. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmatey they : jab koi shakhs kisi kaam ka irada karey to usey chahiye ke farz key ilawa do rakatein (nafl) padhey, phir kahey : ( اللَّهُمَّ إِنِّي أَسْتَخِيرُكَ . . padhi. . إِنْ كُنْتَ تَعْلَمُ هَذَا الْأَمْرَ ), 'yahan us chiz ka naam ley, '(خَيْرًا لِي فِي عَاجِلِ أَمْرِي) (ya yun farmaya : ) (خَيْرًا لِى فِى دِينِي وَمَعَاشِي وَعَاقِبَةِ أَمْرِي وَآجِلِهِ . فَاقْدُرْهُ لِي وَيَسِّرْهُ لِي وَبَارِكْ لِي فِيهِ وَإِنْ كُنْتَ تَعْلَمُ ھٰذَالْأَمْر) (jis tarah pehley kaha tha, isi tarah yahan kahey) ( وَإِنْ كَانَ شَرًّا لِي فِي دِينِي وَمَعَاشِي وَعَاقِبَةِ أَمْرِي ) (ya kahey) (شراًلِّي فِي عَاجِلِ أَمْرِي وَآجِلِه فَاصْرِفْهُ عَنِّي وَاصْرِفْنِي عَنْهُ وَاقْدُرْ لِي الْخَيْرَ حَيْثُ كَانَ ثُمَّ رَضِّنِي بِهِ),''aey Allah ! main terey ilm key wastey sey tujh sey bhalai talab karta hun aur teri qudrat key wastey sey (khair ke haasil karne ki) taqat maangta hun aur tujh sey terey azeem Fazal ka sawal karta hun. be-shak to (har chiz par) qudrat rakhta hai aur main (kisi chiz par) qudrat nahin rakhta, to (ghaib) janta hai, main nahin janta. to (tamam) poshida umoor sey ba-khabar hai. aey Allah ! agar terey ilm mein ye kaam merey liye meri duniya, meri muaash (kamaai) aur anjam kaar mein behtar hai. (ya farmaya) merey fori maamlat mein aur baad key maamlat mein behtar hai. to isey merey liye muqaddar kar dey, isey merey liye aasan farma dey aur merey liye is mein barkat ata farma aur agar terey ilm mein ye kaam merey liye bura hai (yani) pehley jumley waley alfaz (dobara) kahey (ke meri duniya mein, meri muaash mein aur merey anjam kaar mein. ya merey fori maamlat mein aur baad key maamlat mein) to is kaam ko mujh sey door hata dey aur mujhey is sey (behtar kaam ki taraf) pher dey aur merey liye khair muqaddar kar dey jahan kahin bhi ho, phir mujhey is par razi (aur mutmain) kar dey.''"
1384,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abu Ufee Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laye aur farmaya : jis ko Allah sey ya makhluq mein sey kisi sey koi hajat darpesh ho, usey chahiye ke wuzu kar key do rakatein padhey, phir kahey : (لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ الْحَلِيمُ الْكَرِيمُ سُبْحَانَ اللَّهِ رَبِّ الْعَرْشِ الْعَظِيمِ الْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ رَبِّ الْعَالَمِينَ اللَّهُمَّ إِنِّي أَسْأَلُكَ مُوجِبَاتِ رَحْمَتِكَ وَعَزَائِمَ مَغْفِرَتِكَ وَالْغَنِيمَةَ مِنْ كُلِّ بِرٍّ وَالسَّلَامَةَ مِنْ كُلِّ إِثْمٍ أَسْأَلُكَ أَلَّا تَدَعَ لِي ذَنْبًا إِلَّا غَفَرْتَهُ وَلَا هَمًّا إِلَّا فَرَّجْتَهُ وَلَا حَاجَةً هِيَ لَكَ رِضًا إِلَّا قَضَيْتَهَا لِی), ''Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin jo hilm wala aur karam wala hai. pak hai Allah jo arshe azeem ka Malik hai, tamam tareef Allah hi key liye hai jo jahano ko paalne-wala hai. aey Allah ! main tujh sey wo cheezen (kaam aur khisaal) maangta hun jo teri rehmat ka sabab hain aur teri bakhshish ka baais ban'ney waley (kaam) aur har neki mein hissey aur har gunah sey salamti ka sawal karta hun. main tujh sey ye darkhaast karta hun ke mera koi gunah maaf kiye baghair, koi gham khatam kiye baghair aur koi hajat jo teri raza key mutabiq ho, puri kiye baghair na chhod.''phir Allah Taala sey duniya aur aakhirat ki jo hajat chahey mang ley. uski qismat mein wo chiz ho jaeygi."
1385,"Hazrat Usman bin Hanif (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik na-bina aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur arz kiya : merey liye dua kijiye ke Allah mujhey shifa dey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar to chahey to main terey liye aakhirat ki bhalai chahun aur wo terey liye behtar hai aur agar to chahey to main dua kar dun. usney kaha : dua hi kar dijiye. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney usey hukm diya ke wo khub achchhi tarah wuzu kar key do rakatein padhey, phir ye dua maangey : (اللَّهُمَّ إِنِّى أَسْأَلُكَ وَأَتَوَجَّهُ إِلَيْكَ بِمُحَمَّدٍ نَبِىِّ الرَّحْمَةِ يَا مُحَمَّدُ إِنِّى قَدْ تَوَجَّهْتُ بِكَ إِلَى رَبِّى فِى حَاجَتِى هَذِهِ لِتُقْضَى اللَّهُمَّ فَشَفِّعْهُ فِىَّ), ''aey Allah ! main tujh sey sawal karta hun aur Nabiey rehmat Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zariey sey teri taraf tawajjoh karta hun. aey Muhammad ! main aap key zariey sey apni is hajat key silsiley mein apney Rab ki taraf tawajjoh karta hun taake wo hajat puri ho jaey. aey Allah ! Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki shafaat merey haq mein qubul farma. Abu-Is'haq ney kaha : ye hadees sahih hai.''"
1386,"Hazrat Abu-Raafey (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey farmaya : chacha jaan ! kya main aap ko eik tohfa na dun? aap ko faeyda na pahunchaaun? aap sey sila rehmi na karun? unhoney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! zarur aisa kijiye. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aap chaar rakatein padhein. har rakat mein sura Fatiha aur koi dusri sura padhein. jab qirat mukammal ho jaey to rukoo karney sey pehley pandarah baar yun kahin : (سُبْحَانَ اللَّهِ وَالْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ وَلاَ إِلَهَ إِلاَّ اللَّهُ وَاللَّهُ أَكْبَرُ), ''Allah pak hai aur tareefen Allah hi key liye hain aur Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin aur Allah sab sey bada hai.'' phir rukoo karen to (rukoo ki haalat mein rukoo ki tasbeehaat padhney key baad) ye tasbih das baar padhein, phir rukoo sey sar uthaeyn to (qaume key azkaar key baad) das baar ye kahen, phir sajda karen to (sajdey ki tasbeehaat key baad) das baar yehi padhein, phir sar uthaeyn to (jalsey ki dua padh kar) das baar ye padhein, phir sajda karen to (sajdey ki tasbeehaat key baad) das baar yehi padhein, phir (sajdey sey) sar uthaeyn to khadey honey sey pehley (jalse istiraahat mein) das baar yehi padhein. ye eik rakat mein pachhattar tasbeehaat hain aur chaar rakaaton mein teen sau tasbeehaat hain. agar aap key gunah sehraye aaliz ki ret (key zarron) key barabar bhi hongey to (is namaz ki wajeh sey) Allah Taala wo sab bakhsh dega. Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! jo rozaana ye namaz na padh sakey to (kya kerey?) aap ney farmaya : haftey main eik baar padh lein. agar aap sey ye bhi na ho sakey to mahiney main eik baar padh lein. yahan tak key Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : warna saal main eik baar to padh lein."
1387,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Abbas bin Abdul-Muttalib sey farmaya : aey Abbas ! aey chacha jaan ! kya main aap ko Atiya na dun, aap ko hadiya na dun, aap ko tohfa na dun, aap key liye das khubiyan (das qism key gunahon ka kaffara bin janey wala amal) na bayan karun? jab aap wo kaam karen to Allah Taala aap key pehley pichhley, puraney aur naey ghalati sey kiye huye aur jaan boojh kar kiye huye, chhotey aur badey, poshida aur zahir gunah bakhsh dey. das khubiyan ye hain (das qism key gunahon ka kaffara bin janey wala amal) aap chaar rakaat ada karen har rakat mein sura Fatiha key sath koi aur sura bhi padhein . jab aap pehli rakat mein qirat sey farigh hon to khadey khadey kahin : (سُبْحَانَ اللَّهِ وَالْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ وَلاَ إِلَهَ إِلاَّ اللَّهُ وَاللَّهُ أَكْبَرُ), ''Allah pak hai, sab taarifein Allah hi key liye hain aur Allah key siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin aur Allah sab sey bada hai.''  pandarah baar ye tasbih padhein, phir rukoo karen aur rukoo mein das baar yehi tasbih kahen, phir rukoo sey sar utha kar das baar yehi kahen, phir sajda karen aur sajdey mein das baar ye padhein, phir sajdey sey sar utha kar yehi tasbih das baar kahen, phir sajda karen aur das baar ye tasbih padhein, phir sajdey sey sar uthaeyn to das baar yehi padhein is tarah har rakat mein pachhattar baar tasbih hogi. chaaron rakaat mein isi tarah padhein. agar aap mein taqat ho to har roz eik baar zarur ye namaz padhein, agar iski himmat na ho to haftey main eik baar padh lein agar iski bhi qudrat na ho to mahiney main eik baar padhein aur agar ye bhi mumkin na ho to sari umr main eik baar padh lein."
1388,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab nisf (aadhe) Shoban ki raat aaye to us raat ko qiyam karo aur din ko roza rakho. us raat Allah Taala suraj key ghurub hotey hi pehley aasman par nuzool farma leta hai aur subah saadiq tulu honey tak kehta rehta hai : kya koi mujh sey bakhshish maangney wala hai ke main usey maaf kar dun? kya koi rizq talab karney wala hai ke usey rizq dun? kya koi (kisi bimari ya musibat mein) mubtala hai ke main usey aafiyat ata farma dun?"
1389,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik raat mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko (ghar mein) na paya. main aap ki talash mein nikli to dekha ke aap Baqee mein hain aur aap ney aasman ki taraf sar uthaya huwa hai. (jab mujhey dekha to) farmaya : Aaisha ! kya tujhey ye dar tha ke Allah aur uska Rasool tujh par zulm kerengey? Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain ke : mainey arz kiya : mujhey ye khof to nahin tha lekin mainey socha (shayad) aap apni kisi (aur) zauja mohtarma (biwi) key yahan tashrif ley gaey hain. to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala nisf (aadhe) Shoban ko aasmane duniya par nuzool farmata hai aur banu-kalb ki bakriyon key baalon sey ziyada (logon) ko maaf farma deta hai."
1390,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey riwayat bayan ki ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala nisf (aadhe) Shoban ki raat (apney bandon par) nazar farmata hai, phir mushrik aur (musalman bhai sey) dushmani rakhney waley key siwa sari makhluq ki maghfirat farma deta hai. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney apney ustaad Muhammad bin Is-haq ki sanad sey ye riwayat bayan ki to unhoney Zuhaak bin Abdur-Rehman aur abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) key darmiyan Zuhaak key baap ka wasta bayan kiya."
1391,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abu Aufaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke jis din Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko abu-Jahal ka sar kaatey janey ki khushkhabri di gaee , aap ney do rakatein padhin."
1392,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko eik kaam ho janey ki khush khabri di gaee to aap sajdey mein gir padey.
1393,Hazrat Kaab bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke jab Allah Taala ney un ki tauba qubul farmaai to wo sajdey mein gir padey.
1394,Hazrat abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko jab koi khushi wala maamla pesh aata to aap Allah Taala ka shukar ada karney key liye sajda rez ho jatey.
1395,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey koi hadees sunta tha to Allah Taala ney mujhey us sey jo faeyda dena hota dey deta aur jab mujhey koi aur aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki hadees sunata to main us sey qism leta. agar wo qism khata to main is par aetbar kar leta. aur Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney mujhey hadees sunai aur abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney sach farmaya. unhoney farmaya ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo bhi shakhs koi gunah kar leta hai, phir achchhi tarah wuzu kar key do rakat namaz padhta hai aur Allah sey bakhshish maangta hai to Allah usey zarur bakhsh deta hai."
1396,"Hazrat Aasim bin Sufiyan Saqafi (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke musalmanon ney ''zaat salaasil'' ki jang ki lekin ye log (Aasim aur unkey kuchh sathi) jang mein shareek na ho sakey. (baad mein pahunchey, chunanche) wo log (kuch arsa) mahaaz par morcha zan rahey (lekin dobara jang ki nobat na aai to), phir wo Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) key paas wapis aagey. us waqt Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ki majlis mein Hazrat abu-Ayyub aur Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhuma) bhi mojud they. Aasim (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : abu-Ayyub ! hum to is saal jihad sey mehroom reh gaey. hamen bataya gaya ke jo shakhs chaar masjidon mein namaz padhey, uska gunah bakhsh diya jata hai. Hazrat abu-Ayyub (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : bhatijey ! main tujhey is sey aasan amal batata hun, mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna aap farma rahey they : jo shakhs wuzu karey jis tarah hukm diya gaya hai aur namaz is tarah padhey jis tarah hukm diya gaya hai, to uskey guzishta amal maaf ho jaeyngey. Aqba ! kya ye hadees isi tarah hai? unhoney kaha : haan (isi tarah hai)."
1397,"Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna hai, aap ney farmaya : bhala batao ! agar kisi key ghar key samney (saaf pani ka) eik darya behta ho, wo is mein rozaana paanch baar ghusl karey to us (key jism) par kitni mail baqi reh jaeygi? haazirin ney kaha : bilkul nahin rahegi. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : namaz gunahon ko isi tarah khatam kar deti hai jis tarah pani sey mail kuchail khatam ho jati hai."
1398,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney kisi aurat sey zina sey kam tar najaaiz harkat ki. ye to malum nahin ke usney kis had tak ghalati ki, taaham zina nahin kiya, phir wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur ye baat arz ki. tab Allah Taala ney ye aayat nazil kar di : (أَقِمِ الصَّلاَةَ طَرَفَىِ النَّهَارِ وَزُلَفًا مِنَ اللَّيْلِ إِنَّ الْحَسَنَاتِ يُذْهِبْنَ السَّيِّئَاتِ ذَلِكَ ذِكْرٰى لِلذَّاكِرِينَ),''din key kinaron mein bhi namaz qaaim kijiye aur raat ki ghadiyon mein bhi, yaqinan nekiyan buraiyon ko door kar deti hain. ye nasihat hai nasihat qubul karney walon key liye.'' Sabab ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya ye (riayat) sirf merey liye hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo bhi is par amal kerey. uskey liye hai."
1399,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala ney meri ummat par pachas namazein farz kin. main ye hukm ley kar wapis aaya yahan tak key Musa (Alaihissalam) key paas pahuncha , Musa (Alaihissalam) ney farmaya : aap key Rab ney aap ki ummat par kya farz kiya hai? mainey kaha : usney mujh par pachas namazein farz ki hain. unhoney farmaya : apney Rab key paas wapis jaiye kyonkey aap ki ummat iski taqat nahin rakhti. main dobara apney Rab ki taraf gaya to usney nisf (aadhi) namazein maaf farma den. main phir Musa (Alaihissalam) key paas aaya aur unhen bataya. unhoney farmaya : apney Rab key paas wapis jaiye kyonkey aap ki ummat iski taqat nahin rakhti. main phir apney Rab ki taraf gaya to usney farmaya : ye (ada karney mein) paanch hain aur yehi (sawab mein) pachas hain. mera farman tabdeel nahin hota. main phir Musa (Alaihissalam) key paas aaya . unhoney farmaya : apney Rab key paas wapis jaiye, mainey kaha : mujhey apney Rab sey sharam mehsus hoti hai."
1400,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : tumharey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko pachas namazon ka hukm diya gaya tha to unhoney tumharey Rab sey kami kara key paanch karwa lein."
1401,"Hazrat Ubada bin Samit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap ney farmaya : paanch namazein hain jo Allah ney apney bandon par farz ki hain to jo shakhs inhen is tarah ley kar hazir huwa ke unkey haq ko ghair aham samajh kar un mein kami na ki ho to Allah Taala qiyamat key din us sey wada farmaeyga ke usey jannat mein dakhil kar dega aur jo unhen is tarah ley kar aaya ke unkey haq ko ahmiyat na detey huye un mein kami ki (puri namazein ada na kin) to usey Allah key yahan koi ehad hasil nahin hoga, ( Allah ki marzi hai) chahey usey azab dey, chahey bakhsh dey."
1402,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney farmaya : hum masjid mein bethey they ke isi beech main eik aadmi oont par sawar ho kar masjid mein dakhil huwa . usney masjid mein oont bithaya , uska ghutna baandha , phir kaha : aap logon mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kon hain? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Sahaba ki majlis mein tek lagaey tashrif farma they. unhoney kaha : ye safed rang jo tek laga kar tashrif farma hain. us aadmi ney kaha : Abdul-Muttalib key betey ! Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (baat karo) jawab dey raha hun. us aadmi ney kaha : aey Muhammad ! main aap sey kuchh daryaft karunga aur sawal mein sakhti hogi, aap dil mein (narazi) mehsus na kijiyega. aap ney farmaya : jo chaho poochh lo. aadmi ney kaha : aap ko aap key Rab ki aur aap sey pehley logon key Rab ki qism dey kar poochhta hun kya aap ko Allah ney sab logon ki taraf bheja hai? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah gawah hai, haan (yehi baat hai).  usney kaha : main aap ko Allah ki qism dey kar poochhta hun kya Allah ney aap ko raat din mein paanch namazein padhney ka hukm diya hai? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah gawah hai, haan (aisa hi hai). usney kaha : main aap ko Allah ki qism dey kar poochhta hun kya aap ko Allah ney saal mein us mahiney (Ramzan) key rozey rakhney ka hukm diya hai? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah gawah hai, haan. usney kaha : main aap ko Allah ki qism dey kar poochhta hun ke kya Allah ney aap ko hukm diya hai ke aap hamarey dolat mandon sey ye sadqa (zakat) ley kar hamarey gharibon mein taqseem farmaeyn? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah gawah hai, haan. us shakhs ney kaha : main aap ki laee hui (shariyat) par eman ley aaya hun aur main apney peechhey apni qom key afrad ki taraf sey pegham-rasaan bin kar aaya hun. main banu Saad bin Bakr (qabeela) ka eik fard Zamaam bin Solba hun."
1403,"Hazrat abu-Qatada bin Rabai (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah ney farmaya : mainey aap ki ummat par paanch namazein farz ki hain aur mainey apney aap sey wada kiya hai ke jo shakhs unhen waqt par pabandi sey ada kerega mein usey jannat mein dakhil karunga aur jisney unhen pabandi sey ada na kiya, uskey haq mein mera koi wada nahin."
1404,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : meri is masjid main eik namaz, Masjide Haram key siwa , kisi bhi masjid mein padhi janey wali hazar namazon sey afzal hai. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney apney ustaad Hisham bin Ammar sey, unhoney Sufiyan bin Uena sey, unhoney Zohri sey, unhoney Saeed bin Musaiyab sey, unhoney Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) key wastey sey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey isi tarah riwayat bayan ki."
1405,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : meri is masjid main eik namaz, Masjide Haram key siwa, dusri masjidon mein padhi janey wali hazar namazon sey afzal hai."
1406,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : meri masjid mein namaz Masjide Haram key siwa kisi bhi masjid ki hazaron namazon sey afzal hai. aur Masjide Haram main eik namaz padhna kisi dusri masjid ki eik lakh namazon sey afzal hai."
1407,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki azad karda khatoon Hazrat Memuna binte Saad (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! hamein Baitul-Maqdis key barey mein masla bata dijiye . Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wo hashr-nashr ki sar zamin hai. wahan ja kar namaz padha karo kyonkey us jagah main eik namaz padhna kisi aur jagah hazar namazein padhney ki tarah hai. mainey arz kiya : ye farmaiye ke agar mujhey safar kar key wahan janey ki taqat na ho (to kya karun)?  farmaya is masjid key liye tel bhej do jis sey is mein chiragh jalaey jaeyn, jisney ye kaam kiya, wo bhi aisey hi hai jaisey wo shakhs jo (ziyaarat key liye) wahan gaya."
1408,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab Hazrat Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Dawud (Alaihissalam) Baitul-Maqdis ki taamir sey farigh huye to unhoney Allah sey teen cheezen maangin : aisa faisla jo Allah key faisley key mutabiq ho aur aisi badshahat jo unkey baad kisi key shaayaan na ho aur jo shakhs bhi is masjid mein sirf namaz ki niyat sey aaye wo gunahon sey isi tarah pak saaf ho jaey jis tarah us din (gunahon sey pak) tha jab usey uski maa ney janm diya tha. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : do cheezen to unhen mil chukin aur mujhey ummid hai ke teesri bhi mil hi gaee hai."
1409,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kajawey kas kar sirf teen masjidon ki taraf safar kiya ja sakta hai. Masjide Haram, meri ye masjid (Masjide Nabawi) aur Masjide Aqsaa."
1410,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kajawey kas kar safar na kiya jaey magar teen masjidon ki taraf. Masjide Haram ki taraf, Masjide Aqsaa ki taraf aur meri is Masjid ki taraf."
1411,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key Sahaba Hazrat Usaid bin Zuher Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Masjide Qubaa main eik namaz eik Umerey key barabar hai."
1412,Hazrat Abu-Umama Asad bin Sehal bin Hanif (Raziallahu anhuma) ney apney walid Hazrat Sehal bin Hanif (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat kiya hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs apney ghar mein wuzu kerey. phir Masjide-Qubaa mein aaye aur us main eik namaz padhey usey eik Umerey ka sawab milega.
1413,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aadmi ka apney ghar mein namaz padhna eik namaz key barabar hai aur uska qabiley (ya mahalley) ki masjid mein namaz padhna pachchees namazon key barabar hai aur Jaama masjid mein namaz padhna paanch sau namazon key barabar hai. aur Masjide Aqsaa mein namaz padhna pachas hazar namazon key barabar hai aur meri Masjid (Masjide Nabawi) mein namaz padhna pachas hazar namazon key barabar hai aur Masjide Haram mein namaz padhna eik lakh namazon key barabar hai."
1414,"Hazrat Ubai-bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab Masjide Nabawi eik chhappar ki surat mein thi to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khajoor key eik taney ki taraf (munh kar key) namaz padha kartey they aur usi taney sey tek laga kar khutba detey they. eik Sahaba ney arz kiya : kya hum aap key liye koi aisi chiz na bana den jis par aap Jumey key din (khutba deney key liye) khadey huwa karen taake log aap ki taraf mutawajjeh ho saken aur aap ka khutba (achchhi tarah) sun saken? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : haan. usney aap key liye (member key) teen darjey bana diye. wohi (teen sidhiyan) ab (mojud) member ka sab sey baalaai (oopri) hissa hai. jab member tayyar ho gaya to Sahaba kiram ney isey usi maqam par rakha jahan wo ab hai. jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uth kar member par janey lagey to us taney key paas sey guzrey jis sey tek laga kar khutba diya kartey they. jab aap us sey aagey badhey to wo zor zor sey roney laga yahan tak key (shiddate gham sey) uski aawaz phat gaee. jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney taney (key roney) ki aawaz suni to (member sey) nichey tashrif ley aaye, us (taney) par haath phertey rahey yahan tak key wo khamosh ho gaya. uskey baad aap phir member par tashrif ley gaey. aap jab namaz padhtey they to uskey peechhey namaz padhtey they. jab Masjide-Nabawi ko (dobara taamir karney key liye) todaa gaya aur masjid ki imarat mein tabdili (aur tausee) ki gaee to wo tanaa Hazrat Ubai-bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) ney ley liya, wo unkey paas unkey ghar hi mein raha yahan tak key bahut puraanaa ho gaya, phir usey dimak ney kha liya aur wo reza reza ho gaya."
1415,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas aur Hazrat Anas Raziallahu anhum sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik taney sey tek laga kar khutba detey they. jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney member banwaayaa to aap member ki taraf chaley. tanaa (sutoon) ro pada. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey paas aaye aur usey seeney sey lagaya. tab wo khamosh huwa. Nabi (Alaihissalam) ney farmaya : agar main isey galey sey na lagata to ye qiyamat tak rotaa rehta.
1416,"Hazrat Abu-Haazim (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke logon mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key member key barey mein ikhtilaf paida ho gaya ke wo kis chiz (ki lakdi) sey bana huwa tha? chunanche wo Hazrat Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aaye aur un sey poochha. unhoney farmaya : ye baat mujh sey ziyada jan'ney wala koi baqi nahin raha. wo ghaaba key jhao sey bana tha. usey falan khatoon key falan badhaee ghulam ney banaya tha. wo usey ley kar hazir huwa. jab wo (apney maqam par) rakha gaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) is par khadey huye, aap ney qibley ki taraf munh kiya. log aap key peechhey (aap ki iqtida (pairvi) mein namaz ada kar rahey) they, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney qirat ki, phir rukoo kiya, phir (rukoo sey) sar uthaya, phir aap ultey paon peechhey hatey yahan tak key zamin par sajdey kiye , phir dobara member par khadey ho gaey aur qirat ki, phir rukoo kiya, phir qauma kiya, phir ultey paon peechhey hatey yahan tak key zamin par sajdey kiye."
1417,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik darkht ki jad ya farmaya eik darkht key taney key qarib khadey hotey they, phir aap ney member banwaa liya to tanaa roney laga yahan tak key masjid mein mojud logon ney uski aawaz suni (wo rotaa raha) yahan tak key Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney uskey paas aa kar is par haath pheraa to wo khamosh ho gaya. eik aadmi ney kaha : agar aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey paas na aatey to wo qiyamat tak rotaa rehta."
1418,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik raat mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki iqtida (pairvi) mein namaz (tahajjud) padhi. aap itna arsa khadey rahey ke mainey eik burey kaam ka irada kar liya. (Abu-Waeil farmatey hain) mainey kaha : wo kon sa kaam tha? farmaya : mainey irada kiya ke main beth jaun aur Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko khada rehney dun."
1419,"Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney qiyam farmaya yahan tak key aap key qadam Mubarak sooj gaey. arz kiya gaya : Allah key Rasool ! Allah ney aap key to agley pichhley gunah maaf kar diye hain (phir aap itni mashaqqat kyon kartey hain)? farmaya : kya main shukar guzar banda na banun?"
1420,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (lambi) namaz padhtey they yahan tak key aap key qadmon par varam aa jata. arz kiya gaya : Allah Taala ney aap key agley pichhley gunah maaf kar diye hain. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : to kya main shukar guzar banda na banun?
1421,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey sawal kiya gaya : kon si namaz afzal hai? farmaya : lamba qunoot (lambi qiyam wali namaz)."
1422,"Hazrat Abu-Fatima (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! mujhey koi amal bataaiye jis par main qaaim rahun aur usey kiya karun. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kasrat sey sajdey kiya kar kyonkey to Allah key liye jo bhi sajda kerega uski wajeh sey Allah tera eik darja buland kar dega aur teri eik ghalati maaf kar dega."
1423,"Hazrat Maadaan bin Abu-Talha Yaamree (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke main Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) sey mila to mainey arz kiya : mujhey koi hadees sunaaiye shayad Allah mujhey us sey faeyda pahunchaey. wo khamosh rahey. mainey dobara arz kiya to wo khamosh rahey. mainey teen baar yehi kaha to mujh sey farmaya : Allah key liye sajdey kiya kar kyonkey mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna hai : jo banda Allah key liye eik sajda karta hai, uski wajeh sey Allah uska eik darja buland karta hai aur eik ghalati maaf kar deta hai. Hazrat Maadaan (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : phir meri mulaqat Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) sey hui, mainey un sey yehi darkhaast ki to unhoney bhi mujhey yehi jawab diya."
1424,"Hazrat Ubada bin Samit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna : jo banda bhi Allah key liye eik sajda karta hai, Allah uskey badley mein uskey liye eik neki likhtaa hai aur is (sajde) ki wajeh sey uska eik gunah maaf karta hai aur is (sajde) ki wajeh sey uska eik darja buland karta hai, isliye sajdey kasrat sey karo."
1425,"Hazrat Anas bin Hakeem Zabi (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke mujh sey Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : jab to apney shehar walon key paas pahunchey to unhen batana ke mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna hai : musalman bandey sey qiyamat key din sab sey pehley jis chiz ka hisab liya jaeyga, wo farz namaz hai. agar usney puri namazein padhi hongi to theek hai warna kaha jaeyga : dekho kya uskey koi nafl bhi hain? agar uskey nafl huye to uskey farzon ki kami naflon sey puri kar di jaeygi, phir doosrey farz kaamon ka hisab bhi isi tarah hoga."
1426,"Hazrat Tameem daari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat key din bandey sey jis amal ka sab sey pehley hisab liya jaeyga, wo uski (farz) namaz hai. agar usey pura ada kiya hoga to (baqi namaazein) uskey liye nafl likh di jaeyngi. agar unhen pura nahin ada kiya hoga to Allah Taala farishton sey farmaeyga : dekho, kya tumhen merey bandey key koi nafl miltey hain? usney apney faraaiz mein jo kotahi ki thi, wo un (nawaafil) sey puri karo, phir doosrey kaamon ka hisab bhi isi andaz sey hoga."
1427,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya tum mein sey kisi sey ye nahin ho sakta ke jab wo namaz padhey to aagey-peechhey ya daain baain ho jaey. yani nafl aur sunnat padhtey waqt."
1428,"Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Imam is jagah (nafl ya sunnat) namaz na padhey jahan usney farz namaz ada ki hai yahan tak key wahan sey eik taraf hat jaey. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney apney ustaad Kasir bin Ubaid Hamsi sey , unhoney Baqiyya sey , unhoney abu-Abdur-Rehman Tameemi sey ba-wasta Usman bin Ata, Hazrat Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) sey isi tarah riwayat kiya."
1429,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Shabal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney teen kamon sey mana farmaya hai : kowey ki tarah thongein maarney sey, darindey ki tarah bazu phelaney sey aur is baat sey ke aadmi namaz key liye eik jagah muqarrar kar ley jis tarah oont (baadey mein apney liye) jagah muqarrar kar leta hai."
1430,Hazrat Yazeed bin Abu-Ubaid (Rahimahullah) Hazrat Salma bin Akwaa (Raziallahu anhu) key mutalliq farmatey hain ke wo zuhaa (chaasht) key nafl padhney key liye tashrif latey to us sutoon ki taraf jatey jo musahaf key paas hai. uskey qarib namaz padhtey. main (Yazeed bin Abu-Ubaid) masjid key kisi hissey ki taraf ishara kar key kehta : aap yahan kyon nahin namaz padh letey? wo farmatey : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko is jagah ehtimam sey namaz padhtey dekha hai.
1431,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Saaib (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Fateh Makka key din Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap ney namaz padhi to apney jootey apni baain taraf rakhey."
1432,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : apney jootey apney paon mein rakho (pehney raho). agar unhen utaaro to apney dono paon key darmiyan rakho. unhen apni daain taraf na rakhna, na apney sathi key daain taraf rakhna, na apney peechhey rakhna ke apney peechhey waley (namazi) ko takleef do."
